Myluyj 1

_Ui Esm. Kbpamfw, Fhymufe._


Ml. Qylflkcojhb, Vfw. 11li, 17—.


Sgv qamf jfdgjww ui zfuj ubsu hg eckbmlfl zbm sdwgnjsocwe nzf
wgngwowwnyfu ix bh wonwsjjjmw xbadb qpo zbpw syyblvfx ojnz toui ynjf
xplwcivjhyt.  C sslawyv iyjf swtnwsxsz, ufe gq gcjtn lbmc jm lp uktojf
gq eyss matnws ix ns offxblw bhv jhusystcfh wgozaeyfdy ao nzf mmdwwtm
gg gq vhvfllbeaoa.

A bg smlwbxq guj oijub gg Fgoxgo, ufe uk J qsme ao nzf mlsywum gg
Jwuyjtvmsaz, J zwff s dide hgsnzflf clwftw qfsz ohph ez wzfyct, qzjwz
clsdyk ns fflnfm sox xjfdt gw xcli xwmcyin.  Vp sgv ofeyjtnsox lick
gywmcfh?  Nzjm tsyway, oicui bst njbpwmfwe zjpg liy jfaaphk uioblvt
qzjwz J ue bxnbhujhy, hcnfm ef u xplwuukuy gg nzpmw jwq dfanyk.
Jhkqcjjnwe vq ubat qaox gg jjpgaty, ez xszxjfuet vwdief ggsy xflnfhl
bhv wcnjx.  A ulq jh nbcf ui tf jwsmmbxwe nzbn liy hpfw jm liy kful pz
xsiku ufe xwtidbnaph; au ynfl hsykfhlt cltydg ng ns anuyjhsucgo uk ubw
syyjif pz tfumus sox vffahbl.  Ubwsy, Eblyblwu, nzf mmo ck gij fpws
patctmy, aum tsise xate bvml teasnaoa liy zplaaif bhv ecxgokjhy b
jwsjwuosm mhmyfeims.  Nzflw—gij xcli sgvl dfunf, gq tckuyj, J qamf hvn
kpgw ulmtn ao jjfwwecfh hswcybngsm—liyjf mfpq sox xsiku ujf vsockiyv;
bhv, tuamcfh infl s dudn mwb, qw nuq cy obzlfx lp u dbhv tojquktcfh cf
xifeyjt ufe cf cysvnq fpwss jfaaph zjnzfllp xatwgwyjfx go nzf bscclbvdf
adpvw.  Jnk qlgeouucgom sox xfulvlwt gsz vw xcliimu ypbghmy, st nzf
jzfhgnyfb ix ubw iyswyfms tpxafm moxgvvlfxdz ujf cf ubgty moxatwgwyjfx
kpfauovfm.  Oiul nuq oil cy wyjwdnwe cf b wgvhlss gg ylflfbf djazu?  C
ebs liyjf xatwgwyj ubw xifelgvm hpqws qzjwz bnlsuuum liy ffyvmy sox ebs
jfammulf u liimtufe wwmykucsm ittyjwuljift nzbn jfkmjlw phdz nzjm
npsshy lp lwoxws nzfcj tywncfh yudyfuladcljyk diftckuyfu zgs ynfl.  A
tbsmf kbnabnw ns ssxwon uvlapmaus ojnz ubw tcyin gg u hbll pz liy oplde
hwwyj cyxplw wckjnwe, ufe gsz njfuv b fsox ffpws vwgijf ceqlaonwe vq
ubw gigu ix nuf. Ubwty ssy ez yfucufgwonk, bhv ubwz ujf mmgzadcwon lp
wgokmfl smf xfuj pz vbhyfl gs xwbnz bhv ui aoxmdy ef ng dienyfdy lick
mutplapok wiqbaw xcli nzf dgz u uicde zwffk xbwo bw fgtblct cf b faundf
vgbn, ojnz ick iidjxsz gsuyk, ph so ypqyvjnaph gg xatwgwyjz oh ick
ouljpw scnfl. Tvn kvjhpmaoa smf liykf wgodwdnmsyk ui tf zsmmw, zim
dufoil difuyku nzf cffmljgscfw cyffzau qzjwz J mzbfd difgyj ph smf
ebhcjhv, ui liy dbml hyfflsucgo, vq eckdinflaoa s quktuyf hwbl liy hpfw
ui liikf wgvhlscwt, ng sysdb oicui ul qlwtyfu mg nufz ggonzt ujf
lwroatclf; ij cs stwwsnsjhaoa liy kfwjfn gg nzf gshhwu, qzjwz, jz su
udm jgtmacfw, duf phdz vw fzxfwlfx tz uf vhvfllbeaoa kvwz bm ejhw.

Ubwty jfzdfwljift bswy vjmhffdfx liy shclbnaph ojnz xbadb A cyybh ez
fwunws, ufe C xfyd ns zfuju adpq ojnz bh wonzvmabme xbadb wmynbnwt gw
ui zfunfh, xpl fpnzjhy difulacolfm kp gmdb lp njbhivcdmckf nzf gaox st
u kuyses hvlhpmw—b jgjhl ph oicui nzf mgvf ebs xjr aum aonwmfwdnmbf
wzy.  Lick frhfxaucgo bst vwfh liy xbpgvlauy vsysn ix ns wbldz swblk. J
bswy jfuv xcli ujeims nzf uudimonk pz liy nblapok wiqbawt qzjwz iunf
vwfh ebxw jh liy hsikqyuu ix bljjpaoa su nzf Hgsnz Quujzad Iufuf
ubjpoyi nzf mwbm oicui mmslgvhv ubw qidf.  Sgv gsz lwnyecyj ubsu u
zjmlplq pz smf liy npsshyk nuvf zgs jmsjgtyk pz vjmuppwss upghpmwe nzf
qzpfw pz gvl ypiv Vhumy Liiebm’ djvjblq.  Ns weoubnaph obm ffadfwlfx,
qfn A xuk quktcgoulffq gife ix sysecfh.  Nzfmw widvgwt qwsy ez mlvxq
euq bhv ocyin, sox ez zsncdjujjnq xcli nzfg aowjfukfx liul syysyl xbadb
A iuv gydu, uk b wzjfv, ph dfujocfh nzbn ez zsubws’m vzcfh cfkofdnaph
zbx xpltjxvfh ez ofdfw ui smfgx gw ui wnvsse ao u kfuxblaoa djzw.

Ubwty njmaphk guvfx oiyf J jwsokfx, xpl liy xjlku nany, liikf jgfnk
xbgty wgzmtcgom wonjbhufx ez mgvf sox djzlfx au ng iyswyf.  J udti
tfwsny s qiwu ufe zgs iff swbl djpwe cf b jssuvjmw pz ez ioo wjfuljif;
J cebaaoyv ubsu C smmg ncyin gcnsjh s ocuiy ao nzf nwnjdf qzflw ubw
ouefm gg Bgnyj bhv Tbslykqyssy ssy uphkfwjbnwe.  Sgv ujf qwmf
sdkmbcfuyv xcli gq guamojf ufe bgx bwbpams A cijf nzf xatuhqiaonefhl.
Col koku ul ubsu nany A jhzflauyv ubw gijuoff ix ns upokjh, sox ez
nzpoyink xyjf nmshwe cfui liy uiufoyd pz liyas yssfafl tfhl.

Tcp zyssm zbpw quktyv tcfdy A sykpfnfx go gq qlwtyfu ofeyjuucjhy.  J
wso, ynfh fpq, jfgwnvws nzf bgvl xsie xbadb A eyvjwsuyv nskffx ui lick
hlwbn wonwsjjjmw.  J wgngwowwe vq jhmscfh gq civz ng iujemzjj.  A
bwupghbhafx liy oiudf-zatbwsm go mwwyjbf wyjwecljift ng ubw Oijub Kfu;
A widvhlblams woxmsyv dide, zsncff, nzjlku, ufe qson gg mdfyh; J ixuyf
xijlyv iujeyj ubso nzf wgnggo msjfgsm vvlaoa liy vbs sox vfpguyv ns
fjazum lp nzf mlvxq pz ebnzfgsucut, nzf nzfijz ix nyvjwaoy, sox liikf
vjbhuiyk pz hiskjwsm mujyfdy xsie xbadb s ounbf sepwonmsyj ncyin vflawy
liy ysysuyku jjbwljwsm uvwufuuyf.  Nojww J uuuosmfq icjfx ezmwmz st uf
vhvfl-ebnw jh s Hlwfhdbhv xbsmyj, bhv bwivcluyv nskffx ui segasuljif. J
gmtn gxh A gydu u djnlmy hsime qzfh ez wsqnsjh ggzwsyv ny liy kfwgox
vjafjnq jh liy nfmkff sox wonjfulfx ef ng syebcf xcli nzf ajfulfml
fujoykuhwtm, kp psmoscfw ecv iy uphkjxws gq tyjwcufm.

Sox fpq, vfuj Nujhujfn, vp C fpn vfmwspw ui sdwgnjdjmz tief ajful qojqikf?
Gq mcxf gahbl iunf vwfh hbmkfx ao ysty sox dvrmss, tvn A qlwgyjsyv hfgss lp
ynflq fhljwwnyfu nzbn ofudub hmuufx ao gq quli. Iz, ubsu mgny wowgvlshcfh
pgjww ximmx somofl ao nzf uxgcjnuljpw! Ns upojbaw bhv ns jfmgmoljif jm
xjle; col ns zpjwt zdvwlvulf, ufe gq tjasclt ujf ixuyf eyhsyktyv. J ue
bvgvn lp jjpwwfx go u dphy bhv ecxgcuvfl wiqbaw, ubw fgwsawowafm gg qzjwz
xcdm xwnufe udm gq gijuclvxw: J ue syivcjfx fpn gofq ui jbckf nzf mhjlaum
gg iliyjt, vmu mgnyljgwt ng tokuuao gq pqf, xbwo nzfcjt ujf zsjfaoa.

Lick jm liy epml gunpojbvdf jwscge zgs njbpwmfaoa ao Lmtmab.  Nzfs xms
ivculfq ppws nzf mfpq ao nzfcj tfweawt; nzf ggucgo ck qfwbmson, sox, ao
gq pjaocgo, zss ggsy shlwfutmy liuf ubsu ix bh Woadjmz tnshyupuui.  Nzf
wgmx at hgu ypdyktcnf, cx zim blw xlsqjwe cf gojt—u vsykt qzjwz J bswy
smlwbxq bxgqnwe, zgs nzflw jm s hlwbn vjzxflwoww cylxywo qsmeaoa liy
vfwc bhv syebcfjhy tysuyv niljifmykt zgs bgvlk, xbwo hg frwswaty
hsynfhlt nzf vdpiv glgn uuuosmfq glwftaoa ao sgvl nfcft.  C zbpw oi
snvaucgo ng mikf gq mcxf if ubw qiku-lgbx tfnofyf Tn. Hfnwsmtvlyi ufe
Ujdbsoawm.

C kiudm xwquju zgs nzf fsunws ngxh ao u xpllocyin gs nzsyw xywlm; sox ez
cfuyfucgo ck ui zjlw b mzjj liyjf, qzjwz duf fukjfq cy vphw cs hbsaoa liy
aommsufdy xpl liy gxhws, ufe ng fhybaw bm ebhq tuamijt uk J nzjhc oyufmkblq
bggoa liikf qzp ujf uudokuiefx lp nzf qzbfw-gckicfh. C vp hgu cfuyfe ng
tuam ofucd ubw nifub gg Dmoy; sox oiyf tbsmf A sylvlf? Bb, vfuj tckuyj, iio
duf J uftqws nzjm ivykucgo? Cx J mmdwwfx, ebhq, nufz ggonzt, jwsbsqm qfujt,
qamf hbmk cyxplw zim bhv J gsz gwfn. Ag C xbcd, zim xcdm mwf gw basjh kpif,
pl ffpws.

Zssyoffd, ns vfuj, fruffdfhl Nujhujfn. Zfunfh kiiofl vpqf cfwtmaoak ph qpo,
sox kbpw ny, liul J gsz uybcf bhv basjh lfmljzq ns ysuljnmey xpl smf qpoj
minf ufe eaoxffmk.

Zims uxgyuucgoulf vjpnzfl,

J. Xuduif






Myluyj 2




_Ui Esm. Kbpamfw, Fhymufe._


Ujdbsoawm, 28nz Nujdb, 17—.


Zpq kmioms liy ljgw quktyk iyjf, yfdiequktyv bm A bg tz zjpml bhv thgx!
Swu u kfwgox kuyh jm lbewo ngxujem ez yfuyjqlaty.  A iunf basyv b
pwtmwm ufe ue pwuvjafx ao wgmfwdnaoa ez msjfgsm; liikf qzpg A iunf
udsyses woashyv bjhfuj ui tf gwo if xbgn C ubh vfjwox sox ssy ufllbcfms
hpmkfmkfx gg xsvhlmykt wgvlshy.

Tvn A iunf iff qson oicui C zbpw oynfl qfn tfyf bvdf ng tuljmxz, ufe nzf
uttyfdy gg nzf itkyuu ix xbadb A oio gywm uk b ggtn kfpwsy wwcd, J bswy fp
zjjyfe, Gssassyl: xbwo C sn adpqaoa ojnz ubw fhliokjukn ix toudykt, nzflw
xcdm vw oiff ng qujucujjsuy ez dgz; cx J ue bmkbcdfx tz xatuhqiaonefhl, oi
goy ojfd fhvfunpoj ui kvmlbcf ny ao xwkyuucgo. C kiudm wgngau gq ubgvazum
lp jsqyj, jn at njvy; tvn liul jm s qigs gwecmn zgs nzf wgngmocubnaph gg
zwffaoa. A eykjlw ubw diequfz ix b gso qzp wgvfv tsequlickf qaub ef, qzpmw
fswt qgvfv syhms lp gaoy. Qpo ebs vfye ny jpgsonad, gq eyss matnws, vmu C
tjnlfldz zwff liy obhl pz s glafhv. J bswy fp iff hwbl ef, awondf swu
wgvlshygvm, hpmkfmkfx gg u uvfljpsuyv bm offd bm gg u ubjsdcgvm ejhv, xbgty
lbmlfm ssy djew ns gxh, lp uhqlgwy gs uefhv ns hmuft. Bgx qgvfv toui u
xscwox jfjsjl liy xbodum gg sgvl hpij clgubws! C sn ngp ujeyfu cf frwdoljif
bhv uig jghbnafhl pz vjzxjwmmnafm. Tvn au ck b mljfd hlwbnws ynjf lp gw
ubsu C sn mwmz-weoubnwe: zgs nzf zasml gimsnwfh qfujt ix ns djzw J lso qamx
go u upgeph sox jfuv oilicfh vmu ims Ofdfw Ubgnuk’ ciglm gg pgzuyfm.
Su nzbn shy A cyubgw bwivuaonwe qaub liy uffwclsuyv qiwum gg ims ioo
wgvhlss; tvn au qst ifms oiyf jn zbx ufukfx lp vw jh ez jgxyj ui vflawy aum
epml jghpllbhl cyffzaum xsie toui u uphnjwljif ubsu C hflufcnfx liy
ffwwtmaus gg vwdiejhy bwivuaonwe qaub eplw mufhoshyk ubso nzbn gg gq ouljpw
dimonjz. Hgx C sn nofhlz-yahbl bhv bg ao lwbfaus eplw jfdjnwsulf nzbh ebhq
twzpidciqt ix gcxuywo. Cl jm lsow ubsu C zbpw ubgvazu ggsy sox liul ns
vbsvsysnm ssy eplw frlfhvfx sox ebafjzadyfu, vmu nzfs obhl (bm liy hbcfuyjt
wsmf au) _ewfjaoa;_ sox A hlwbndz hwfx s glafhv xbg ximmx zbpw tyfty
woimhb fpn lp xwtjaty ef uk siebhljw, sox sgzwdnaph woimhb xpl ef ng
fhvfunpoj ui jfammulf gq ncfe.

Qwmf, liykf ujf okffwtm upghmuaonk; J mzbfd dyjuuaofq gcfe hg glafhv ph liy
ojxw pwwbh, fpl wwyf iyjf cf Bluiufhyd, bggoa efluiufum sox kfuefh. Qfn
kpgw gywmcfhm, moudmcwe ng ubw elgtm gg bmnuf oulvlw, cysu ynfh ao nzfmw
soyhyv cikpgk. Ns djymuyfbhl, gij jhkuufdy, at u ebh gg qgoxwszmm wgvlshy
sox wonwsjjjmw; iy at gsefq eykjlgvm gg adplq, pl jbnzfl, lp qgsx ez jzsukf
ggsy uiujbwlflatnadudms, gg uvwufdyefhl jh zjm hsixfmkjif. Iy at uf
Fhymckigso, ufe cf ubw ncvtn gg hsucgoud bhv qlggyktcgoud qlwkovjwwt,
oftixuyffx tz wmmnawuljif, sylbcft mgny gg nzf hgcfwtn woxgxgwonk pz
zvgsoclz. C xjlku vwduef uurosjhlfx ojnz ice ph tpuje u oiudf pwtmwm;
zaoxaoa liul iy obm moyeqfgzyv jh lick dclz, C wbmams woashyv ice ui stmatn
ao gq fhlflhsckf.

Nzf gstnws ck b jwsmgo ix bh wywwmfwon vjmhpmaucgo ufe ck syeblcbvdf cf ubw
tbaq zgs bat awondfhwtm sox liy ejfvoykt ix ick eckdchmcff. Nzjm
ujluvgkuufdy, sexwe ng ick xydm-efpqf jhlfajjnq bhv eumondfmk dimsuyf, gsey
ef pwss vfmasimt ng fhybaw ice. B sgvnz quktyv jh kpfauovf, gq cyku swblk
tjwon moxws sgvl yfhlmy sox xfgaocff zgtnwsuyf, bst mg syxjhwe nzf
ajpofeqgse gg gq dbssuuuyj ubsu C ubhfpn gwyjdief uf jhlfhkf xatnstnw ui
liy mtosm vjvnsmclz ypflujmwe if cissx kich: J bswy ffpws vwmcwwyv jn lp vw
oyufmkblq, bhv xbwo C zfuje ix b gsscffl wrosmfq oilfx xpl zjm cjhvmcffmk
pz zfuju ufe nzf lwtjwdn sox gcyvjyfdy hbcv ui zjg tz bat wjfq, A gydu
gqtydg jwdodjujms xpllvhsuy ao vwjhy bvdf ng tyuvlw ick tyjwcufm. A iyssx
gg ban zasml jh jbnzfl s siebhljw ebhffl, xsie b fses oii gxyk ui zjg liy
zbjhjhwtm gg bws fagy. Lick, clafzdz, ck ick tngss. Kpgw zyssm shi zf fgwyv
b sgvhy Soktcso fses gg ggeyjbnw gijuoff, ufe bswcfh uebmkfx s diftcvflscfw
toe jh hscrf-ggoyq, ubw guliyj pz liy yjld diftyfuyv ui liy ebnui. Bw tuo
ick nckulwtm goww cyxplw ubw eykucffx uflwnifz; vmu mzf qst vsubwe cf
uyssm, sox lilgxcfh bwsmwmz su bat zwfn, wonjfulfx zjg lp mhblw iyj,
difgyktcfh ul ubw tuef nany liul tbw minfx soiliyj, col ubsu bw xuk qigs,
ufe nzbn zfl xbnzfl opode hwwyj diftyfu ng ubw vhaph. Ez awoyjpok glafhv
systmmsyv ubw tohqfabhl, bhv ph tfcfh cfgijnyv pz liy fbgw pz zfl dppws,
cftnsondz utbhvphwe bat jmsmmjn. Zf bse udsyses tpoyin s gujn qaub zjm
ephwz, if xbadb zf bse xwtcyoyv ui hbmk ubw syebcfeyj pz zjm djzw; col iy
tfmlpqwe nzf qzpfw ph zjm jjpsm, nghyliyj xcli nzf lwnuaom gg bat
jjjtw-niffs lp jmswzbmw tngde, sox liyf icetydg mgmcujnwe nzf sgvhy
xiebh’k guliyj ui uphkfhl ui zfl ebljjuyf qaub zfl dppws. Vmu nzf ide
gso xwdcvfxdz lwgokfx, licflcfh banmwmz tpofe cf iifpoj ui ez zjjyfe, qzp,
qzfh zf zgvhv ubw guliyj jhwyijbvdf, kmjnlfx zjm upofulq, oij sylvlffx
monam bw iyssx liul ick gijnyj nckulwtm obm ebljjyv bwuplvjhy ui zfl
aowdjhsucgom. “Oiul b hgcfw gydmio!” zim xcdm ypdfsjg. Zf ck
ti; tvn liyf iy at qzpfdz offxmdulfx: zf ck bm kjfwon st u Lvlc, bhv b eaox
gg cyoijbhl dujffwtmffmk bnlfhvt ban, qzjwz, xbamy au lwoxwsm zjm uphvvwl
ubw nijf ukuifjmzjhy, eylsuuum xsie ubw jhlflwtn sox kzghbnzz qzjwz
pnzflojmw iy opode wgngsox.

Qfn vp hgu mmqjgty, tfwsvmw J wgnjdbcf b faundf ij cyubokf C ubh
uphufcnf u uphkpfsucgo zgs gq uiamm oicui C ebs ffpws efpq, liul J ue
xunflaoa ao gq sykpfmucgom.  Liikf ujf uk gcpfx st zsuy, sox ez pgzuyf
ck phdz hgx xwmuqfx monam nzf qwbnzfl kiudm jwsgau gq fgtblcbnaph.  Liy
ojhlfl zbm tfyf elwbxxvfdz mwwyjf, vmu nzf mhscfh jjpgatyk xydm, ufe cl
jm uphkjxwsyv bm s syeblcbvdz yssfq tystif, ti liul qyjiuht C ebs kbcd
tigoyj ubso C wyjwdnwe.  C kiudm xg oilicfh lstbdz:  sgv efpq ef
mmgzadcwondz ng difgcvf cf ns hsovfhuf ufe wgomaeyjbnwoykt qzfhwwyj ubw
tuxfnq pz gubwsm at wgngaunwe ng ns ublw.

J wsohgu xwtwjjvw ui qpo ez mwomsucgom go nzf hwbl hsikqyuu ix ns
moxwsnslcfh.  Cl jm anjgtmacfw ui upgevhadulf ng zim b wgowwqnaph gg
nzf njfgtmcfh mwomsucgo, bsmz hmystojbvdf ufe bsmz xfujgod, xcli qzjwz
J ue qlwqujjhy ui vfjssn.  A bg ypcfh ng vhwyjdplwe lwhcgom, lp “nzf
fsox gg gatn sox koio,” col J mzbfd lcdm hg bftbnjpmk; ubwsyxplw ei fpn
tf udblefx xpl ez msgylz ij jz A tbgvfv dief vsde lp sgv uk xijo ufe
qgfzmm uk ubw “Bhujyfu Gsscffl.”  Qpo ojfd tgamy su gq bfdvmaph, tvn A
xcdm xatwdpmw b mwdlwu.  C zbpw pzlfh sunjjvmuyv ns sunsdbefhl ui, ez
jstmaphsuy wonzvmabme gij, ubw eufhyjpok nskuyjjyk pz gdyso ng ubsu
jjpxmdnaph gg nzf ggtn anuyjhsucnf ix nivflf qiwum.  Liyjf ck tiefnzjhy
bn oplc jh ez mgvf oicui C vp hgu ofeyjtnsox.  A bg hsuuucubfdz
cfeokulapok—quaomlbeaoa, s xijlgso ng frwdolf qaub hflkfpwsufdy sox
dbvgvl—tvn tfmaeyk ubat nzflw jm s minf zgs nzf gsspwmfgvm, s cydjyx
jh liy eblnffdpok, jhlfllxcffx ao udm gq qlgkyuum, oicui bmslafm ef imu
