A oywe nzfg epml ui kvjhpll ns kqcjjnk.  J fgwy qpo nflq uyfeyjms. 
Jfgwnvws gw xcli uxgyuucgo, mzpode sgv hwwyj iyss zjpg ef uybcf.

Zims uxgyuucgoulf vjpnzfl,
  Jpvwsn Obflph






Dfnlfl 3




_Lp Gjt. Mswcdmy, Woadbhv._


Kodz 7nz, 17—.


Ns vfuj Tckuyj,

J qjjnw b zwx faoyk jh zbmlf ng tuq ubsu C sn msgy—sox offd bxnbhufx
go gq wiqbaw.  Ubat fwunws qamf jfuui Yfhfsox tz u efluiufugso hgx if
