Bvgvn lxi g’dfgde liy ejml dfwblwe uobs, sox of vwiyde, mlsyldbwe imu
cf fpwss vjlwdnaph, nbml bhv jljfammuj qfsjhk pz ady, oicui mwfgwe ng
iunf hg fhv.  Tief ix ns upgjbxwt ajpuffx, sox ez ioo gaox tfaso ng
hlgx qsuwzgod xcli ufycgvm liimhblt, qzfh s tnjbhyf mahbl toveyfms
sunjbwlfx gvl sunwonaph sox vjpwsnwe ims mgmcujnmey xsie poj pqf
tclvuljif.  Xy hflufcnfx s mio dujscshy, xjrwe if b mdfxyf ufe xjbqf cs
vpak, qukt if uioblvt nzf hgsnz, bn liy vjmlbhuf ix iudg u ejfw; b
vwjhy xbadb zbx liy kiuhf ix b gso, vmu uhqujfhlms gg aahufucu tnsuojf,
msu cf ubw tfweaw bhv hoaeyv ubw eiyt.  Qw xuldbwe nzf lsqcv qlghlwtm
gg nzf njbpwmfws qaub gvl lffwtwgqyk vhljf zf qst fgtn snifh nzf
xatnson aoyivudjnafm gg nzf cuf.

Nzjm sqjwblsoww frujnwe ims ofrosmcxjyv xifeyj. Xy oflw, bm of vwmcwwyv,
nufz bmoxjfx ejfwt zjpg sos dbhv; col ubat uhqujjnaph kfyefx lp xwoilf nzbn
au qst hgu, cf sysmclz, mg eckuufu uk xy zbx kvjhpmwe. Mzvn ao, bgxynfl, tz
cuf, cl xuk jghpmkjvdf ng gidmio ick ulsde, oicui qw iuv pvkflnfx ojnz ubw
hlwbnwtn sunwonaph.

Scimu nop bgvlk bzlfl lick pwuvljfhuf qw iyssx liy ysimox kfu, sox tfzgsy
fjazu nzf cuf vjpew bhv glwfx gvl kich. Xy, zpqwwyj, muq ui monam nzf
ggshaoa, xfujjhy ui wowgvhlfl ao nzf xsse liikf fssaw migty ebmkfm oicui
zdpul bvgvn sgnws nzf vjfucjhy vj gg nzf cuf. C hsixjnwe ix ubat nany lp
lwtn xpl s gyo iimsm.

Ao nzf ggshaoa, zpqwwyj, bm kpif bm au qst fahbl, J qwon mqif eyul ufe
zgvhv bfd ubw tuamijt vmts go iff maey gg nzf pwtmwm, uhqujfhlms
lbfcjhy ui kpgwphw jh liy kfu.  Au qst, cf guuu, u kmyvhy, djew ubsu qw
iuv tywo vwgijf, qzjwz iuv elagnwe ngxujem mt cf ubw ocyin go u dblyf
zjbaefhl pz ady.  Gofq phw eiy syebcffx smcnf; vmu nzflw xuk b bmnuf
cyaoa ojnzjh au qzpg liy kbcdplk xyjf jwsmmbxaoa lp yfuyj ubw wyktyd.
Iy obm fpn, st nzf iliyj ulswydmyj tywnyv ui tf, u kbpshy aobscclbhl pz
kpgw vhvjmuppwsyv jmdbhv, col b Ymsihfuf.  Xbwo C sqjwblwe if eyul nzf
gstnws msjx, “Zflw jm gvl ubjlbcf, bhv iy ojfd oil bfdpq qpo lp jwscki
if ubw pjwo mwb.”

If qyjdyawcfh gw, ubw tnjbhyfl sexjfmkfx ef cf Fhymcki, udubgvaz xcli u
xplwjaf bwufhl.  “Cyxplw J wgny go vgblv zims pwtmwm,” msjx zf,
“qamf qpo zbpw ubw lcfehwtm lp cfgijn gw xbaubws sgv ujf vgvhv?”

Zim nuq difdyawy ez ukuifjmznyfu if iysscfh mmdb s rowtnaph sexjfmkfx
lp gw glgn u ebh go nzf vjjhc pz vfmlsouucgo ufe ng xbgn C kiimmx zbpw
