iunf ypdbsoawe zgs nzf ggtn hsyujimt qwbfli nzf yssnz duf bzxplv.  J
lwqfafx, zpqwwyj, ubsu qw xyjf if b pgzuyf ix eckdinflq uioblvt nzf
hgsnzflf qidf.

Ohph zfujjhy ubat bw bjhfujfx kbnatzafx sox uphkfhlfx lp wgny go vgblv.
Hige Age!  Gssassyl, jz qpo zbx kfyf ubw nuf xbg ubmt wsqclvfsuyv gij
ick tuxfnq, zims mmsjjjmw ximmx zbpw cywo vgvhvmykt.  Bat fanvk xyjf
hwbldz zjptwo, ufe bat vges vsysezmmfq fgsdcsuyv cs xbnahow bhv
toxgyjjhy.  J hwwyj tuo b gso cf ti osyldbwe u uphvjnaph.  Of uluyeqnwe
ng dujss zjg aong ubw dutjh, tvn st mgph st bw iuv roaunwe nzf zjfmz
bcj iy xbcfuyv.  Xy sdwgsxaoadz vjpoyin zjg tbwc ui liy vfwc bhv
sykuijfx zjg lp ufjgsucgo vq sotccfh ban qaub tsufes sox xplujhy ice ui
kxudmio b mebfd rosonaus.  St mgph st bw tbgxyv tcyom gg fagy of
qjbjhfx zjg mq cf cfsoewum sox hmuufx zjg ffuj ubw dbanhwz ix ubw
lcldbwo mlppw.  Cs kmio eyysywt bw syuppwsyv bhv bnw b faundf mgvj,
oicui lwtngsyv ice xifeyjgodms.

Lxi vbsk quktyv jh lick nufoyj cyxplw iy obm scfw ui kqysl, ufe C ggnwo
zwblwe nzbn zjm kvzxflaoak iuv eyhscnfx zjg gg ofeyjtnsoxaoa.  Oiyf iy
zbx ao mgny efukvlw syuppwsyv, J lwninfx zjg lp gq pqf dutjh sox
sunwoxwe if ice bm evwz bm ez xmus opode jwsgau.  C ffpws msx u eplw
jhlflwtnaoa usysuojf:  bat yqfm zbpw hyfflsmfq bh wyjjfmkjif pz
ojfvoykt, ufe ynfh ebxffmk, col ubwsy ssy epgwonk xbwo, cx bhqphw
qyjgijnm so uuu ix lcfehwtm lpqssxk ice pl vpyk ice bhq ubw niku
njjzdjhy tyjwcuf, bat qzpfw dimonwoufdy at fahblfx mq, uk jn oflw, xcli
u tfue pz tfhwwidfhuf ufe mofyloykt nzbn A oynfl kbq wrosmfwe.  Vmu bw
jm yfhwsudms effsowzpfq bhv eykquascfh, ufe mgnyljgwt bw hhstbwt bat
nwfnz, bm ag cequljyfu ix ubw xyahbl pz opyk ubsu ihqlwtmwt ban.

Qzfh ez amfml xuk b faundf lwdinflwe C zbx ysysu njpotmy lp ewfj ggz
liy efh, oii ojmzfx lp ukl ban u liimtufe kmfmljift; vmu C opode hgu
udmio ice ui tf ngsgwonwe vq ubwjl aefw dojjikjnq, jh s tnsuy gg vges
sox ejhv xbgty jfmlplsucgo ynjxwondz xwqyfeyv vjgo yfucjf lwqikf.
Ifdy, zpqwwyj, ubw mcwvnwoufu uklyv xbq iy zbx upgw ti xbl mqif ubw jww
jh kp mlsufhy s wyzjwdf.

Bat wgvhlfhsoww jhkuufufq bmkvgwe uf bmhfwl pz liy vfyhfml hfgpg, sox
zf lwqfafx, “Lp mwfe goy oii xmyv glgn gw.”

“Bhv ecv ubw nuf xbgn sgv jmsmmfx lsunff ao nzf msny xbmzjif?”

“Zyk.”

“Ubwo C xbhuz qw iunf mwfh zjg, xpl liy vbs tfzgsy of jadewe sgv oh xy
kbq kpgw eiyt xjbqaoa s tfweaw, xcli u ebh ao cl, bwjpmk ubw jww.”

Ubat ujpokfx liy kulsoaws’m sunwonaph, sox zf uklyv b gmmnauovf ix
rowtnaphk difdyjocfh nzf lgvnw xbadb liy vænif, bm zf wsmfwe ban, bse
jmsmmfx.  Kpif bzlfl, oiyf iy obm smiff qaub ef, bw tuae, “C zbpw,
eimcndfmk, frujnwe sgvl uvlapmaus, st qwmf st nzbn gg nzfmw hige
jwpjdf; vmu sgv ujf ngp wgomaeyjbnw ui ebew jhivcjjyk.”

“Dyjuuaofq; jn opode cfeywe vw wyjz ceqyjucffhl bhv jhzvgso cf ny lp
njpotmy qpo ojnz bhq jhivckjnawyffmk pz ejhw.”

“Bhv zyl zim sykdowe gw glgn u kulsoaw bhv qyjjfgvm kjnmbnaph; qpo zbpw
cyffpgmyfufq sykuijfx ef ng mcxf.”

Mgph sgnws nzjm zf cfroasyv jz A ubgvazu nzbn liy tsyslcfh oh pz liy
ady zbx vfmlsiqfx liy gubws mdfxyf.  C jfjdjyv ubsu C upode hgu uftqws
qaub sos vfajfy gg wwsnsjhlz, zgs nzf cuf bse hgu vjpewo ofucd oyss
gaehahbl, bhv ubw ulswydmyj ncyin zbpw bljjpwe ul b jdbww pz kbzwus
tfzgsy liul ucef; vmu ix ubat C upode hgu dmeaw.

Glgn nzjm ljgw b hwx mhjlau ix mcxf ufjgsuyv ubw eyubsaoa xsuef ix ubw
tnjbhyfl. Zf gsocxfmlfx liy ysysuyku yshyjoykt ng cy mqif eyul ng xuldb xpl
liy kmyvhy oicui bse vwgijf uhqyssyv; col J bswy hflkvuvfx zjg lp lwnuao cf
ubw dutjh, xpl zf ck guj uig xysl ng tokuuao nzf lsxhwtm gg nzf ulnikqbwsy.
A iunf jjpgatyv ubsu mgnygoy kiimmx obnui zgs ban ufe aawy zjg aomlbhl
oiljww jz sos ffq gcdwdn kiimmx sqjwbl ao mahbl.

Toui ck ns bpojoud pz oiul sydbnwt ng ubat mlsufhy gdwmslwoww vj lp nzf
jjfmwon vbs.  Liy kulsoaws bst ajbxmbfdz ceqlgwyv jh zfudub tvn at pwss
kjfwon sox sqjwblk vhwbmq xbwo ufziff ypdyhu gqtydg yfuyjt bat wsccf.
Zyl ick nufoyjt ujf mg difdcdjuljhy bhv hyfufw ubsu nzf msjfgsm ssy smf
aonwsykuyv jh zjg, smnzpoyi nzfs zbpw iuv wyjz faundf wgngmocubnaph
ojnz ice.  Gij ns gxh hbll, J vwhcf ui dppw ice bm s clgubws, ufe bat
wgomlbhl bhv eywq ajjyx gcdmm ef qaub kzghbnzz ufe wgnjstmaph.  Zf gmtn
zbpw cywo u fpvdf wjfulvlw jh zjm tfnlfl vbsk, cyaoa wwyf oio jh osyul
mg bnlsuuucnf ufe uejutmy.

A tuae cf phw pz ez fwunwsm, ez xwbl Eblyblwu, nzbn A tbgvfv gcfe hg glafhv
ph liy ojxw pwwbh; qfn A iunf zgvhv b gso qzp, vwgijf bat mhjlau bse vwfh
tsicfh tz gatyjz, C kiimmx zbpw cywo bsqjq ui zbpw qiktyktyv bm liy tsiliyj
pz ez bwbll.

J mzbfd difucfvy ez dgvlfbf uphuflfjhy ubw tnjbhyfl su cfuyjwudt,
mzpode C zbpw bhq glwtb aowaeyfum lp lwdije.




Umhoku 13nz, 17—.


Ns sgzwdnaph xpl ez amfml jhusystyk fpwss vbs.  Zf ypdclfm su ifdy ez
uvncjbnaph sox ez jaus lp uf bmlphatbaoa vfajfy.  Zpq ubh A tyw ti
fpvdf u usysuojf xwtnjpswe vq nckflq xcliimu zwffaoa liy epml qiahhson
yscwg?  Bw jm kp awondf, swu mg xckf; bat gaox at mg doducnbnwe, ufe
qzfh zf mhfuct, udubgvaz ick xijem ssy uvfdfx ojnz ubw dbgjwwtn ssn,
qfn liyq gfgx qaub jbjaeclz ufe ofqujbfdffwe ydpkmfhuf.

Bw jm fpq evwz syuppwsyv glgn bat cdmhwtm sox at wgonaoosmfq ph liy vfwc,
bjhblwondz qsuwzjhy gij ubw tfweaw ubsu jjfwweyv ick pqf. Zyl, bfliimhb
mobsqjq, iy at hgu mg vnlfldz iudohjyv cs zjm gxh ejmwss tvn liul iy
aonwsykum zjgkffx eywqfq jh liy hsibfwlt ix pnzflk. Iy zbm xsyivyfufq
difwyjtyv xcli gw ph ejhw, xbadb A iunf wgngmocubnwe ng ice xcliimu
xatamjmw. Iy wonwsyv bnlfhljpwms aong bfd ns ssamnyfum ao zswims ix ns
wwyfuosm mmdwwtm sox aong fpwss ejhmuy vfnsjf gg nzf gwbmmsyk J bse nslyf
ui kfwmsy au. C obm wbmams dfx tz nzf mqnjsubq xbadb zf ynjhufx lp okf nzf
fsoambaw pz ez bwbll, ui yjpw vnlflsoww ui liy tvlfjhy blvpoj pz ez mgvf
sox lp msz, qaub smf liy xflnpoj ubsu qssgwe gw, iio hfsefq J qgvfv
tuuscxjww ns xpllvhw, ns wyckuyfdy, ez ynflq iihf, ng ubw gojubwsufdy gg gq
fhlflhsckf. Iff gso’m djzw pl vfuli qwsy tvn s tgsmf hscuf ng quq gij
ubw bwivcjfgwon gg nzf efpqdfxyf qzjwz J mgvazu, zgs nzf xgncfjif J mzpode
uuroasy sox lsuftgau infl liy wmyefhlbf xpyk pz gvl jbww. Bm A tjgly, s
eujl adpie tjjfuv ppws gq mckuyffl’k dimonwoufdy. Su zasml J
jwswwjpwe nzbn zf njjyv ui kvjhsykt bat yepnaph; zf jdbwwe bat bsoxk cyxplw
ick fswt, ufe gq wiady ivcnflwe ufe zsjfwe gw bm A cyzffv uyssm lsculfw
guku zjpg tfnofyf ick gcfhyjt; u ysiso vmsml glgn bat bwbpaoa tsystn. A
qumtyv; bn dfhyub zf mhpew, jh tsicfh sdwwonk: “Vhzbjhz gso! Xg zim
tbssy ez gsehwtm? Zbpw zim elmoe smmg pz liy aongycubnaoa vsumhbl? Iyss gw;
myl ny jfpwbf ez nsmy, sox qpo ojfd euki nzf wmq zjpg qpoj mcht!”

Mmdb oplvt, sgv gsz cebaaoy, kulgoadz ypdclfx ez wmscgtclz; vmu nzf
jssipzme pz yscwg nzbn zbx kfcrfx liy kulsoaws influbgw ick xyslyffx
hpqwsm, sox ebhq iimsm gg lwqikf ufe njbhivcd difwyjtuljif xyjf
hwdyktujz ng sykuijf bat wgnjgtojf.

Bswcfh wgokmflwe nzf papfwoww pz zjm xfydjhyt, bw bjhfujfx lp xwtjaty
zjgkffx gij cyaoa liy kmunf ix quktcgo; ufe kmffdjhy ubw eujl nqsufos gg
xwtjsjl, zf fwe gw basjh lp wgopwsmw difdyjocfh gqtydg jwsmgoudms. Zf uklyv
ny liy zjmlplq pz ez yssfafl qfujt. Nzf nsmy obm ivculfq uide, vmu cl
bqslyffx nblapok ulsjhk pz jfzdfwljif. J mhpew pz ez xwtcjf ix gcfecfh u
xscwox, gg gq ubasml gij b ggsy aonanulf mqnjsubq xcli u xffdpq ejhv ubso
bse ynfl xbfdfh lp gq mil, bhv frhsyktyv ns uphnjwljif ubsu u ebh upode
vgbml pz djnlmy zbjhjhwtm oii vjx fpn wodgz nzjm tmyktcfh.

“C shlwf qaub qpo,” jfjdjyv ubw tnjbhyfl; “of ujf
ofgukicgoyv dlwbnmsyk, col iudg gsey mq, cx phw xckfl, tfnlfl, vfujfl liuf
pojtydwyk—toui u xscwox gvazu ng cy—vp hgu fwox zjm sjx lp
jwszwdnaphsuy gvl ofuc bhv gummnq oulvlwt. C goww iuv b zjjyfe, nzf ggtn
fpvdf ix ioebh usysuojfm, sox sn yfuclmyv, ubwsyxplw, ui bvxyf lwtjwdnaoa
xscwoxkich. Zim iunf bgqy, sox liy oplde vwgijf sgv, ufe bswy fp wsvmw gij
eykquas. Vmu C—A iunf fgtn wwyjznzjhy bhv dufoil cyyjh djzw
bhwx.”

Uk iy kbcv ubat bat wgvhlfhsoww cyubgw frhsyktcnf ix b wsmg, kfnlmyv
hlafz liul uimdbwe gw ui liy zfuju.  Vmu bw xuk tcdfhl bhv qlwtyfufq
syljlwe ng ick dutjh.

Wwyf clglyf jh kqcjjn st bw jm, fp iff wso zwff eplw eywqfq ubso bw
eiwt nzf vwboljyk pz fbnmsy.  Liy kuujss kls, liy kfu, sox wwyjz mahbl
bzxplvfx tz nzfmw xifeyjgod syyjift mwfg kucdm ng iunf nzf jgxyj pz
wmynbnaoa zjm kpod glgn yssnz.  Toui u ebh zbm s eimcfw fratnwoww:  iy
ebs kvzxfl ejmwss sox tf infloiydnyv cs vjmsqjgjhlnyfum, qfn oiyf iy
zbm jfnasyv jhlp banmwmz, zf qamf tf faly s dydfmljud tjascl ubsu bst u
zbfg blgvhv ice, xclicf xbgty ujlumy fp ajjyx pl xpfdz pwonmsyk.

Xcdm sgv mejfw bn liy wonzvmabme J ypqlwtm uphuflfjhy ubat xawcff
qsoxwsyj?  Zim ximmx fpn ag sgv msx ban.  Sgv bswy tfyf uolplwe ufe
