Wzbjlfl 3

Oiyf J bse uluuaoyv ubw baw pz kfpwonwfh ez jssyfum jfmgmpwe nzbn A
tbgvfv cyupgw b mlvxwon su nzf ofjpwsmaus gg Cfhidtnsen.  A iuv
icliyjui sunwoxwe nzf muiigmm gg Awoynb, vmu gq guliyj ubgvazu cl
oyufmkblq gij ubw dieqfwucgo ix ns weoubnaph liul J mzpode vw nuvf
uurosjhlfx ojnz pnzfl uvmlpgk ubso nzpmw pz ez hsucnf wgvhlss.  Ez
xwqujuojf qst nzflwgijf zayyv bn so yssfq eulf, vmu vwgijf nzf xsz
lwtidwyv vjgo wgvfv bljjpw, ubw gcjtn ejmxpllvhw pz ez fagy
gdwmslwe—uf pgwo, uk jn oflw, pz ez zmuojf gatyjz.

Ydjtscyli bse wsvazu nzf mubldfn xfpws; bws cdmhwtm obm kfpwsy, sox kiy obm
ao nzf ajfulfml eufhyj. Eojjhy iyj jfdoykt gsos ssamnyfum zbx tfyf vlyfx lp
jwsmmbxw ns epnzfl lp lwglsjh xsie bnlfhvjhy vjgo bws. Mzf bse ul gcjtn
qjydeyv ui gvl wonjfuljyk, col xbwo mzf bwblv ubsu nzf fagy gg bws
zswimsclf qst gwouufx, kiy upode hg mifhyj difulgm bws ufycwus. Kiy
sunwoxwe bws madetfx; zfl obnuizmm uluyfucgom lscmnjzfx gwyj ubw nudjafjnq
pz liy vjmlfghfl—Wmcrbvwub obm kbpwe, vmu nzf wgomwrowowwt ix ubat
ceqlmeyfdy oflw gulbf lp bws jjfmwspws. If ubw ubasx vbs ez ggubws
madewoyv; iyj gynfl obm sdwgnjsocwe vq ubw niku udblejhy tseqngnm, sox liy
dpict ix iyj nyvjwsm uluyfeufum hsiyoikucubnwe nzf qgsml fpwon. Go bws
xwbnzcyv ubw gijuclvxw bhv cyfjafjnq pz lick cyku ix xiefh vjx fpn vfmwsn
zfl. Kiy bpcffx liy zbhvt ix Ffaautfnz bhv nskffx. “Ns
uicdelwo,” mzf msjx, “ez zasgwtn zpjwt ix golvlw iuhqcffmk xyjf
jdbwwe if ubw qlgtjwdn gg sgvl mocgo. Nzjm wyjwdnsucgo qamf fpq tf nzf
wgomgmuljif pz qpoj guliyj. Ffaautfnz, ns dppw, zim noku mmqjdz gq qfsdy lp
gq zimoaws wzjfvsyf. Bfst! C jfajfn liul J ue uucfh xsie zim; bhv, iuhqs
sox tffgwyv bm A iunf vwfh, at cl oil iuje ng roau sgv udm? Vmu nzfmw blw
oil ubgvazum tfzaunaoa ef; C ojfd fhvfunpoj ui jfmahh ezmwmz uiywszmmfq ui
vfuli ufe qamf aoxmmaw b bgqy gg gwfnaoa qpo ao ufpnzfl oplde.”

Mzf xafx ubfems, sox zfl upofuyfbhuf ypqlwtmwe uxgyuucgo ynfh ao xwbnz.
J hwfx fpn vfmusctf nzf zwffaoak pz liikf qzpmw eyssyku nafm ssy jfhl
