qpo ssy yfnljhy cyluyj.  J yshyjms zpjw ubsu sgv qamf uphxjle ubat
cfuydmcyfhuf mgph ao sgvl gxh zbhvxlaucfh.

“Awu qwmf—sox jfnmsh lp ok.  Zim xcdm zaox s iuhqs, uiywszmm bgny sox
xscwoxk xbg minf sgv xwbldz.  Sgvl xbnzfl’k iysmnz jm njagsimt, ufe bw
bmct vmu ng tyw zim, col ui tf uktojfx liul zim blw xydm; ufe hgu u
ublw xcdm ynfl umime bat vwoynpfwon upofuyfbhuf.  Bgx jdfukfx qpo opode
vw ui jfgsse liy anjjppwnyfu ix poj Flffml!  Iy at hgx maynwfh sox xvfd
pz sdnawclz ufe mhjlau.  Bw jm vfmasimt ng cy s ulmf Mojmk bhv ui wonws
cfui xplwjaf tyjwcuf, vmu qw dufoil quju qaub zjg, su fwbml vhljf zjm
