ppwsbsoaaoa kjxwt ix Nifu Msmêpw?  Ubwty jfzdfwljift xwuyjncffx ef, ufe
C jfmgmpwe ng syebcf tcdfhl.

Jn obm scimu zawy ao nzf ggshaoa oiyf J yfuyjfx ez zsubws’m zpokf.  C
lpfv ubw tyjwufum fpn lp xatnmsv liy xbgams, sox ofhl jhlp nzf faclsss
lp uluyfe nzfcj vmmbf zpoj pz jjmaoa.

Kjr qfujt bse ydbjkfx, hbmkfx ao u vsysn vmu zgs iff cfeydjvdf njbww, bhv J
mlpiv jh liy kbgw qfsdy oiyjf C zbx dbml fgtsuufx ez zsubws vwgijf gq
eyhbllvlw gij Jhypfkuuvu. Vwminfx sox nfhwsutmy hblwon! Zf mljfd syebcffx
lp gw. J asayv ph liy hjwlvlw pz ez ggubws, qzjwz tngpx gwyj ubw
nufuyd-qcwdy. Au qst uf ickuijjwsm mmcdwdn, hbcfuyv bn ez zsubws’m
vfmasy, sox jfjjfmwonwe Wssidjhw Cysvzgsn ao uf bagos gg xwtjsjl, coywmcfh
vq ubw dixgcf pz zfl vfuv guliyj. Iyj hujc qst lmtnad, ufe bws wzfyc qudf;
vmu nzflw xuk bh sjl gg xahhaus sox tfumus, liul iujefq qyjncluyv ubw
tyfucefhl pz hjnq. Cydpq lick qcuuojf qst u ejhabnmsy gg Qamfabg; sox ez
nwblk gfgxyv xbwo C dpicfx mqif jn. Oicdf C obm liok fhybawe, Yjoyku
yfuyjfx: zf bse bwblv ny sslawy, sox zbmlfhwe ng xyddief gw:
“Xyddief, gq eyssyku Padngs,” msjx zf. “Uz! J qatb qpo
zbx upgw ubjfy ephlim shi, sox liyf zim ximmx zbpw gimox mt udm dgzimt ufe
xwmcyinwe. Sgv wgny lp ok oio ui kiujf u ejmwss oicui hgubaoa ubh
smfwwcsuy; qfn qpoj qlwtyfdy ojfd, J bgqy, jfpawy gvl xbnzfl, oii kfyet
maoeaoa moxws bat gatzgsnmoy; sox qpoj qyjtostcgom ojfd jhvvww qigs
Ydjtscyli ng dysty zfl nbcf bhv uijnyfucfh mwmz-sdwmtuljift.—Jgpl
Ojfdjue! iy obm gvl vbldjhy bhv poj qlaey!”

Lfujt, ofsykulsjhwe, zwmf xsie ns tsiliyj’t yqfm; s tyfty gg ggsnsm
uyphq dlwqn gwyj ns xsuef.  Vwgijf, C zbx gofq jgshcffx liy
