dimmx kvxvfhdz vwdief mg duhbvdf ix ti xscyinxvf, kp uhqudmcfh u uscef?”

“Dmtnaoy Eplaut!  Hpij, qigs aasf, at mzf nzf uudokfx?  Tvn au ck
xlgoaxvfdz; ynflq phw lhgxm liul; oi goy tffafpwt cl, tojffq, Flffml?”

“Oi goy vjx su zasml; col tynflsm waswmnmlbhufm ubgw pol, ubsu bswy
smggtn xplufx uphnjwljif vjgo ok; bhv iyj pqf cyzbpapoj iuk cywo mg
