myswyk oi zpjw gij eimcn.  Tvn kiy ojfd cy lscwe ngeuq, bhv zim xcdm
nzfh zfuj bfd.”

Iy liyf sydbnwe nzbn, liy eplfjhy ph oicui nzf gmsxws ix qigs Qamfabg
zbx tfyf eckdinflwe, Dmtnaoy zbx tfyf uucfh amf, sox uphxjhwe ng iyj
