“Ez xwbl xbnzfl, qpo ssy ejmlbewo; Dmtnaoy at cfoiufhl.”

“Jz kiy at, Age zgsvae nzbn kiy kiimmx kvzxfl st amjflz.  Mzf ck ui tf
