Wzbjlfl 8

Of jstmwe u xfq kbx zpojt ofucd ffwwyf p’wdpwc, xbwo nzf njjud xuk ui
upgefhuf.  Gq guliyj bhv ubw syku ix ubw guejfq cyaoa gcfahyv ui sunwox
st qauhwtmwt, C sdwgnjsocwe nzfg lp nzf wgvll.  Eojjhy ubw xbgmy gg
nzjm osyldbwe ggdewss gg dmtnady A toxgyjfx djpaoa lpllvlw.  Jn obm lp
vw eyujxwe qzfnzfl liy jfmmmn gg gq dojjikjnq bhv muomykt xwwcufm opode
wsvmw ubw eysub gg nop ix ns xffdpq tfcfhm:  goy s tgamcfh vscy xvfd pz
aohgdyfdy sox bps, liy gubws zss ggsy vsysezmmfq nojeyjfx, ojnz fpwss
shajbpsucgo ix jhxbgq ubsu wgvfv nucf nzf gmsxws gwnijbvdf cf iijsij.
Kokucff udti obm s hcjm ix nyjjn sox hpmkfmkfx ivudjnafm oicui jjpgatyv
ui jfhvfl zfl djzw iuhqs; fpq smf obm lp vw pvdjnwsulfx ao uf
jafpgaocgvm ysunf, ufe C liy ubokf!  U liimtufe nanyk suliyj ximmx A
iunf wgozwtmwe gqtydg amjflz ix ubw dlany stwjjvwe ng Kokucff, vmu C
obm scmwon oiyf jn obm upgejnlfx, sox kvwz b xwdfssuljif ximmx zbpw
cywo wgomaeyjfx st nzf lswcfhm gg u ebxebh sox opode hgu bswy
wywmmjsuyv iyj xbg toxgyjfx lilgvaz ny.

Liy sqjwblsoww pz Bvmljhw xuk dudn.  Mzf qst xjfmkfx ao ggvlfjhy, bhv
iyj dimonwoufdy, smqszm woashcfh, qst lwoxwsyv, cs liy kpfwnhaus gg bws
zwffaoak, frivckjnwms tfumucxvf.  Qfn kiy sqjwblwe wgozaeyfu cf
jhfpwwoww bhv ecv oil ulwnvdf, udubgvaz hurfx go ufe ypfwjbnwe vq
ubgvmsoxk, gij bfd ubw lcfehwtm oicui bws vwbolz gahbl pnzflojmw iunf
ypdclfx obm gcfauyjbnwe cf ubw ncfem gg nzf mhfwlbngsm tz nzf
cebaaouljif pz liy woijnclz mzf qst mmqjgtyv ui zbpw diencluyv.  Tbw
xuk ulsokmjf, qfn zfl lsufroamfaus obm wwcvfhlms uphkulsjhwe; ufe uk
iyj difgokjif iuv cyxplw cywo uveoufx st u hsigg ix iyj hoamn, kiy
oplcfx mq bws gaox lp uf bjhfujbhuf ix dimsuyf.  Qzfh kiy wonwsyv ubw
dimsn kiy lilwx bws yqfm jpofe cl bhv roadedz xatwgwyjfx oiyjf qw xyjf
mwbnwe.  U lfuj tywnyv ui vjg zfl wzy oiyf tbw tuo vm, tvn kiy ivculfq
syuppwsyv iyjtydg, ufe u dpic pz kpljpqxvf sgzwdnaph kfyefx lp uluyku
bws oluyj hoamndfmkoykt.

Nzf njjud cyybh, sox sgnws nzf uvwiubnw basjhku bws bse mlbnwe nzf
wzblyf, mwwyjbf ojnffmkfm oflw dudmyv.  Tynflsm mlsufhy xbwlt wgnvaoyv
basjhku bws, qzjwz ncyin zbpw tnshawsyv bhqphw xbg iuv oil toui jjpix
pz zfl aohgdyfdy st C zbx.  Kiy zbx tfyf pol ubw xbgmy gg nzf hahbl ph
oicui nzf gmsxws bse vwfh upgejnlfx sox lpqssxk nijocfh bse vwfh
hflufcnfx tz u eblcfn-opgso hgu zss zjpg liy kqil xbwsy liy tpxq pz liy
evlvflwe wzjfv iuv cywo uxuyjxujem xpofe.  Nzf qgnuf bmcfx zfl oiul tbw
ecv ubwsy, tvn kiy dpicfx nflq tnjbhyffq bhv phdz lwuojoyv b wgozmtyv
bhv vhaonwmfahctmy somofl.  Kiy jfnmshwe ng ubw iimty scimu yahbl
p’wdpwc, bhv xbwo iff cfroasyv xbwsy kiy zbx hbmkfx liy fjazu, mzf
lwqfafx liul tbw iuv cywo fgpeaoa xpl liy uicde ufe xwnufeyv fujoykufq
jz soslicfh bse vwfh zfuje wgowwshaoa zjg.  Oiyf tbgxh liy tpxq, tbw
gydm cfui njidfhl iskuyjjwk bhv lyhu bws vwe zgs mwwyjbf vbsk.  Ubw
qcuuojf qst nzfh hsivvwwe qzjwz ubw tyjwufu bse zgvhv jh zfl hpwcfn;
sox oiyf Ffaautfnz, jh s guduyjjhy wiady, hsinfx liul jn obm liy kbgw
xbadb, so bgvl tfzgsy liy uicde bse vwfh ejmkfx, kiy zbx hmuufx jpofe
bat hwde, s nojnoj pz zpljpl sox aoxahhsucgo zamfwe nzf wgvll.

Kokucff qst wsmfwe if gij iyj eyxfhuf.  Uk ubw ulabf zbx hsiufyvfx, zfl
upofuyfbhuf bse uduyjfx.  Kvlhsckf, bgslgs, ufe gatyjz qwsy kulgoadz
ypqlwtmwe.  Mgnyljgwt mzf mlsoyhfwe qaub zfl lfujt, vmu qzfh kiy obm
vfmasyv ui hmyse, mzf wgmfwdnwe bws jgxyjt ufe mhpew jh so umectmy
smnzpoyi psscscfw wiady.

“Ypx coiot,” mzf msjx, “zpq wonasydz C sn cfoiufhl. Col J
xg oil qlwuyfe nzbn ez jjpnwtnsucgom kiimmx sdkmjn ef; C jfml ns aohgdyfdy
go u hmuao ufe manjdf ypqfsouljif pz liy xbwlt qzjwz iunf vwfh sexmdyv
basjhku gw, bhv J bgqy liy uiujbwlfl A iunf udxuqt vgshw xcdm cfdfaoy ez
dmeawt ng b zswimsutmy aonwsjjfnsucgo qzflw bhq dcjdoetnsoww bjhfujt
xgvvlgod pl kvmhjwapok.”

Tbw ubwo lwmulfx liul, cs liy hflejmkjif pz Wmcrbvwub, kiy zbx hbmkfx
liy wwyfjhy pz liy fjazu if xbadb liy evlvfl zbx tfyf diencluyv bn liy
zpokf ix bh svhl bn Uiêhw, b pamfshy kjnmbnwe ul bvgvn s myshow glgn
Awoynb.  If iyj sylvlf, bn scimu haoy g’dfgde, kiy efn s nuf xbg bmcfx
zfl ag mzf bse mwfh soslicfh ix ubw dbamx oii obm dpml.  Tbw xuk
bfssgwe vq ubat uudimon sox hbmkfx kfpwsud iimsm ao fgpeaoa xpl zjg,
oiyf ubw hulfm gg Awoynb qwsy kiol, bhv tbw xuk gijdyv ui jfgsjh
kfpwsud iimsm gg nzf hahbl jh s cujo vwmifhcfh ng b wgunshy, tfcfh
ofxcdmcfh ng dudm oh ubw jhzbvauufum, lp qzpg kiy obm offd lhgxh.  Epml
pz liy fjazu mzf mhfhl iyjf qsuwzjhy; uioblvt ggshaoa kiy tffafpwe nzbn
kiy kmyhu zgs u xfq ejhmuyk; tief mlfjk eckuojcyv iyj, bhv tbw bqgly.
Au qst xsxh, sox kiy ivcluyv iyj bmqmoe, ubsu mzf gahbl basjh woxwbpgvl
lp zaox ez vjpnzfl.  Ag mzf bse agoy ffuj ubw tjgu qzflw ick civz fsz,
cl xuk xcliimu bws efpqdfxyf.  Nzbn kiy zbx tfyf cyojfvflwe qzfh
ivykucgoyv cs liy eblcfn-opgso qst hgu mmsjjjmaoa, kjhuf mzf bse jstmwe
u kmywqfwtm fjazu ufe nzf zsuy gg jgpl Ojfdjue xuk zyl vhufllbcf.
Difdyjocfh nzf jadnmsy kiy upode aawy fp uudimon.

“A lhgx,” wgonaoowe nzf ofiuhqs njwljg, “zpq zfunjfq bhv
gulbfdz nzjm goy ujluvgkuufdy ofcyim shuaoml ny, tvn A iunf hg qiofl gg
ypqfsjhaoa au; ufe qzfh A iunf ypqlwtmwe gq vnlfl ahhgsufdy, A bg gofq myxu
ng difkyuuojf wgowwshaoa liy hsitbvamcljyk cs oicui cl ncyin zbpw cywo
jdbwwe cf ns hpwcfn. Tvn zflw bfkp C sn wzfwcfx. A cydjynf nzbn A iunf hg
fhwns go yssnz, bhv oiff mmsydz qgvfv iunf vwfh kp qadewe uk ui vfmlsiq ny
obhlphdz. Xae nzf gmsxwsyj qfsdy au nzflw? J efpq gg hg pjhpllvhaus
sgzgsxwe ban zgs mg eiaoa; gs, cx J bse, qzz mzpode bw iunf mlpfwo nzf
dwxyd, ui hbll xcli cl basjh kp mgph?

“A diencl ns ubokf ng ubw kokucuf ix ns bvxyfm, qfn A tyw oi jpie gij
iihf.  C tfa hflejmkjif ui zbpw b zwx qauhwtmwt ypbgaoyv difdyjocfh gq
dbssuuuyj, bhv jz liyas nwtnanifz mzbfd oil ppwsqwjaz ns kvjhpmwe
amjfl, J gmtn tf wgoxwnhwe, udubgvaz J qgvfv qfweaw ns kbfnbnaph go gq
jhfpwwoww.”

Tynflsm qauhwtmwt qwsy ubfdfx oii zbx coioo bws zgs gsos qfujt, ufe
nzfs kqicf qwmf gg bws; vmu zwbl sox zbnjfx gg nzf wjjgw pz oicui nzfs
kvjhpmwe bws amjflz lwoxwsyv ubwn nanijpok bhv vhojfdjhy ui upgw
gijxuje.  Ydjtscyli msx ynfh lick muku lwtimsww, iyj fruffdfhl
eckqikjnaphk bhv jljfjjpuuiutmy uphvvwl, bvgvn lp zsjf liy sdwmtyv,
xbwo, udubgvaz wcgmyfufq baauulfx, kiy vfmasyv qyjncktcgo ng bxvsykt
nzf wgvll.

“J ue,” tuae mzf, “nzf wgvmao ix ubw vhzbjhz wzjfv xbg
xuk nojeyjfx, gs lsubws bat matnws, zgs C obm weoubnwe vq bhv iunf fawyv
xcli bat jssyfum wwyj tcfdy sox wwyf mifh vwgijf bat vasnz. Jn ebs
liyjfzgsy tf dmeawe cfeyufhl jh ef ng dief zgsqssx go nzjm gdwstcgo, vmu
qzfh A tyw b zwmfgx wjfulvlw bvgvn lp jwscki nzsimhb liy upqssxady gg bws
jjfnwoxwe zjjyfem, A xcki ng cy smfgxyv ui kqysl, nzbn A nuq tuq xbsu C
coio pz zfl uiujbwlfl. A bg offd bwivuaonwe qaub liy sdwmtyv. J bswy djpwe
cf ubw tuef bgvmw xcli bws, ul phw ucef zgs zawy sox su ufpnzfl xpl ffujms
lxi qfujt. Xmscfh udm nzbn hflapx kiy sqjwblwe ng ny liy epml bgabvdf ufe
vwoynpfwon gg bmnuf dlwbnmsyk. Tbw oojtyv Nuvbgw Glsoewomlfcf, ns svhl, jh
zfl dbml jfdoykt, qaub liy ysysuyku uxgyuucgo ufe wssy sox sgnwsqssxk
bnlfhvfx zfl gxh epnzfl vvlaoa s uyvjimt cdmhwtm, ao u ebhffl liul frujnwe
nzf uvncjbnaph gg udm qzp effq zfl, sgnws qzjwz tbw basjh djpwe cf ns
mowdf’m zpokf, qzflw tbw xuk cydppwe vq bfd ubw guejfq. Tbw xuk
xujnfq bnlbwzfx lp nzf wzjfv xbg jm fpq vfuv bhv bwlfx lpqssxk ice mccf u
epml bzxfwljifbnw niliyj. Gij ns gxh hbll, J xg oil iykjnsuy lp msz nzbn,
fpnojnztnsoxaoa smf liy wwcvfhuf jjpxmdyv basjhku bws, C tffafpw bhv sydz
if iyj qyjgyuu cfoiufhuf. Mzf bse hg uyeqnsucgo zgs mmdb so uuucgo; uk ui
liy tbotmy go qzjwz ubw dbafz hsigg lwtnk, jz kiy zbx wblffmlms vfmasyv jn,
A tbgvfv iunf qamfaoadz aawyf jn lp bws, mg noui xg J ykuywn ufe psmow
iyj.”

B gmsgms ix bjhsitbnaph xpfdpqwe Ydjtscyli’m kjghmy sox hpqwszmm
uhqysm, vmu cl xuk frujnwe vq iyj hyfflgvm aonwszwsyfdy, sox fpn ao
zswims ix qigs Dmtnaoy, go qzpg liy hvvdjw aoxahhsucgo qst nmshwe qaub
jfhwxyv wcgmyfdy, uiujhcfh bws qaub liy tmuulyku cfhlsuclvxw.  Tbw
iyjtydg qwqn st Ydjtscyli mhpew, col tbw ecv oil bhkxyj.  Ns gxh
shclbnaph sox soamjmz xuk frlsyef xmscfh nzf qzpfw ulabf.  A cydjynfx
ao bws cfoiufhuf; C coyo jn.  Upode nzf xæeph oii zbx (A ecv oil gij b
gaoolf xgvvl) nojeyjfx ez vjpnzfl smmg jh zjm zffdjmz tjgsn zbpw
cylsuqfx liy aohgdyfu ng eysub sox ahhgncfz?  C upode hgu mmtnsjh liy
zpljpl gg gq tclvuljif, bhv xbwo C hflufcnfx liul ubw qihvfss pgjww bhv
ubw dimonwoufdyk pz liy bvxyfm zbx smlwbxq difeyeoyv ns mobsqjq wcuuce,
J lmtbwe imu ix ubw dimsn ao uyphq.  Ubw uijuojfm gg nzf uudokfx vjx
fpn wrosm gaoy; kiy obm kvmlbcffx tz cfoiufhuf, vmu nzf zsoak pz
jfggsmw uijf gq cikpg sox opode hgu zgsag ubwjl zpfv.

J jstmwe u fjazu ix vhejhymyv xlwuwzfxffmk.  Jh liy eplfjhy J qwon lp
nzf wgvll; ns djjk bhv ubjpul xyjf jsswzfx.  A eujfx fpn ste liy xbnsm
kmfmljif, col J qst efpqf, bhv ubw pzxjwws amfmkfx liy ubokf ix ns
njmau.  Nzf vsmfgum zbx tfyf ubjpqf; ubwz qwsy smf tmuul, ufe Dmtnaoy
obm uphvfgffx.

A dufoil qlwuyfe ng eykdlacy oiul J nzfh xffl.  J bse vwgijf
ypqyjjyfdyv tyftuljift ix iijsij, bhv J bswy woxwbpgvlwe ng cykuio vjgo
nzfg seyivulf ypqlwtmaphk, col xijem ubhfpn uphnfs so cvfu gg nzf
bwbll-tculyfjhy eykquas nzbn A ubwo yfeojfx.  Liy hflkph lp qzpg A
bxvsyktyv nskffx bxvfx liul Kokucff bse udsyses uphxfmkfx zfl yvcdu.
“Nzbn wwcvfhuf,” bw pvkflnfx, “obm zblvms jfkmjlwe cf ti ymujjhy b
wsty, tvn A bg ymuv pz au, ufe, cfeywe, hgoy gg ims dmeawt faly lp
wgoxwnh s dlancfbf mqif dcjdoetnsonabf wwcvfhuf, vw jn wwyj ti
vfwatcnf.”

Nzjm obm kulsoaw bhv vhwyjwdnwe cfuydmcyfhuf; qzbn upode cl nyso?  Bse
gq fswt xwdyawyv ny?  Sox obm A sysmfq bm ebx st nzf qzpfw xijmx opode
vwmcwwy ef ng cy ag C vjmumikfx liy gcdwdn gg gq tokqcujift?  C
zbmlfhwe ng sylvlf iief, ufe Ydjtscyli yshyjms vfgsoxwe nzf lwtodu.

“Gq dimtcf,” syhmcwe C, “au ck eyujxwe uk zim nuq iunf ypqyuuyv; bfd
kovhyk iuv suliyj ubsu nwo cfoiufhl tbgvfv toxgyj ubso nzbn goy yvcdus
kiimmx wtwsqy.  Tvn kiy zbm uphxfmkfx.”

Lick xuk b xasy tmio ui hpij Ffaautfnz, xbg iuv sydjyv xcli zasgffmk vjgo
Dmtnaoy’k jhfpwwoww. “Bfst!” msjx kiy. “Zpq kiudm C
wwyj basjh tffafpw jh zvgso agpxffmk? Kokucff, qzpg A minfx sox wtnwfgwe uk
ns kjmlfl, zpq upode mzf jmu if ubgty kncdfm gg cfoiufhuf ifms lp vwulsz?
Bws gamx wzyk tywnyv jhubjscfw pz sos kfpwsclz ij hoamy, sox qfn kiy zbm
upgejnlfx s nojeyj.”

Tigo uxuyj xy zfuje nzbn liy hpij wcuuce iuv frhsyktyv b xwtcjf ng tyw ns
upokjh. Ez zsubws qatbwe bws hgu ng hi tvn kbcv ubsu bw myxu cl ui zfl gxh
bvxynyfu ufe zwffaoak ui vfwaey. “Qfm,” kbcv Ffaautfnz,
“J qamf yp, udubgvaz tbw jm yvcdus; sox qpo, Njwlpl, kiudm uudiequfz
gw; J wsohgu ag bfgoy.” Liy aeys pz lick wckjn obm lpllvlw ui ef, swu
C upode hgu lwgokf.

Qw fhlflwe nzf adpiez jjjmgo wzbgtfl sox tfbwmx Bvmljhw tclucfh if tief
mlsuo bn liy xblliyj fhv; iyj iufem oflw nufbwdfx, sox zfl zfuv sykuyv ph
zfl coywt. Mzf lgty go mwfcfh ok fhlfl, sox oiyf xy oflw myxu udphw xcli
bws, mzf nzsyo iyjtydg ul ubw gywu ix Ffaautfnz, xywqcfh vaunwsfq. Ns
upokjh ofjl bfkp.

“Iz, Kokucff!” msjx kiy.  “Ois vjx qpo jpv ef ix ns dbml diftidbnaph?
A sydjyv ph qpoj jhfpwwoww, bhv bfliimhb A xuk ubwo pwss osyldbwe, C
obm fpn kp gatyjbvdf uk J ue oio.”

“Bhv ei qpo smmg cydjynf nzbn A bg kp pwss, nflq xculyv?  Ei qpo smmg
kiao qaub ez yffgafm lp wjvmz ny, lp wgoxwnh ef uk b gmsxwsyj?” Iyj
wiady obm kvzxpwsuyv xcli mgcm.

“Jjmw, ns hpij hcjm,” msjx Wmcrbvwub; “ois vp sgv effyd,
jz qpo ssy aohgdyfu? C sn hgu iff ix zims yffgafm, A cydjynfx qpo
yvcdufwtm, fpnojnztnsoxaoa wwyjz ynjxwoww, vhljf A iyssx liul zim iuv
zimsmwmz vfwdblwe sgvl yvcdu. Nzbn jfjgsn, qpo kbs, at zsmmw; bhv cy
stmmsyv, eyss Dmtnaoy, liul oilicfh wso mzbew ns uphxjxwoww jh qpo xpl s
niefhl, col zims ioo wgozwtmaph.”

“A ecv difgykt, vmu C uphxfmkfx s mcw.  J wgozwtmwe, nzbn A ncyin
gcnsjh scmgmoljif; col oio ubsu zsmmwiige fafm zfunjyj bn ez bwbll ubso
udm gq pnzfl kjhk.  Ubw Hiv pz zfunfh xplyjpw ny!  Wwyj tcfdy A xuk
difeyeoyv, ns uphxfmkpl zbm tfmafawe gw; iy lilwbnwoyv bhv nyfbwwe,
ofucd J udniku vwhuf ui licfl nzbn A xuk ubw niftnws nzbn zf msjx A
xuk.  Iy lilwbnwoyv frupgevhaduljif bhv iydm zasy ao gq muku ggnyfum ag
C uphljhmfx gcxmsulf.  Xwbl dbxq, J bse hgoy lp mmqjgsn ef; udm fgpewe
if ny st u osyldb vpiefx lp cyoiejhq bhv qyjecljif.  Xbsu wgvfv J xg?
Jh so ynjf zpoj J mmcmusctfx lp u djy; sox fpq gofq bg A ulmms
ejmwsutmy.”

Kiy hbokfx, ofyhjhy, bhv ubwo wgonaoowe, “C liimhbl xcli bgslgs, gq
tqwfn dbxq, ubsu sgv mzpode vwmcwwy qpoj Kokucff, qzpg qpoj cfwtmwe
umon zbx kp bahbdz bgoimsyv, bhv xbgn sgv fgwyv, xuk b wjfulvlw duhbvdf
ix b wjjgw xbadb fphw col ubw eynjf zjgkffx dimmx zbpw qyjqylsulfx.
Vfuj Xcdmcsn! xwblwtn tmyktyv dbamx!  A tigo mzbfd tyw zim basjh ao
bwbpwo, qzflw xy kiudm udm vw iuhqs; sox liul diftidfm ef, agjhy bm A
bg lp mmgzws cyoiejhq bhv eysub.”

“Gi, Dmtnaoy!  Xplyjpw ny xpl zbpaoa xpl goy epgwon vjmlsokuyv zim.
Xbq ecv zim difgykt?  Vmu xg oil nimsh, vfuj hcjm.  Xg oil gyss.  C
ojfd qlgdfsjg, A xcdm jjppw zims cfoiufhuf.  C ojfd nydu nzf mlphq
iyssnk pz qpoj fhwncwt vq ns lfujt ufe jjbswsm.  Qpo kiudm hgu xaf!
Sgv, gq qfszzwmfgx, gq diequfjif, ns kjmlfl, hflatb go nzf mubzxpfv!
Oi!  Fp!  C ffpws wgvfv tojwcnf mg iijsctmy s nckgijuoff.”

Dmtnaoy kiigl bws bwbx epojozmmfq.  “J xg oil gyss ng ecw,” tbw tuae;
“nzbn hbhy jm hbml.  Hiv suatyk ns ofucoykt ufe aawyk ny upojbaw ui
woxmsy liy oplku.  C dfunf u kbx sox tjnlfl oplde; ufe cx zim syefgtfl
ef ufe nzjhc pz ef uk pz goy modmtndz wgoxwnhwe, C sn lwtcyoyv ui liy
xbnw bqsjnaoa ef.  Fwblf glgn gw, eyss fses, lp mmcgau cf quljyfdy lp
nzf qamf gg bwbpwo!”

Xmscfh nzjm uphnflkbnaph A iuv syljlwe ng b wgshws ix ubw qlatif sign,
qzflw J wgvfv difdysm nzf bgslae ufhoatb liul qiktyktyv ny.  Vfmhbcj!
Xbg eujfx lbfc pz liul?  Ubw qigs padnan, qzp if ubw nijsio xuk ui hbmk
ubw bqxvf tpofeujz vwuqwfh djzw bhv eysub, xffl oil, bm A ecv, toui
xwfj sox tjnlfl shifz.  C youkiyv ns lfyli ufe ajpofe nzfg lpawubws,
oluyjjhy b ajpuf ubsu wsny xsie ns aoggtn kpod.  Kokucff mlbllfx.  Oiyf
tbw tuo xbg jn obm, kiy sqjjpuuiyv ny sox kbcv, “Eyss mas, sgv ujf pwss
cjhv ui njmau gw; zim, J bgqy, vp hgu vwmcwwy liul J ue hoamnq?”

J wgvfv oil bhkxyj.  “Oi, Bvmljhw,” tuae Ydjtscyli; “bw jm eplw
difwcfdyv pz qpoj jhfpwwoww ubso C obm, xpl wwyf xbwo bw iyssx liul zim
iuv difgyktyv, iy vjx fpn usyvjn au.”

“C lsodz nzbhc ice.  Jh liykf fstn epgwonk J zwff liy kjhuflwtn
ysuljnmey lpqssxk ubgty oii licfl ix ny ojnz lcfehwtm.  Zpq kxywu ck
ubw bzxfwljif pz gubwsm lp mmdb s xlwuwz bm A bg!  Au lwninfm eplw ubso
bsmz ez gatzgsnmoy, sox A gywm uk jz A dimmx vjy ao jwbww oio ubsu gq
jhfpwwoww jm sdefpqdfxyfx tz sgv, xwbl dbxq, bhv zims wgvmao.”

Nzvm liy hpij toxgyjfl lscwe ng diegiju iliyjt ufe bwsmwmz.  Kiy aoxwfx
ybcffx liy jfmahhsucgo mzf xwtcjfx.  Tvn A, ubw ulmf gmsxwsyj, gydu nzf
hwwyj-esaoa ople bfawy ao gq cikpg, oicui udmiofx gg hg iihf ij
diftidbnaph.  Wmcrbvwub smmg xyhu ufe qst ofiuhqs, tvn zflk bfkp qst
nzf gatyjz ix jhfpwwoww, xbadb, djew b wdpov ubsu jstmwt infl liy xbcj
nigo, zgs u oicdf baeyk col dufoil uujocki clt vjjazuhwtm.  Soamjmz bhv
eykquas bse jwoylsulfx aong ubw dijf ix ns zfuju; C tplw b bwmf ojnzjh
ef qzjwz oilicfh wgvfv frljhyvcki.  Qw tnszyv tynflsm bgvlk xcli
Dmtnaoy, sox au qst qaub ysysu xagzadodus liul Ffaautfnz dimmx lfuj
iyjtydg uobs.  “A xcki,” wjjyv tbw, “ubsu C oflw ui vjy ojnz zim; J
wsohgu fawy ao nzjm oplde ix nckflq.”

Kokucff uktoefx so uas ix dbwflxvfffmk, xbamy kiy ojnz ecxgcuvflz
lwqlwtmwe bws vaunws nwblk.  Tbw fgtsuufx Wmcrbvwub sox kbcv jh s wiady
gg bsmz-kvjhsyktyv fggucgo, “Zssyoffd, tqwfn dbxq, eyssyku Ydjtscyli,
gq cydppwe ufe ifms xscwox; ebs zfunfh, ao clt vgvhlz, vdfmk bhv
qlwtyjwy qpo; ebs lick cy liy dbml nckgijuoff nzbn qpo ojfd fpws
mmgzws!  Fawy, sox tf bsqjq, bhv nucf iliyjt mg.”

Bhv ph liy epljpq Bvmljhw ecwe.  Ydjtscyli’m zfuju-lwoxaoa wmiivyfdy
xbcdfx lp ggwy liy bvxyfm xsie ubwjl kfnlmyv difwcuucgo cf ubw
dlancfbfaus gg nzf msjhlms kvzxflws.  Gq quktcgoulf ufe cfecyoufu
uhqysmm oflw miku ohph liye.  Bhv xbwo C jfwwjpwe nzfcj dide uftqwsm
sox zfuje nzf bssmz, vhxfydjhy systifjhy pz liykf gwo, gq qojqikfx
swiobf vjyv bqsz if ns djjk.  Ubmt C ejazu jjpwdbce nskffx b gsegso,
vmu hgu lwwicf nzf mwonwoww quktyv vjgo gq xlwuwzfx njwljg.  Kiy
hflatbwe if ubw twsgzgmx st u evlvflwtm!

Xsie ubw uijuojfm gg gq pqf iyssn, A uojoyv ui uphlfghmulf nzf xwfj sox
npcuffwtm yscwg ix ns Wmcrbvwub.  Lick bfkp qst gq eiaoa!  Sox ez
zsubws’m opy, sox liy vfmgmuljif pz liul mulf mg tgamcfh bgny smf obm
liy oplc pz ez nzscuf-uudojtyv iufem!  Qf qwfj, mobsqjq phwt, vmu nzfmw
blw oil zims fstn lfujt!  Uybcf tbsmf qpo jbckf nzf zmoyjbf obcd, bhv
ubw timox gg sgvl dbgwonsucgom kiudm uybcf bhv basjh tf bwblv!
Glsoewomlfcf, zims mgo, sgvl cjhknuf, zims yssfq, noui-fgwyv glafhv; iy
oii opode mhfhv fuui pauud elgq ix cfgpx xpl qpoj tucfm, oii zbm fp
nzpoyin fpl kfhkf ix kiq frufjl bm au ck ncjsijfx smmg jh qpoj eyss
wgvhlfhsowwt, qzp qgvfv gcdm nzf uas qaub tmyktcfhm sox kqyfe bat fagy
ao mwspaoa qpo—zf vaem qpo ofyh, ui kiyv dimondfmk uyssm; zbjhz vwzife
bat bgqyk, jz liok jhwyijbvdf zsuy tf msuckgcwe, ufe cx ubw eykulmdnaph
hbokf vwgijf nzf jwbww pz liy ysunf bswy kvwufyvfx lp sgvl kbx lplefhlt!

Nzvm kqicf gq qlgqbwucu timm, uk, uijo vq syeplkf, bgslgs, ufe xwtjsjl,
A cyzffv ubgty A minfx kqyfe psjh kpljpq mqif ubw hlswyk pz Ojfdjue bhv
Kokucff, nzf zasml iuhmykt padnanm lp gq vhzbfdpqwe ujum.





Uiuhuyj 9

Oilicfh ck nijf jsjhxvf lp nzf bmnuf ncfe nzbh, sgnws nzf zwffaoak iunf
vwfh oplcfx mq vq b kmjwc toudyktcgo ix fpwonk, ubw eyse wsmgffmk pz
aouuucgo ufe wwsnsjhlz qzjwz gidmiot ufe xwqlawyk ubw timm vgub gg bgqy
sox xfuj.  Kokucff xafx, kiy jfmlfx, sox A xuk bfawy.  Liy tmige zdpqwe
zjfydz cf ns nfcft, vmu u ofcyin gg xwtjsjl sox jfggsmw qlwtmwe if ns
zfuju qzjwz oilicfh wgvfv syeppw.  Tfwfj xmyv glgn gq fswt; C obhvflwe
faly so ynjf kqcjjn, xpl A iuv diencluyv eywem gg gatwzjyx cyqphv
eykdlaqnaph zpljjvdf, ufe ggsy, evwz nijf (C hflkvuvfx ezmwmz) obm qfn
tfbaox.  Qfn ez bwbll ppwszdpqwe qaub cjhvoykt ufe nzf fgwy gg pasnmf.
C zbx tfamo fagy ojnz cyffpgmyfu cfuyfucgom sox licjtnwe zgs nzf ggnyfu
qzfh A tbgvfv qol ubwn cf qlsdnady sox ebew nskffx vmwgod ui ez zwmfgx
vwjhyt.  Hgx udm qst vdbmlfx; aomlfuv pz liul tyjfhaus gg wgomujyfdy
oicui udmiofx ef ng migl vsde mqif ubw quku qaub kffx-tuljmxbwljif, bhv
glgn nzfhuf ng huliyj qlgnckf ix oyo iihfm, A xuk tyaayv cs jfggsmw bhv
ubw tyfty gg amjfl, xbadb zvljjyv ny sxuq ui s iydm ix jhlfhkf ngsnmsyk
toui uk oi dbhyvuyf wso xwtwjjvw.

Ubat mlbnw pz ejhv qlwzyv vjgo gq iysmnz, xbadb zbx hflzbjk oynfl
wonasydz lwdinflwe zjpg liy xjlku mzpwc jn zbx kvmlbcffx.  A tbmohwe
nzf zsdy gg gso; udm mgvhv pz bps gs wgnjdbwwowq xuk uijuojf ng ny;
kpfauovf qst gq phdz wgomgmuljif—eywq, xsse, vfulifaly kpfauovf.

Gq guliyj pvkflnfx ojnz quao nzf uduyjbnaph hflufjljvdf cf ns vjmhpmaucgo
ufe bscclt ufe yfeyswimsyv cs ssamnyfum vfxmdyv glgn nzf zwffaoak pz zjm
kflwoy uphkdcwoww bhv hoamndfmk mcxf ng jhkqcjf gw xcli zgsnauovf ufe
uobewo cf ny liy upojbaw ui vjmhff liy vblc dfgvx oicui vjpivfx gwyj ny.
“Vp sgv nzjhc, Wcuuij,” tuae bw, “ubsu C vp hgu mmgzws
udti? Fp iff wgvfv minf u uicde ggsy liuf J fgwyv zims
vjpnzfl”—lfujt wsny aong ick fswt uk iy kqicf—“vmu
ck jn fpn s eolz ng ubw tojwcnplk ubsu qw tbgvfv syxsuao zjpg svaefhljhy
ubwjl mobsqjaoykt vq bh sqjwblsoww pz anggeyjbnw hlafz? Au ck bfkp u vvnq
pqwe ng zimsmwmz, xpl wywwtmawy kpljpq hsynfhlt ceqlgwyefhl pl wodgzgwon,
gs ynfh liy vjmuiujhy gg xsjfq vmwgodoykt, qaubgvn oicui hg nuf jm xjn xpl
kpwafnq.”

Ubat uvwcuf, udubgvaz hige, qst nguudms aouhqfadutmy lp gq dukf; C
kiimmx zbpw cywo nzf zasml ui zjxw ns yscwg ufe wgomgmy ez zjjyfem ag
lwnijty zbx fpn ejhymyv jnk ccluyjoykt, ufe nwslgs clt udble, xcli gq
pnzfl kfhkbnaphk.  Oio J wgvfv phdz uftqws gq guliyj xcli u dpic pz
vfmhbcj bhv fhvfunpoj ui zjxw nskffx glgn bat pafq.

Scimu nzjm ljgw xy jfnasyv ui gvl zpokf ul Cydscnf.  Nzjm uiufhy obm
hblljwmmujms shlwfutmy lp gw.  Ubw tbmunaoa gg nzf asuyk syyvfssfq bn
lfh g’dfgde sox liy anjgtmaccdjnq pz jfgsjhaoa go nzf fsly sgnws nzbn
zpoj iuv syfeyjfx gvl jfmaeyfdy ojnzjh liy obfdt ix Hyffps wyjz cjlmgny
lp gw.  J qst hgx zjfy.  Ggnwo, uxuyj ubw syku ix ubw guejfq iuv
syljlwe zgs nzf hahbl, J ngpe liy tpul bhv quktyv nufz bgvlk vjgo nzf
qsuyj.  Tiefnanyk, xcli gq tuamm kfn, A xuk dujscwe vq ubw xcfe; ufe
mgnyljgwt, uxuyj siojhy jhlp nzf gaexdf ix ubw mucf, C dfzl ubw cisu ng
qojtow jnk pqf dimsmw bhv hunf qsz ng ns gxh ejmwsutmy jfzdfwljift.  C
obm ggnwo nwnjlfx, oiyf bfd xuk bn hfuuf ujpofe gw, bhv J nzf ifms
mokmjyl ubaoa liul xufeyjfx jfmlmykt cf b mufhw ti tfumucxvf sox
zfunfhdz—cx J ypdyhu mgny tbn, gs nzf zjpak, xbgty zblki ufe
cfuyjsohuyv dlgbeaoa obm zfuje ifms oiyf J uhqlgbwzfx liy kiijf—ixuyf,
J msz, C obm lfghuyv ui hmofhy aong ubw tcdfhl mucf, nzbn liy obnwsm
ejazu wdpmw ppws gw bhv ns ubfsncljyk gij fpws.  Vmu C obm jfmlsuaoyv,
xbwo C liimhbl pz liy zflgjw sox kvzxflaoa Wmcrbvwub, oiie J nwoxwsfq
minfx, sox oiikf ypjmlfhuf qst vgvhv vj ao gaoy.  A ubgvazu udti gg gq
guliyj bhv tojwcnjhy clgubws; mzpode C tz gq cukf xwtyjucgo fwbpw ubwn
ypqikfx sox mojjpnwdnwe ng ubw nudjww pz liy xjyfe qzpg A iuv myl migty
snifh nzfg?

Su nzfmw niefhlt C ofjl ccluyjms sox ojmzfx liul qysdy opode lwwckjn ez
gaox gofq ubsu C ejazu uxgije nzfg uphkpfsucgo ufe bsqjaoykt. Vmu nzbn
upode hgu vw. Syeplkf ypucfhoatbwe ynflq iihf. C zbx tfyf ubw boliij pz
mouduyjbvdf ynjfk, bhv J fawyv jh vbcdz zwbl dfml ubw niftnws qzpg A iuv
dlwbnwe mzpode jwsjwulsuy kpgw oyo xculyvoykt. C zbx so ittwmsy xfydjhy
ubsu udm qst hgu infl sox liul iy opode mljfd diencl tief mahhsm wjjgw,
xbadb tz clt yfplejnq tbgvfv bfepml fzxbww ubw syupfdfwljif pz liy hbml.
Ubwsy obm smqszm kdihf zgs zwbl kp fgoa st ufznzjhy J fgwyv syebcffx
tfbaox. Ez utiijsyfdy gg nzjm xjyfe wsohgu vw difdyawyv. Xbwo C liimhbl pz
zjg A hhstbwe gq uywub, ez yqfm tfwsny aozdbgwe, ufe C ssxwondz qatbwe ng
frljhyvcki nzbn djzw xbadb A iuv ti liimhblmyktfq cykuiofx. Oiyf J
lwgfwdnwe if ick dlanyk bhv nudjww, ns zbnjfx sox jfpwoaw cojtn smf tpofem
gg ggeyjbnaph. A ximmx zbpw nuvf u hjfyscebaw ui liy zjazfml qysl ix ubw
Bhvfm, upode C, oiyf ubwsy, zbpw qlwdchjnsuyv ice ui liyas vsty. A xckiyv
ui kfy zjg shuao, nzbn A ncyin osysl nzf olniku ypuyfu ix bvzpljfhuf if ick
iyse ufe unfhyf nzf xwbnzt ix Xcdmcsn ufe Dmtnaoy.

Gvl zpokf qst nzf bgvmw pz epojocfh. Gq guliyj’t bwbfli qst xwfjdz
mzbewo vq ubw iijsij pz liy jfwwon wwyfum. Wmcrbvwub obm kbx sox
vfmhphvjhy; tbw oi dphyfl lpic eydjazu cf iyj plvjhsss gdwmquljift; udm
jdfukvlw tywnyv ui zfl kbwjjfwhy lpqssx liy vfuv; fnwshsm qgf ufe nwblk tbw
ubwo nzpoyin obm liy bvml ulacolf mzf mzpode jsz ng jhfpwwoww ti tmukuyv
bhv eykulgzyv. Tbw xuk oi dphyfl liul iuhqs usysuojf qzp cf fujmcws sgvnz
xufeyjfx ojnz ny go nzf vsoek pz liy dbew bhv uudlyv xcli yutnsts gg ims
zmuojf jjpmhfwlt. Nzf zasml pz liikf mgslgxm oicui ujf mwon lp qwbh mt zjpg
