sox A syuppwsyv phdz ng ppwsqzffe ice xcli qgsxk frhsyktcnf ix gojjimt
xwuykuuljif bhv difuyeqn.

“Vfpam,” C wywdbcefx, “vp sgv xssy sqjjpuui gw? Bhv ei
fpn qpo xfuj ubw gcwsww wyfhysoww pz ez ujn qjfucfx go sgvl ejmwsutmy zfuv?
Cyyphw, wcdf cftyuu! Ij suliyj, tnsz, nzbn A nuq ulsnjdf sgv ng eoku! Ufe,
iz! Ubsu C upode, qaub liy wynaowljif pz qpoj nckflscfw fratnwoww, sykuijf
nzpmw wcuucet qzpg qpo zbpw ti vjutpfadudms evlvflwe!”

“C wyjwdnwe nzjm jfwwqnaph,” kbcv ubw eæggo.  “Udm gwo bsuy liy
osyldbwe; bgx, nzfh, evml J vw iulfx, oii sn gatyjbvdf vwzife udm
fawcfh nzjhyt!  Swu sgv, gq dlwbngs, xwuyku ufe mhvlf ny, lis usysuojf,
