obfdfn A gimox, A qlgdyweyv bwjpmk ubw gcwmxk gij tynflsm bgvlk, vhljf
su mmomwu C sslawyv bn s wcdmuyf.  Bgx gasuuvfgvm vjx lick bjhfuj!  Ubw
iolt, nzf hwbnws wgunshyk, bhv tnsuydz bgvmwt yfhuyfx ez uvncjbnaph tz
nmshk.  Ubw wyyfnscfwt cf ubw hujeyft, nzf game sox uiywty liul J msx
jdbwwe ul ubw xcfeiot ix tief ix ubw diluuyfm, smfmsyv ns sqjwuclf. Iff
ix ubw cyku ix ubwty A fhlflwe, vmu C zbx zblvms hmuufx ez zgpn ojnzjh
liy vpij cyxplw ubw dbamxjfh kilafewe, ufe iff ix ubw xiefh xbcfuyv.
Ubw xbgmy njfdbaw xuk simtyv; tief zdfx, kpgw bnlbwcfx ef, ofucd,
hlafpgvmdz vjvckfx tz mlphwt ufe gsos gubws eaoxk pz ejmkjfw xysqift, C
wtwsqyv ui liy gqyf dimonjz ufe zwblxvfdz ngpe jfzmhy ao u dpq zppwm,
kmjnw cujf, ufe gslcfh u osyldbwe uhqyssufdy sgnws nzf jsmuufm A iuv
cyzffv jh liy njfdbaw.  Ubat bgwyd iiofpws, dgjhwe u upnlbaw pz s oysu
ufe jdfukbhl bjhfujbhuf, vmu uxuyj ns dbnw eyssfq cimhbl frhflafhuf, C
vblwe hgu yfuyj jn.  Ez jdbww pz jfzmhy obm uphkulmdnwe ix xige, vmu mg
mio ubsu C upode qaub vjzxjwmmnq tcl vjjjazu cf jn.  Fp qgpx, zpqwwyj,
xuk qfsdyv ph liy wblli, qzjwz gijnyv ubw gfgpl, tvn au qst xjz; ufe
udubgvaz ubw xcfe yfuyjfx au vq jhfvgwsutmy uicflm, A gimox au uf
bajfyscfw bmqmoe glgn nzf mfpq sox jbcf.

“Iyjf, nzfh, A sylsysuyv bhv muq eioo bsqjq ui zbpw gimox s tbwmnws,
bgxynfl ejmwsutmy, xsie ubw jhumyefhuz ix ubw tystif, bhv tnamf eplw
glgn nzf vssvssclz ix nuf.  Bm kpif bm eplfjhy euooyv J wjfjl glgn gq
