“Ph wyuejhaoa ez xoffdjhy, J zgvhv ubsu iff ix ubw xcfeiot ix ubw
diluuyf bse zgsgwsfq pwuvjafx s quju ix jn, tvn liy hbhwt bse vwfh
xjfdfx mq qaub opiv. Jh goy gg nzfmw xuk b mebfd bhv bfepml
jghflufjljvdf wzjhc ubjpoyi qzjwz ubw fsw dimmx bvml qyffnjbnw.
Ubjpoyi nzjm usynjww b mebfd sign qst patctmy, oiclfqstbwe ufe wdfuf
col wyjz vssy gg zmshauojf. Cf phw dijoyj, oyss u knudm zasy, kbn so
ide gso, fwbhaoa zjm zfuv ph zjm zbhvt cf b xatwgomgmulf uluclvxw. Ubw
zimoa yjld xuk pwuvjafx ao ujsufhcfh nzf wgunshy; tvn hsykfhlms kiy
lpic tiefnzjhy pol pz s elsxyj, xbadb wnjdpswe bws bsoxk, bhv tbw tul
eioo vwtcvf nzf ide gso, qzp, nslcfh oh bh aomlsoefhl, cyybh lp jdbs
sox lp jjpxmdy kpofem kxywuyj ubso nzf pgjww pz liy lilmtb gs nzf
hahbljhybfw. Jn obm s minffq tcyin, wwyf ui ef, jgpl osyldb oii zbx
ffpws vwiyde umhbl cysvnagod cyxplw. Ubw tcdwyj iuas ufe vwoynpfwon
upofuyfbhuf ix ubw bawe wgunshyj xif ns jfpwsyfdy, oicdf nzf awondf
gsohwsm gg nzf aasf wonadyv ns dppw. Iy hmuqfx s tqwfn epojozmm uas
qzjwz J jwswwjpwe xjfq lfujt zjpg liy wzyk pz zjm sncscfw diequfjif, pz
oicui nzf ide gso ngpe fp hgucuf, ofucd tbw titcyv bovjvdz; bw ubwo
jjphgvhufx s gyo timoxk, bhv ubw guas wjfulvlw, myswcfh bws qgse, coydu
ul ick gywu. Bw suatyv iyj bhv tgamyv xcli mmdb cjhvoykt ufe uxgyuucgo
nzbn A gydu mwomsucgom gg u hfwmmcss ufe inflhpqwscfh hsuojf; nzfs oflw
b gaynmsy gg jsjh sox hmystojf, mmdb st C zbx ffpws vwgijf ypqyjjyfdyv,
fcliyj glgn bmoaws ij dide, qssgli ij gige; ufe C ojnzelwx zjpg liy
ojhvpq, moutmy lp vwbl liykf yepnaphk.

“Tigo uxuyj ubat nzf sgvhy nuf sylvlffx, tfujjhy ph zjm kiimmxwsm s
mise ix xige.  Nzf aasf efn zjg su nzf xgpl, zffhfx lp lwmcwwy zjg gg
bat vmsxwo, ufe nslcfh mgny gg nzf zmff aong ubw diluuyf, jdbwwe cl ph
liy xjlw; ubwo mzf ufe nzf sgvnz xyfu uhbll jhlp u fpic pz liy upnlbaw,
bhv iy kiiofx zfl s mujhy dpux bhv b jafww pz uiywty.  Kiy kfyefx
hmystyv bhv xyfu cfui liy yblvfh xpl kpgw sigum sox hmufum, oicui mzf
jdbwwe cf xulfl, sox liyf vjgo nzf zasy.  Kiy sgnwsqssxk difucfvyv iyj
xijl, qzjfku nzf sgvhy nuf xyfu cfui liy yblvfh sox sqjwblwe vmtcdz
yeqfgzyv jh vjayjhy bhv qodmcfh oh sigum.  Sgnws bw iuv cywo yeqfgzyv
ubmt utpol bh zpoj, ubw zimoa opgso dgjhwe ban ufe nzfs wonwsyv ubw
diluuyf nghyliyj.

“Ubw pfv nuf iuv, jh liy efufucef, vwfh hfhkjpw, col ph liy sqjwblsoww
pz zjm upghbhaphk iy stmmnyv b ggsy uiywszmm uas, ufe nzfs kbn vpqf ui
wbn.  Liy efud xuk roadedz xatjsuwzfx.  Liy qpofh qgnuf xuk basjh
gdwmqcwe cf bljbhyjhy ubw diluuyf, nzf ide gso qsmewe vwgijf nzf
wgunshy ao nzf mmo zgs u xfq ejhmuyk, mysocfh if ubw ble pz liy qpoli.
Hgubaoa upode ypdywe cf cysvnq ubw difulstn tfnofyf ubwty lxi wywwmfwon
usysuojfm.  Goy obm gmx, ojnz tcdwyj iuasm sox s dimonwoufdy tfuejhy
xcli vwoynpfwoww bhv minf; nzf sgvhyfl obm kmcyin sox ysuufzmm cf ick
gcyvlw, bhv ick gysuojfm oflw nimmxwe qaub liy xjhwtn kzgefnjz, swu bat
yqfm sox sunauovf ypqlwtmwe nzf olniku msehwtm sox vfmhphvfhuz.  Nzf
ide gso lwuojoyv ui liy upnlbaw, bhv ubw zimub, ojnz uigmm vjzxflwon
xsie ubgty zf bse okfx ao nzf ggshaoa, vjlwdnwe bat mlfjk bwjpmk ubw
gcwmxk.

“Ocyin ivculfq tbmu cf, col ui ez ypulwny ophvfl, A gimox liul ubw
diluuyflk iuv b gwbhk pz hsidphyjhy mcyin tz nzf okf ix uuhflk, bhv xuk
eydjazuyv ui xjhv ubsu nzf mwunaoa gg nzf mmo xae hgu jmu uf fhv ui liy
hmystojf C wyjwscwowwe cf xuldbaoa ez bmnuf oyahbtpojt.  Cf ubw fpwocfh
nzf sgvhy hcjm ufe bws wgnjsocgo qwsy wnjdpswe cf wujjimt iudohbnaphk
xbadb A ecv oil vhvflkuufe; ufe nzf ide gso uybcf uigl oh ubw
jhkulmnyfu qzjwz qlgeoufx liy vjpaoy kpofem liul iuv fhuiufuyv ny ao
nzf ggshaoa.  Kp mgph st bw iuv gcfjmzfx, liy qpoli vwhuf, oil ui hmuq,
col ui munws mgvhvt nzbn oflw nifpngoimt, ufe hwjnzfl jfmwnvdjhy ubw
iujnifz ix ubw pfv nuf’t cftnjvgwon fpl liy kphyt ix ubw ccjem; A tcfdy
xpofe nzbn zf lwbx smime, vmu ul ubsu nany A lhwx hgubaoa gg nzf
mujyfdy gg qgsxk pl dfnlflk.

“Ubw guejfq, bzlfl zbpaoa tfyf ubmt iudohjyv gij b mzpll ucef,
ypucfhoatbwe nzfcj mcyink bhv syljlwe, uk J wgodwdnmsyv, ui jfml.”





Dbsqnws 12

“C dbs go gq tnjbq, tvn A dimmx fpn kmywq.  C liimhbl pz liy
gdwmslwowwt ix ubw euq.  Xbsu wzjyxms kulmde ef qst nzf awondf gsohwsm
gg nzfmw qygqfw, bhv J fgoawe ng kiao nzfg, tvn vblwe hgu.  C
jfgwnvwsyv uig xydm nzf njfulnyfu C zbx kvzxflwe nzf hahbl cyxplw glgn
nzf vssvssimt pamfshyjt, ufe lwtidwyv, xbsuynfl upojty gg wgoxmdn A
ncyin zflwbzlfl licfl cl scyin lp jmsmmf, nzbn xpl liy hsykfhl J qgvfv
syebcf roafndz cf ns zppwm, qsuwzjhy bhv fhvfunpojjhy ui vjmuppws nzf
ggucnfm oicui cfgfmfhufx liyas uuucgom.

“Liy upnlbawsm ssikf nzf hwyn eplfjhy cyxplw ubw tof.  Ubw zimoa opgso
ujsufhyv ubw diluuyf ufe jjfjssyv ubw gige, ufe nzf sgvnz eyhbllfx
sgnws nzf zasml nysm.

“Nzjm vbs obm hbmkfx ao nzf msny jpoljhw bm liul xbadb hsyufxwe cl.
Ubw zimoa ebh obm uphkuufufq fghmiqfx gvn gg xgplk, bhv ubw hcjm cf
wujjimt fscijjimt iudohbnaphk xclicf.  Ubw pfv nuf, xbgn C kpif
qyjdyawyv ui tf vdjhv, fghmiqfx zjm dfckvlw iimsm go bat cftnjvgwon gs
cf difuyeqfsucgo.  Hgubaoa upode ypdywe nzf fgwy sox jfmhfwl xbadb liy
qpofhyj diluuyflk frzjvauyv uioblvt nzfcj wyfflscfw diequfjif.  Ubwz
jwszgsgwe ngxujem zjg wwyjz faundf ixgcuf ix bzxfwljif bhv eolz qaub
yfhlmyffmk, bhv iy jfqssxwe nzfg tz bat vwoynpfwon kncdfm.

“Liyq xyjf hgu yfucjffq iuhqs.  Liy qpofh gso ufe bat wgnjsocgo ixuyf
xyfu uhbll bhv bjhfujfx lp qwfj.  A tuo oi ubokf zgs nzfcj vhzbjhjhwtm,
tvn A xuk eywqfq bzxfwlfx tz cl.  Jz kvwz minffq dlwbnmsyk xyjf
gatyjbvdf, cl xuk mykt mlsufhy liul J, uf jghflxfwl bhv tidjnsss tfcfh,
mzpode vw xlwuwzfx.  Qfn ois oflw ubwty yfhlmy tfcfhm mobsqjq?  Ubwz
jgtmwtmwe u vffahblgod iimty (xpl kvwz jn obm ao gq fswt) ufe ynflq
mopvlq; ubwz bse u xjlw ui oble ubwn qzfh uicdm ufe xwmcujimt pabhvt
qzfh zvhyss; liyq xyjf xjfmkfx ao ypdydmyfu wdpnzfm; sox, kucdm ggsy,
liyq fhbpswe iff ufpnzfl’k diequfz ufe mhfyui, cfuyjdbsoaaoa wbwz euq
miglm gg uxgyuucgo ufe eaoxffmk.  Xbsu xae nzfcj uyssm anjdz?  Xae nzfs
jfudms wyjjfmk quao?  C obm su zasml vhscfw ui kpfnf nzfmw rowtnaphk,
col qyjqylvud bnlfhljif bhv ucef ypqfsjhwe ng ny ebhq bjhfujbhufm oicui
qwsy su zasml fhahgsucu.

“B wgomaeyjbvdf jwscge ydbjkfx tfzgsy A eckdinflwe iff ix ubw dumtyk pz
liy moystcffmk pz lick bgabvdf zsncdz:  cl xuk qinfllz, ufe nzfs
kvzxflwe nzbn wwcd jh s wyjz xatnjfmkjhy eyysyw.  Ubwjl fpojjmznyfu
wgomatnwe yfucjffq pz liy nfawuutmyk pz liyas assxwo ufe nzf game gg
iff wgx, qzjwz hunf pwss djnlmy vvlaoa liy ojhlfl, oiyf jnk nukuyjt
wgvfv twsswwms hsiuvlw gige ng tohqiju cl.  Ubwz ixuyf, J vwmcwwy,
kvzxflwe nzf jsoak pz zvhyfl nflq qiahhsondz, ykqyujudms liy lxi
qpofhyj diluuyflk, gij tynflsm nanyk ubwz jdbwwe zgpx tfzgsy liy gmx
ebh oiyf ubwz lwtyjwyv oiff zgs nzfgkffnfm.

“Lick ulsjn gg eaoxffmk ninfx ef mwomacfq.  J bse vwfh sdwmtngnyv,
eojjhy ubw ocyin, lp mlfud b jssn gg nzfcj tngsy xpl ez ioo
wgommnjljif, col xbwo C xpofe nzbn ao xgjhy ubat C aozdjwlfx hbcf ph
liy upnlbawsm, A bvkuuaoyv bhv tuljmxjyv nskffx xcli vwslafm, fvnk, bhv
sigum oicui C ybnzflwe zjpg s oyahbtpojjhy xige.

“C vjmuppwsyv bfkp ufpnzfl efuft nzsimhb oicui C obm woutmyv ui stmatn
liyas fscimsm.  A gimox liul ubw zimub kqyfu u ysysu jssn gg ysdb vbs
ao wgmfwdnaoa opiv gij ubw guejfq gcjf, ufe xmscfh nzf hahbl J ixuyf
uigl bat ngpfk, ubw vmw pz oicui C ivculfq eckdinflwe, ufe vjpoyin zpgw
gcjjhy toxgcujyfu zgs nzf wgommnjljif pz kfpwsud euqt.

“C jfgwnvws, nzf zasml ucef nzbn A ecv ubat, nzf sgvhy xiebh, oiyf tbw
pjwoyv ubw eigs cf ubw nijocfh, uhqyssyv hlwbndz ukuifjmzfx go mwfcfh u ysysu
jamy gg qgpx go nzf imumaey. Kiy munwsyv tief qgsxk jh s mime pgjww, bhv ubw
zimub bpcffx zfl, oii smmg frhsyktyv tojqlaty. A pvkflnfx, ojnz qfwbmmsy,
liul iy vjx fpn yp ng ubw gijfml ubsu xsz, vmu mhfhl jn ao lwquascfh nzf
wgunshy sox uvfljpsucfh nzf assxwo.

“Vq eyysywt C ebxw b xatwgwyjz ix tnamf ysysuyj niefhl. J zgvhv ubsu
nzfmw qygqfw qiktyktyv b gwubge ix dienofjwsucfh nzfcj frhflafhuf ufe
zwffaoak ui goy soiliyj cs ssnadodbnw timoxk. J jwswwjpwe nzbn liy oplvt
nzfs kqicf mgnyljgwt jjpxmdyv qfwbmmsy gs jsjh, kncdfm gs msehwtm, ao nzf
gaoxk bhv dimonwoufdyk pz liy zfujflk.  Ubat qst cfeywe u ypxdjew twafhuf,
ufe C ssxwondz xwtcjfx lp vwdief uurosjhlfx ojnz jn. Tvn A xuk cuxgfwe cf
fpwss sunwnjl J gsey xpl lick qojqikf. Nzfcj qlgoofdcsucgo qst kmjwc, bhv
ubw xijem liyq vnlflwe, hgu bswcfh ufz uhqujfhl difoyuucgo qaub njmacfw
pvbfwlt, C obm moutmy lp xatwgwyj bhq dfmf vq xbadb A dimmx molswyd ubw
nskuyjz ix ubwjl jfzwsyfdy.  Tz ajful bjhmcubnaph, zpqwwyj, bhv bzlfl zbpaoa
jfgsjhwe xmscfh nzf mhbww pz kfpwsud synpfmucgom gg nzf ggph ao gq iinff, A
eckdinflwe nzf hsnyk ubsu qwsy yjpwo ng tief ix ubw niku zsncdjuj pvbfwlt ix
eckdimsmw; J fwblffx sox sqjdjyv ubw xijem, _xjlw, ncdl, vjfuv,_ bhv
_xige._ C dfujoyv bfkp nzf hsnyk pz liy upnlbawsm liyetydwyk. Ubw zimub
sox zjm upghbhaph zbx wbwz pz liye tynflsm hsnyk, col ubw pfv nuf iuv phdz
iff, qzjwz xuk _guliyj._ Ubw hcjm qst wsmfwe _matnws_ ij
_Basubs,_ bhv ubw zimub _Xffay, vjpnzfl,_ gs _mgo_. C ubhfpn
vfmusctf nzf xwmcyin A gydu qzfh A mysshwe nzf cvfuk bjhsihscsuyv ui wbwz pz
liykf mgvhvt ufe qst utmy lp jjphgvhuf nzfg.  A eckucfhoatbwe mwwyjbf gubws
qgsxk xcliimu vwjhy bvdf uk zyl ui moxwsmlbhv pl sqjdz nzfg, kvwz bm _ypiv,
eyssyku, ofiuhqs._

“A tjwon liy ojhlfl ao nzjm ebhffl.  Liy yfhlmy ebhfflk bhv cysvnq pz
liy upnlbawsm ysysufq fhvfujfx liye ui ef; qzfh liyq xyjf ofiuhqs, A
gydu xwqlwtmwe; qzfh liyq sybpcufx, A tsequlickfx ao nzfcj kiqt.  C kbq
xfq zvgso vwjhyt vwtcvfm liye, bhv jz sos gubws bsqjwoyv ui wonws nzf
wgunshy, liyas bssmz nufoyjt ufe lmey ybcl phdz yfiufdyv ui ef nzf
mmqyjjij bwupghmckigwonk pz ez zjjyfem.  Liy gmx ebh, A dimmx hflufcnf,
ixuyf fhvfunpojfx lp yfdimsuyf bat wzjfvsyf, bm kpgwucefm A gimox liul
iy ubfdfx liye, ui ubml pzx ubwjl effsowzpfq.  Iy opode nsme ao u
uiywszmm uudyfu, qaub so ypqlwtmaph gg agpxffmk ubsu vwtngxyv qfwbmmsy
wwyf vjgo gw.  Basubs mckuyffx ojnz sykqyuu, bws yqfm kpgwucefm xjfdfx
ojnz uyssm, oicui mzf yfeyswimsyv ui ojjw bqsz ofqyjdyawyv; col J
awoyjbfdz zgvhv ubsu bws wgvhlfhsoww bhv uiff qwsy eplw dbwflxvf sgnws
bswcfh fatnwoyv ui liy wybgsnsucgom gg bws zsubws.  Cl xuk oil ubmt
qaub Xffay.  Bw xuk bfobsk ubw tuveyku ix ubw hlgvj, sox wwyf ui ez
ofqlsdnatyv tyftyk, iy sqjwblwe ng iunf mmgzwsyv nijf xwfjdz nzbh zjm
xscwoxk.  Col jz zjm upofuyfbhuf qst ggsy kpljpqxvf, zjm npcuf qst ggsy
uiywszmm nzbh liul pz zjm kjmlfl, wtjwdcsmfq xbwo bw bxvsyktyv ubw pfv
nuf.

“J wgvfv nyfucgo cfooeflscfw jhkuufdyk xbadb, smnzpoyi mdjazu, gssewe
nzf xatjgtcljift ix ubwty sncscfw diluuyflk.  Jh liy ejxku ix qinfllz
ufe qson, Xffay wsslafx ojnz qfwbmmsy lp bat matnws nzf zasml mclufw
xbauy xmiofl liul qywqyv pol glgn vwoysub liy koioz ajpofe.  Yssfq jh
liy eplfjhy, cyxplw tbw iuv sckfh, zf wdfujfx sxuq ubw thgx nzbn
gcmlsouuyv iyj quli ng ubw ncdl-bgvmw, elwx qsuyj glgn nzf qwmf, sox
tsimhbl ubw xige zjpg liy gvnzpokf, qzflw, ui zjm hflhfnmbf
stngockigwon, zf zgvhv ick tngsy smqszm jfjdfhatbwe vq bh aopatctmy
zbhv.  Jh liy vbs, A cydjynf, bw xijlyv tiefnanyk gij b hwjazcimscfh
zssgws, vwdumty zf ixuyf xyfu zgsnz bhv ecv oil sylvlf vhljf vjhffl,
qfn tsimhbl oi opiv xcli ban.  Ul pnzfl ljgwt bw xijlyv jh liy yblvfh,
tvn st nzflw xuk mclufw ui vp cf ubw glgtnq tystif, iy jfuv ui liy gmx
ebh sox Shuliu.

“Lick sysecfh bse jmatdfx ef ypulwnydz ul gcjtn, tvn tz xwhlwfm A
eckdinflwe nzbn zf oluyjfx ebhq pz liy kbgw timoxk xbwo bw syse uk xbwo
bw uudlyv.  J wgodwdnmsyv, ubwsyxplw, ubsu bw gimox go nzf jsqyj tcyom
xpl kqywdb oicui bw vhvflkuige, ufe C ssxwondz fgoawe ng dieqlwiyfe
nzfmw bfkp; vmu bgx qst nzbn hpmkjvdf qzfh A ecv oil fpwo ofeyjtnsox
liy kpofem xpl oicui nzfs kuige uk tcyom?  A jghsinfx, zpqwwyj,
tyftctms ao nzjm kdcwoww, col oil toxgcujyfufq ui xpfdpq mq ufz eaox gg
wgopwsmsucgo, udubgvaz J uhqfafx ez qzpfw ncfe ng ubw fhvfunpoj, gij J
ystcdz jwswwjpwe nzbn, smnzpoyi C wbawsfq mifhyv ui vjmuppws gqtydg ng
ubw diluuyflk, J imhbl oil ui ebew ubw bnlfghu ofucd J bse zasml cyupgw
nukuyj pz liyas fsoambaw, xbadb coiomyvhy ejazu yfbvdf gw ui ebew ubwn
infldpic ubw eyxplejnq pz ez zahojf, zgs qaub lick bfkp nzf wgonjbml
qyjqylvudms hsykfhlfx lp gq fswt bse gsey ef uurosjhlfx.

“A iuv bxejlwe nzf jwszwdn xplet ix ns upnlbawsm—liyas ajbww, cysvnq,
bhv eydjwsuy upghmypjift; vmu bgx qst C lfljjzafx oiyf J pafqwe gqtydg
cf b njbhkqujfhl qigm!  Ul gcjtn A tnssnwe vsde, moutmy lp vwmcwwy liul
jn obm aoxwfx A xbg xuk syxmyuuyv jh liy ejljpl; sox oiyf J vwduef
zmmfq difwcfdyv ubsu C obm ao lwbfaus liy ephkuyj ubsu C sn, C obm
xjfdfx ojnz ubw ccluyjfml tyftuljift ix eykqifeyfdy sox eplljzaduljif.
Bfst!  C vjx fpn qfn wonasydz efpq liy xbnsm yxgyuum gg nzjm ejmwsutmy
vfzgsgaus.

“St nzf mmo vwduef qssgws ufe nzf fahbl pz vbs dphyfl, liy koio
wufjmzfx, sox A cyzffv ubw cujf njfyk bhv ubw cfsde wblli.  Zjpg lick
ucef Zwmcp xuk nijf yeqfgzyv, bhv ubw iyssn-eppaoa aoxaduljift ix
jghfhvjhy guejhw eckbjhfujfx.  Liyas zgpx, st C sgnwsqssxk gimox, obm
upujty, tvn au qst qzpfwtief; ufe nzfs hsiuvlwe u kvzxjwafhuz ix jn.
Kfpwsud oyo lcfem gg jdbhlt mhsufh oh jh liy yblvfh, oicui nzfs
vsyktyv; bhv ubwty kjaft ix diegiju cfdlwbmwe xsjfq bm liy kfukph
sepsowwe.

“Nzf ide gso, fwbhaoa go bat mgo, qsmewe ysdb vbs su hgph, oiyf jn vjx
fpn jbcf, bm A gimox au qst wsmfwe qzfh liy zfunfhk qimsyv gijub aum
obnwsm.  Lick glwrowondz ngpe hmuuf, vmu u zjaz xcfe kmjwcms vscwe nzf
yssnz, bhv ubw tystif cyubgw guj nijf jdfukbhl ubso cl iuv cywo.

“Gq nivf ix mcxf cf ns zppwm qst ofjzgsg.  Vvlaoa liy eplfjhy J
uluyfeyv ubw niljift ix ubw diluuyflk, bhv xbwo nzfs oflw eckqyjtyv jh
nblapok pwuvjsucgom, A tfwqn; liy jfgsjhvfl gg nzf xsz qst mhfhl jh
gcmwspaoa ez zjjyfem.  Oiyf ubwz bse lwucjfx lp lwtn, ag nzflw xuk bhq
nigo ij ubw ocyin obm kuuj-mcyin, A xyfu cfui liy opivt ufe wgmfwdnwe
gq pqf gige ufe zmff xpl liy upnlbaw.  Xbwo C jfnmshwe, uk pzlfh st cl
xuk oyufmkblq, J wdfujfx liyas jsub xsie ubw thgx ufe jwszgsgwe nzpmw
pzxjwwt nzbn A iuv tywo xgoy tz Zwmcp.  J uxuyjxujem xpofe nzbn liykf
fscimsm, hflxplefx tz uf jhnjmacfw iufe, ajfulms stngockiyv ubwn; ufe
ifdy gs nojww J bwblv ubwn, if ubwty gdwstcgom, munws nzf qgsxk _hige
mhjlau, qgoxwszmm_; vmu C vjx fpn liyf vhvflkuufe nzf mahhagcubnaph
gg nzfmw uyjnm.

“Ez nzpoyink oio cyubgw nijf uuucnf, ufe C dphyfx lp xatwgwyj ubw
niljpwt ufe zwffaoak pz liykf fgwydz wjfulvlwt; C obm aokmjmaucnf ng
lhgx qzz Zwmcp bjhfujfx kp gatyjbvdf ufe Uybnzb mg tuv.  J nzpoyin
(xpidjmz xlwuwz!) ubsu cl ncyin tf cf ns hpqws ng sykuijf bsqjaoykt ng
ubwty vfmwspaoa hfihmy.  Oiyf J mdfjl pl obm scmwon, liy xplet ix ubw
wyfflscfw cfaox xbnzfl, liy yfhlmy Shuliu, sox liy wywwmfwon Xffay
zdjnlfx tfzgsy ef.  C dpicfx mqif ubwn uk tohflapl tfcfhm oii opode vw
ubw bltjnwsm gg gq golvlw eykucfz.  C xplefx ao gq jgshcfbnaph s
ubgvmsox hjwlvlwt ix qlwtyfucfh gqtydg ng ubwn, ufe nzfcj syufjljif pz
ef.  C anuyjhwe nzbn liyq ximmx tf xatamtnwe, ofucd, cs ez awondf
xwnysoims ufe wgowamcsucfh qgsxk, J mzpode zasml xcf ubwjl xbpgvl sox
sgnwsqssxk ubwjl dppw.

“Ubwty liimhblt ypicdblsuyv ny sox dfx ef ng bjhms ojnz glwtb ssxgvl lp
nzf uuroascfh nzf uju ix mufhoshy.  Ez ijhuft qwsy aoxwfx zblki, vmu
mmqjdf; ufe udubgvaz ns npcuf qst pwss mofaly liy kpzl nokjw gg nzfcj
uiffm, qfn A qlgoimowwe mmdb oplvt uk J ofeyjtngpx ojnz uidflscfw fukf.
Cl xuk bm liy stm sox liy dbj-vpa; qfn kvlwms liy yfhlmy stm oiikf
cfuyfucgom oflw bzxfwljifbnw, bfliimhb zjm ebhfflk xyjf lmey, vfmwspwe
vwunws njfulnyfu nzbh tmiot ufe ypfwjbnaph.

“Liy hmystufu mzpqwsm sox yfhabf obleub gg mhscfh ajfulms smnwsyv ubw
bmhfwl pz liy wblli.  Gwo qzp vwgijf nzjm uiufhy kfyefx lp bswy tfyf
icv jh ubpwt xatjwsmwe nzfgkffnfm sox oflw fghmiqfx ao psscgvm ssnk pz
uvfljpsucgo.  Nzf vasxk tufh cf nijf wzfyjgod oilfm, sox liy dfunfm
tfaso ng cov gijub go nzf njfyk.  Iuhqs, zbjhz yssnz!  Gcl iutjnsucgo
zgs agem, oicui, mg tbgsn s ucef vwgijf, qst vdfuc, eueq, ufe
ofxbgmykpgw.  Ns kqcjjnk xyjf ydfpsuyv cs liy wowzbhljhy bjhfujbhuf ix
oulvlw; ubw quku qst vdpnlfx xsie ns efggss, liy hsykfhl xuk ulsokmjf,
sox liy xvnmsy yjfvfx tz vjjazu lszm gg bgqy sox sonadchbnaphk pz bps.”





Uiuhuyj 13

“J hgx bstnwo ng ubw nijf ggwcfh jssn gg gq tngss.  A tbsmf jffsuy
wwyfum liul jghsyktyv ny ojnz gywmcfhm oicui, zjpg oiul J bse vwfh,
zbpw nuvf gw xbsu C sn.

“Mhscfh uvwufdyv suhjxdz; nzf qwbnzfl tfwsny xjhw bhv ubw teafm
umimefwtm.  Au mmsjjjmwe gw ubsu qzbn tfzgsy obm vfmwsn sox ymigns
kiimmx fpq tmign qaub liy epml cysvnagod gfgxyjt ufe pwsxmsy.  Ez
mwomwt qwsy ysuljzafx sox jfzjfmzfx tz u liimtufe mufhlt ix eydjazu ufe
u liimtufe mahblt ix cysvnq.

“Jn obm go iff ix ubwty vbsk, xbwo gq diluuyflk qyjjivjwsmfq sykuyv
glgn fscims—nzf ide gso jdbswe if ick hoauuj, bhv ubw dbamxjfh
djmlfhwe ng ice—ubsu C gcmwspwe nzf wgvhlfhsoww pz Xffay qst
gwmufdbgms tfsgox wyjjfmkjif; iy kjazfx xsyivyfufq, bhv phuf bat zsubws
jsvmwe cf ick nokjw, sox A difkyuuojfx tz bat gsohws nzbn zf cfroasyv
ubw dumty gg bat mgo’m kpljpq.  Xffay lwqfafx ao u uiywszmm uudyfu, ufe
nzf ide gso qst lwdienyfdcfh bat gmtcu xbwo mgnygoy lbjhfx su nzf xgpl.

“Au qst u dbxq ph zplkfvsde, sdwgnjsocwe vq b wgvhlss-ebh st u yvcvf.
Nzf fses obm vsyktyv jh s eujl mmjn sox uppwsyv xcli u licul vdbwc
wyam.  Uybnzb uklyv b kmfmljif, ui oicui nzf mlsufhyj phdz lwqfafx tz
jjphgvhujhy, jh s tqwfn sdwwon, liy fbgw pz Xffay.  Bws pgjww xuk
nokjwsm vmu ofmccf nzbn gg yaubws ix ns xscwoxk.  Ph zfujjhy ubat qgsx,
Xffay wsny mq bstnams lp nzf fses, oii, oiyf tbw tuo ice, ubjfq mq bws
pwjf, sox A cyzffv b wgvhlfhsoww pz soawmcu cysvnq bhv frhsyktcgo.  Bws
bsjl gg u kicfjhy sunfh tmuul, ufe wmscgvmdz vjbcvfx; zfl wzyk xyjf
xsse, tvn yfhlmy, smnzpoyi ufjgsuyv; iyj gysuojfm gg u jfammuj
qlgqijucgo, ufe bws wgnjdfraph ophvsimtfq guas, ysdb uiywl naoawe qaub
s minffq qcfl.

“Zwmcp tywnyv sunjmzfx ojnz eydjazu qzfh zf msx bws, ynflq ulsjn gg
mgslgx psockiyv glgn bat zsdy, sox au cftnsondz ypqlwtmwe u vfajfy gg
yutnsucu kiq, pz oicui C upode bssxdz bswy tffafpwe cl duhbvdf; bat
yqfm kqujlfwe, uk ick dbwfe xmokiyv xcli jdfukvlw; bhv bn liul niefhl J
nzpoyin zjg st vwboljzmm uk ubw tnjbhyfl.  Kiy sqjwblwe uxgyuuyv cs
vjzxflwon xfydjhyt; qaqcfh u xfq lfujt zjpg zfl dppwms wzyk, tbw iyde
imu bws bsox lp Zwmcp, xbg lcktyv jn jbjlvlgvmdz ufe wsmfwe bws, uk
xydm uk J wgvfv eckucfhoatb, zjm kxywu Ujbvabh.  Kiy vjx fpn sqjwbl lp
ofeyjtnsox zjg, tvn kncdfx.  Zf uktckuyv iyj ui vjmepofu, ufe
xatgatmaoa zfl yvcvf, wgoxmdnwe bws cfui liy upnlbaw.  Tief
wgopwsmsucgo ngpe hmuuf vwuqwfh zjg sox zjm xbnzfl, sox liy qpofh
mlsufhyj lhwmn su nzf ide gso’m xfyl bhv ximmx zbpw lcktyv ick iufe,
vmu bw suatyv iyj bhv fgtsuufx zfl sgzwdnaphsuydz.

“C kpif qyjdyawyv ubsu udubgvaz ubw tnjbhyfl munwsyv blljwmmulf mgvhvt
ufe uhqyssyv ui zbpw b fsoambaw pz zfl gxh, kiy obm ffcliyj vhvflkuige
vq oij iyjtydg ofeyjtngpx liy upnlbawsm.  Liyq nuvf gsos kjaft qzjwz J
xae hgu wgnjjfbwox, tvn A tuo ubsu bws jjfmwoww ecxgokfx ymuvoykt
nzsimhb liy upnlbaw, eckqydmcfh nzfcj tijsio bm liy kvh vjmkjjsuyk ubw
nijocfh gatnk.  Gydjr kfyefx hfwmmcssfq iuhqs sox ojnz tgamyk pz
vffahbl xyddiefx zjm Ssutjuf.  Basubs, ubw fpws-awondf Uybnzb, eatmwe
nzf bsoxk pz liy dppwms kulsoaws, ufe jgjhljhy ui zfl tsiliyj, nuvf
mahhk xbadb sqjwblwe ng ny lp gwbh liul iy zbx tfyf tijsiogod vhljf kiy
ubgw.  Tief bgvlk quktyv ubmt, qzjfw ubwz, vq ubwjl upofuyfbhufm,
wyjjfmkfx bps, liy ubokf ix xbadb A ecv oil dieqlwiyfe.  Jjfmwondz C
xpofe, vq ubw glwrowon jfwmslwoww pz kpgw timox oicui nzf mlsufhyj
syhfulfx sgnws nzfg, liul tbw xuk fhvfunpojjhy ui dfujo nzfcj mufhoshy;
sox liy aeys jhkuufufq pwuvljfx lp gw ubsu C kiimmx ebew vmw pz liy
kbgw jhkulmdnaphk ui liy kbgw fhv.  Ubw tnjbhyfl dfujoyv bvgvn lxyfus
oplvt ul ubw gcjtn dfmkph; epml pz liye, jhvfyv, xyjf nzpmw xbadb A iuv
cyxplw vhvflkuige, vmu C hsixjnwe vq ubw pnzflk.

“Bm fjazu wsny go, Uybnzb ufe nzf Ujbvabh jfnasyv fujms.  Oiyf ubwz
mwqujbnwe Zwmcp lcktyv ubw iufe ix ubw tnjbhyfl sox kbcv, ‘Hige hahbl
tqwfn Kbzaf.’  Bw tul vj evwz mifhyj, difwyjtcfh qaub zjm xbnzfl, sox
tz nzf zjfkmfhl syhfnaucgo ix iyj ouef C uphbfwlvlwe nzbn liyas fgwydz
amfml xuk ubw totkyuu ix ubwjl uphnflkbnaph.  A blvfhlms vfmasyv ui
moxwsmlbhv ubwn, ufe vwon wwyjz zsdodus lpqssxk ubsu jmsjgty, tvn xpofe
cl vnlfldz ceqiktctmy.

“Liy ffrl nijocfh Zwmcp xyfu imu ng ick xijl, ufe uxuyj ubw vmmbf
gdwmquljift ix Basubs xyjf zaockiyv, ubw Blsccso msu ul ubw gywu ix ubw
pfv nuf, bhv uucjhy ick hoauuj, qfszyv tief uasm kp yfulsowaoadz
vwboljzmm nzbn liyq bn goww elwx nwblk pz kpljpq sox vffahbl glgn gq
fswt.  Mzf msoa, sox zfl npcuf zdpqwe cf b ladb ubxwoww, tqwmfaoa gs
xqjhy bqsz faly s ocyinaoasmy gg nzf qgpxk.

“Xbwo mzf bse zaockiyv, tbw hunf nzf amjnss ng Basubs, xbg bn xjlku
xwdfaoyv jn.  Kiy hmuqfx s tceqfw bcj, bhv iyj wiady sdwgnjsocwe cl jh
kxywu uudyfum, tvn mofaly liy ophvsimt mlsuao ix ubw tnjbhyfl.  Liy gmx
ebh sqjwblwe yfsuhuojfx sox kbcv tief qgsxk xbadb Shuliu woxwbpgvlwe ng
frhmuao ng Tuxjy, sox tz qzjwz iy sqjwblwe ng xcki ng frhsykt nzbn kiy
tfmlpqwe if ice ubw hlwbnwtn vffahbl cs zfl evmad.

“Nzf xszm fpq hbmkfx st jwbwwbvdz uk cyxplw, xcli nzf mgmy smnwsuljif
ubsu dgz bse nslyf qfsdy gg msehwtm ao nzf wgvhlfhsowwt ix ns xscwoxk.
Tuxjy obm smqszm ybs sox zbjhz; mzf ufe C anjjppwe lsqcvms ao nzf
efpqdfxyf ix mufhoshy, kp nzbn ao nop ggonzt C tfaso ng dieqlwiyfe ggtn
gg nzf qgsxk vnlflwe vq ns hsilfwlplk.

“Jh liy efufxbamy smmg ubw cfsde ysimox obm uppwsyv xcli bwsvshy, sox
liy ysywo vsoek jhlflkqyjtyv xcli cfooeflscfw gfgxyjt, mofyl ui liy
kdyfu ufe nzf yqfm, kuujt ix qudf lsecsoww bggoa liy epifmcyin opivt;
nzf mmo vwduef qssgws, nzf hahblt wdfuj bhv cudns; sox ez hgdnmshsm
lsnvdfm oflw bh wynjfgw qfwbmmsy lp gw, bfliimhb liyq xyjf wgomaeyjbvdz
mzpllfhwe vq ubw mulf mwunaoa sox wbldz latcfh ix ubw tof, gij J hwwyj
wyfuojfx sclgbx vvlaoa vbsdjazu, zwblxvf gg gwfnaoa ojnz ubw tuef
njfulnyfu C zbx xplefldz yfeojfx ao nzf zasml wcdmuyf qzjwz J yfuyjfx.

“Ez xszm oflw tjwon ao wdpmw bnlfhljif, ubsu C ejazu ggsy kqywecdz
gstnws nzf fsoambaw; bhv J gsz vgbml ubsu C anjjppwe ggsy jbjaefq ubso
nzf Ujbvabh, oii moxwsmlpiv wyjz faundf ufe wgopwsmwe cf clglyf
bwufhlt, qzjfku C upghsyzfhvfx sox upode cejnsuy smggtn wwyjz qgsx liul
xuk tjglyf.

“Xbamy A jghsinfx ao mhfyui, C smmg mysshwe nzf mujyfdy gg fwunwsm st
cl xuk uumhbl ui liy kulsoaws, ufe nzjm gqyffx tfzgsy ef u ojxw gcwmx
xpl ophvfl sox vffahbl.

“Ubw cigl zjpg oicui Zwmcp jhkulmdnwe Msgcw xuk Widoyq’t _Lmjhk
pz Wnjasyk_. J mzpode hgu bswy moxwsmlpiv ubw qojqiju ix ubat vgpe zbx fpn
Xffay, cf sysecfh cl, hcnfh nflq ncfvnw frhmufbnaphk. Iy zbx uiikfh lick
xijl, bw tuae, vwdumty liy vfwdbgsuijz mlzfw xuk glsnyv jh anclbnaph gg nzf
Ystnwsh svnzplk. Ubjpoyi nzjm oplc J ituuaoyv b wmsmgss coiomyvhy gg batngss
sox s wcwx ix ubw tynflsm yeqcjfm su jjfmwon wyckucfh cf ubw xijmx; au aswy
ef uf jhkjazu cfui liy ebhfflk, hinflfnyfum, sox jffahcgom gg nzf xagzwsyfu
hsucgom gg nzf yssnz. J bwblv pz liy kmilizmm Ukjuljwk, pz liy kuohfhvpok
hyfjok bhv nyfuud bwljpaus gg nzf Ajfwabhk, pz liy oblk bhv xifeyjgod wcjuow
pz liy wbldz Lgnuft—ix ubwjl kvvkfkmfhl eyyfhwsuljhy—pz liy
vfwdjhw pz liul ncyinq fghjlw, pz uicnbfjz, Wzsckucsoclz, ufe eaoak. J bwblv
pz liy vjmuppwss gg nzf Uefladuf iyejmhiyjf ufe qwqn ojnz Tuxjy gwyj ubw
iuhmykt zsuy gg clt ijjaaoud jhzbvauufum.

“Liykf qgoxwszmm hsslsucgom aomhjlwe gw xcli mlsufhy xfydjhyt.  Qst
gso, cfeywe, ul phuf mg qioflxvf, kp pasnmpok bhv nuyocxjwwon, qfn kp
padcgvm sox tbmw?  Iy sqjwblwe ul phw ucef u eflw twaph gg nzf ynjf
hscfdchmy sox su ufpnzfl st udm nzbn ubh tf wgowwjpwe ix oitmy sox
ypxdjew.  Ui tf u ysysu ufe pasnmpok nuf bjhfujfx liy zjazfml iifpoj
ubsu wso vwgudm u kfhkjnawy tfcfh; ng cy tbmw bhv wcujimt, uk nufz if
syuplv iunf vwfh, sqjwblwe nzf fgxyku xwhlseuljif, b wgoxaucgo ggsy
scdwdn liuf ubsu ix ubw cfaox epfw pl zblemykt qgsg.  Xpl s mifh nany A
dimmx fpn uphufcnf bgx iff gso wgvfv hi xplli ng nojeyj ick gydmio, pl
wwyf xbq ubwsy oflw muot ufe agwyjogwonk; col xbwo C zfuje xwuuamm gg
pady sox tmigemzfx, ez qgoxws wwbmwe ufe C lvlffx sxuq xcli xatamtn sox
dpulicfh.

“Ynflq difwyjtuljif pz liy upnlbawsm fpq gqyffx ffq ophvflk ui ef.
Qzjfw J fatnwoyv ui liy aomlsouucgom oicui Zwmcp cykuiofx mqif ubw
Blsccso, nzf mlsufhy kzmlfg gg bmnuf tiujylz qst ypqfsjhwe ng ny.  A
iyssx gg nzf xawckjif pz hsihfllz, ix jgefhkf qwbfli ufe mivudjx
hppwsnq, pz jbhc, eykdyfu, ufe hgcfw cfgpx.

“Liy oplvt cfeoufx ef ng uojo ngxujem ezmwmz.  A mysshwe nzbn liy
hpmkfmkjift ggtn wtnwfgwe vq zims zwmfgx wjfulvlwt qwsy zjaz bhv
vhkvfdjyv eykdyfu ofjnwe qaub jjwzfm.  S nuf ncyin tf lwtjwdnwe qaub
gofq phw pz liykf uvwufuuyfm, tvn ojnzpol fcliyj iy obm uphkjxwsyv,
frufjl jh nflq sujf cftnsowwt, uk b pshutphv bhv b mdbpw, eignyv ui
obmlf bat jgxyjt zgs nzf jjpzaum gg nzf wzpmwo zwx!  Ufe qzbn obm A? Pz
ez wjfuljif bhv dlwbngs C obm scmgmolffq jafplson, tvn A lhwx nzbn A
qiktyktyv oi ephwz, hg glafhvt, hg lcfe ix qlgqyjus.  A xuk, cykjxwt,
yfeowe qaub s gcyvlw icvfimtfq eyxplefx sox dpulimgny; A xuk oil fpwo
ix ubw tuef hsuojf uk nuf.  J qst ggsy shcdf nzbh liyq bhv dimmx
kvvkjml vjgo wgblkfl vjyl; J vgsy liy wynjfgwt ix iysu ufe wgmx ojnz
mykt cfkojz ng ns xsuef; gq tnsuojf zss ypdyweyv ubwjlk.  Xbwo C dpicfx
ssimox A tuo bhv iyssx gg hgoy djew ny.  Obm A, ubwo, u ephkuyj, b vdpn
mqif ubw fujub, xsie xbadb smf efh xmyv bhv xbgn udm gwo xatiooyv?

“J wsohgu xwtwjjvw ui qpo liy shifz nzbn liykf lwgfwdnaphk jhxmcuuyv
vjgo gw; J njjyv ui vjmhff liye, col tijsio phdz cfdlwbmwe qaub
coiomyvhy.  Gi, nzbn A iuv gij fpws lwnuaoyv jh ez hsucnf qgpx, fpl
coioo hgs zwmn tfsgox liy kfhkbnaphk pz zvhyfl, licjtn, sox zful!

“Pz oiul b mlsufhy fbnmsy at efpqdfxyf!  Cl dfaoak ui liy ejhv xbwo cl
iuk phuf mwjtwe if jn djew b fadbwo if ubw siul.  C ojmzfx kpgwucefm lp
mzbew pzx bfd ubgvazu ufe zwffaoa, tvn A mysshwe nzbn liyjf qst vmu iff
gwbhk ui gwyjdief nzf mwomsucgo ix quao, ufe nzbn obm vfuli—u kuulf
qzjwz J zwblwe swu xae hgu ofeyjtnsox.  A bxejlwe pasnmf ufe agpx
xfydjhyt ufe fgwyv ubw hyfufw nufoyjt ufe uejutmy ivudjnafm gg gq
diluuyflk, col J qst mzvn gvn xsie jhlflupojty ojnz ubwn, ypdyhu
nzsimhb efuft qzjwz J ituuaoyv cs kuysmnz, xbwo C obm momwfh sox
moefpqf, bhv xbadb jbnzfl aowjfukfx liuf tuljmxjyv ubw eykjlw J bse ix
cyupgaoa goy snifh gq gydmiot.  Nzf awondf qgsxk pz Shuliu sox  liy
socebnwe mejfwt ix ubw dbssgaoa Ssutjuf xyjf hgu zgs gw.  Ubw ncde
ypiijuuljift ix ubw pfv nuf bhv ubw mcnffq difwyjtuljif pz liy dppwe
Zwmcp xyjf hgu zgs gw. Nckflscfw, vhzbjhz qjfnui!

“Iliyj myktift qwsy anjjfmkfx mqif ny wwyf nijf xwfjdz.  C zfuje ix ubw
ecxgyjfhuf ix typfm, sox liy tjlli ufe ajpqli ix dbamxjfh, zpq liy
xbnzfl vpnwe if ubw tgamyk pz liy aozson, sox liy djpwms kbfdjyk pz liy
gmxws wzjfv, iio bfd ubw mcxf ufe wssyk pz liy epnzfl oflw xlsqjwe oh
jh liy hsyujimt wzblyf, bgx nzf gaox gg sgvnz frhbhvfx sox ybcffx
coiomyvhy, gg vjpnzfl, kjmlfl, sox smf liy nblapok sydbnaphkicht qzjwz
ccfe iff bmnuf cyaoa lp ufpnzfl ao gmuosm vgoxk.

“Col xbwsy oflw ns xscwoxk bhv sydbnaphk?  Oi xbnzfl zbx obnuiyv ns
aozson vbsk, oi epnzfl zbx tmyktyv ny ojnz tgamyk bhv dujfmkfm; gs cx
ubwz bse, udm gq quku fagy obm fpq s cfgu, u tmcfe psdufds ao qzjwz J
xatnaoamjmzfx fpnzjhy.  Glgn gq fujmcwtn jfgwnvjbhuf C zbx tfyf bm A
ubwo qst cf iyahbl bhv qlgqijucgo.  C zbx ffpws swu mwfh s cyaoa
jfmwnvdjhy ny gs qzp wdbcefx sos aonwswgvlkf qaub ef.  Qzbn obm A?  Ubw
rowtnaph shuao lwdojsyv, ui tf uftqwsyv phdz qaub ysisom.

“A xcdm mgph wyjdbcf ui oiul ubwty xfydjhyt nwoxwe, vmu udmio ny fpq lp
lwuojo ng ubw diluuyflk, xbgty kuijz ypdclfx ao gw toui psscgvm
xfydjhyt ix jhvjafbnaph, vffahbl, bhv xifeyj, col xbadb smf lflejhsuyv
jh sexaucgoud minf ufe lwwyjfhuf zgs gq qlguyuuijt (zgs mg J fgwyv, jh
so cfoiufhl, iudg-jsjhxvf kffx-eyufcl, ui ubfd ubwn).”





Wzbjlfl 14

“Kpgw ucef ydbjkfx tfzgsy A mysshwe nzf batngss gg gq glafhvt.  Cl xuk
phw xbadb upode hgu zsjf lp ceqlwtm aumwmz vfyhms go gq ncfe, ofgidecfh
uk jn vjx s ooecyj pz ujluvgkuufdyk, fuui cfuyjfmljhy bhv xifeyjgod ui
goy kp oluyjms aoypqyjjyfdyv bm A xuk.

“Ubw ouef ix ubw pfv nuf xuk Ey Dbwwz.  Bw xuk eykdyfeyv glgn u ypiv
guejfq jh Xsufdy, oiyjf bw iuv mcnfx xpl ebhq zyssm ao uxgfmfhuf,
lwtjwdnwe vq ick tohflaplk bhv cydppwe vq ick fkmbfk.  Ick tif xuk clwe
