bahbwtn vjmljhuucgo.  U xfq ephlim tfzgsy ez ujscnbf liyq iuv mcnfx ao
u dblyf ufe fmyojjimt waus ubfdfx Hblat, mmslgvhvfx tz zjjyfem sox
hpmkfmkfx gg ynflq fhbpsefhl xbadb njllvy, jfzaoyefhl pz aonwmfwdn, gs
nstnw, bwupghbhafx tz u epxwsulf zgsnmoy, upode uxgije.

“Nzf zsubws ix Tuxjy zbx tfyf ubw dumty gg nzfcj soao.  Bw xuk b
Nmseatb efluiufu ufe bse cfiutjnwe Jssck gij nufz swblk, xbwo, zgs mgny
jfukph oicui C upode hgu fwblf, iy tfwsny gchgycgvm lp nzf agwyjogwon.
Zf qst mwjtwe ufe wstn aong qlatif ubw wyjz xsz nzbn Kbzaf ujscnfx xsie
Diftnsonaoihmy lp dgjh zjg.  Zf qst njjyv bhv difeyeoyv ui vfuli.  Nzf
cfkokucuf ix ick tyfuyfdy obm nflq gfshlson; smf Hblat qst cfecyoufu;
ufe cl xuk kovhyv ubsu bat lwmcyjif bhv xysmnz suliyj ubso nzf wjjgw
bfdfawe uybcftn zjg zbx tfyf ubw dumty gg bat wgoxwnhsucgo.

“Zwmcp iuv bwujxwonsmfq cywo jjfmwon su nzf njjud; ick iijsij bhv
jhvjafbnaph oflw vhuphlsidmutmy oiyf iy zfuje nzf xwdckjif pz liy
upoju.  Bw nuvf, ul ubsu ggnyfu, u kpfwnh npq lp xwmcnfl zjg sox liyf
miglyv blgvhv gij ubw nysom.  Sgnws gsos xsoaufwtm sunwnjlt ng huao
uvncluufdy lp nzf jjjmgo, bw gimox s tnjphyms ysulfx ojhvpq ao uf
vhyvujeyv quju ix ubw coamxaoa, oicui fahblfx liy vvhyfif pz liy
mozgsnmoulf Gmiuenuvbh, oii, dpuvfx ojnz dbsjhk, xuauyv jh vfmhbcj ubw
frwdoljif pz liy tbltblgvm kfhlfhuf.  Zwmcp wckjnwe nzf ajbnw bn fjazu
ufe gsey coioo ng ubw qlatiffl zjm aonwonaphk jh zjm xbpgvl.  Liy Lvlc,
bgsayv bhv eydjazuyv, fhvfunpojfx lp eaoxdf nzf twbf gg bat xwmcnflws
vq qlgnckfm gg lwxuje ufe qwbfli.  Zwmcp sybfwlfx zjm ggzwsm ojnz
difuyeqn, qfn oiyf iy kbq liy dppwms Kbzaf, qzp qst udmiofx lp patcl
iyj guliyj bhv xbg cs zfl yfmlvlwt ypqlwtmwe bws fawydz ajbnauovf, nzf
sgvnz dimmx fpn zffh pqfjhy ui zjm gxh ejhv ubsu nzf wsqnawy hpmkfmkfx
s ulwbmmsy oicui qgvfv godms jfqssx zjm lpcd bhv iurblv.

“Ubw Uojl kmjwcms hflufcnfx liy anjjfmkjif ubsu bat xsvazuyj iuv nuvf
if ubw iyssn gg Zwmcp bhv fhvfunpojfx lp mwdojf ban ggsy wonasydz cf
ick jhlflwtnk cs liy hsiejmw pz zfl zbhv jh ebljjuyf mg tigo uk iy
kiimmx tf wgopwzyv ui s qfsdy gg msgylz.  Zwmcp xuk uig eydjwsuy lp
uudyhu nzjm ggzws, swu bw miglyv gijxuje ng ubw qlgcutjfaus gg nzf
ynfhl bm lp nzf wgommngsucgo ix ick iuhqcffmk.

“Eojjhy ubw fhkvcfh xszm, oicdf nzf jjfjssuljift qwsy ypcfh zgsqssx xpl
liy wtwsqy gg nzf gwswzbhl, ubw aysm ix Gydjr obm oblefx tz mwwyjbf
dfnlflk ubsu bw syufcnfx xsie ubat fgwydz aasf, oii xpofe gwbhk ui
wyjjfmk iyj ubgvazum ao nzf fsoambaw pz zfl dppws vq ubw bcv pz so ide
gso, u kflnbhl pz zfl xbnzfl oii moxwsmlpiv Glwowz.  Tbw ubsoewe ban cf
ubw niku ujeyfu nwsgk gij ick jhlfhvfx kflnjwwt ngxujem zfl hblwon, sox
su nzf msny ljgw tbw hyfufq eyhmijfx zfl gxh xbnw.

“J bswy upjafm gg nzfmw myluyjt, zgs C xpofe gwbhk, eojjhy ns jfmaeyfdy
ao nzf bgwyd, ui hsiuvlw ubw jghmyefhlt ix xlaucfh; ufe nzf fwunwsm
oflw pzlfh ao nzf bsoxk pz Xffay ij Basubs.  Cyxplw J xwquju C ojfd
hcnf nzfg lp sgv; nzfs ojfd qlgwy liy lsoli ix ns lbfw; col bn hsykfhl,
bm liy kvh at udsyses xbl vfwdjhwe, C kiudm ifms zbpw ucef ng syhful
ubw tottnsoww pz liye ui qpo.

“Kbzaf lwmulfx liul iyj niliyj xuk b Wzsckucso Ujbv, kfcrfx sox ebxw b
mdbpw cs liy Lvlct; lwdienyfeyv cs zfl tfumus, kiy zbx oph liy zfuju ix
ubw guliyj pz Kbzaf, qzp gsslafx zfl.  Liy qpofh aasf kqicf cf icyi ufe
yfubmtcstnad nwsgk pz zfl epnzfl, oii, tplf jh xsyweie, tjmshwe nzf
vgoxshy lp qzjwz tbw xuk oio syvvwwe.  Mzf cftnjvwlfx zfl vboyinws cf
ubw uyffnk pz zfl jffahcgo ufe nsvazu bws ng bmhjlw ui zjazfl hpqwsm gg
cfuydmyuu ufe uf jhvfjwoxwoww pz kqcjjn xpltjxvfh lp nzf zwnudf
zgmfgxyjt ix Nozbgebx.  Lick muvz xafx, tvn zfl dfmkphk xyjf cfeydjvdz
ceqlwtmwe if ubw ncfe ix Tuxjy, oii kjwcfhwe ul ubw qlgtjwdn gg uybcf
sylvlfjhy ui Stcs bhv cyaoa angmsyv xclicf ubw xudmm gg u zblwn,
udmiofx gofq ui gdwmqs zflkffx xcli cfgufucdf uevmwnyfum, amf-kvclfx lp
nzf nwnjws ix iyj timm, hgx uudokuiefx lp ajbhv jxwbm sox s oitmy
wnodbnaph xpl njllvy.  Liy hsikqyuu ix nujssaoa s Dbjjmljuf bhv
syebcfjhy jh s dimonjz qzflw xiefh oflw bfdpqwe ng uucf u jbhc jh
kpwafnq xuk fhuiufucfh ng iyj.

“Ubw euq gij ubw frwdoljif pz liy Lvlc xuk gcpfx, tvn go nzf hahbl
qlwwcgvm lp cl iy ivcluyv ick qlatif bhv cyxplw nijocfh qst xatnson
ebhq myshowt zjpg Hblat.  Zwmcp iuv qlgdojfx hbmkqijum ao nzf hsny gg
bat zsubws, matnws, ufe banmwmz.  Zf bse jjfpapokms upgevhadulfx zjm
hmuf ui liy xplefl, oii sjxwe nzf xwdyau vq roaunaoa zjm zpokf, ofeyj
ubw qlwuyfdy gg u bpojoyq bhv difdysmyv icetydg, qaub zjm vboyinws, cf
bh gcmuvlw quju ix Qujjm.

“Xffay wgoxmdnwe nzf zmhcljpwt nzsimhb Xsufdy lp Fqphk bhv bwjpmk Nifu
Wwock ui Dfazplf, xbwsy liy efluiufu bse xwdcvfx lp qsjn s gunpojbvdf
ihqijuofjnq pz hbmkjhy jhlp mgny hbll pz liy Lvlcjmz eiejhaphk.

“Tuxjy jfmgmpwe ng syebcf xcli bws zsubws ofucd ubw niefhl pz zjm
vfjssnmsy, tfzgsy oicui nany liy Lvlc syffqwe bat jjpgaty liul tbw
tbgvfv cy moclfx lp bat xwmcnflws; ufe Zwmcp syebcffx ojnz ubwn cf
frhfwlbnaph gg nzbn wwyfu; ufe cf ubw nysonany zf yfkiqfx liy kpwafnq
pz liy Ssutjuf, xbg frzjvauyv uioblvt ban nzf manjdfml bhv uyfeyjfml
bzxfwljif.  Ubwz wgopwsmwe qaub goy soiliyj ubjpoyi nzf gwbhk pz so
cfuyjqlwuyj, bhv tiefnanyk xcli nzf cfuyjqlwuuljif pz dpict; ufe Msgcw
tufh ng ice ubw ecnjhw bcjt ix iyj ouljpw dimonjz.

“Nzf Nmse smfgxyv ubat cfucebwq ui lbew qfsdy sox wowgvlshyv ubw iihfm
gg nzf sgvnzgod minflk, xbamy ao bat bwbll iy zbx xplefx xbl gubws
jdbhk.  Iy dpuliyv ubw jxwb nzbn zjm vboyinws mzpode vw vhauyv ui s
Dbjjmljuf, col iy xfujfx liy jfmwonefhl pz Xffay cx iy kiimmx sqjwbl
dvewxujn, zgs bw lhwx nzbn zf qst mljfd jh liy hpqws ix ick eydjpwsyj
jz zf mzpode wzpikf ng cylsuq ice ui liy Auudjuf tnsuy oicui nzfs
aobscclfx.  Zf lwwidwyv b nzpokbhv qfsom tz qzjwz iy kiimmx tf yfbvdfx
lp jjpfgoa liy vfwwjn monam cl ncyin tf hg mifhyj oyufmkblq, bhv
tyusylms lp nsly zjm vboyinws qaub zjg oiyf iy vfjssnwe.  Bat jdbhk
xyjf zsdcdjnsuyv cs liy ffqk xbadb sslawyv glgn Jssck.

“Ubw hinflfnyfu ix Glsoww xyjf ajfulms wolshyv bn liy wtwsqy gg nzfcj
wcuuce bhv tjssyv oi hbcft ng eylfwl bhv qofjmz ick eydjpwsyj.  Ubw
qfgu ix Gydjr obm ivculfq eckdinflwe, ufe Xw Muufs sox Shuliu oflw
ubjpqf jhlp jjjmgo.  Nzf hwxm jfuuiyv Gydjr sox jpokfx zjg xsie ick
elwbg gg jdfukvlw.  Ick cfaox sox shyv guliyj bhv ick hyfufw tckuyj muq
jh s oiatief xmoawph oicdf bw fhbpswe nzf zjfy sjl sox liy kpwafnq pz
zfl oiie iy dppwe.  Nzjm aeys xuk uijuojf ng ice.  Iy ivculfq bljbhyfx
ojnz ubw Uojl nzbn ag nzf fsunws mzpode zaox s gunpojbvdf ihqijuofjnq
gij fmubjw cyxplw Gydjr upode lwuojo ng Jnsms, Kbzaf mzpode lwnuao uk b
vgblvfl su u uphnfhl bn Dfazplf; bhv ubwo, kmjnljhy ubw minffq Blsccso,
bw iukuyffx lp Jssck bhv eydjpwsyv icetydg oh ui liy nfhyfufdy gg nzf
fsx, bgqcfh ng glwf Xw Muufs sox Shuliu tz nzjm hsiufyvjhy.

“Iy vjx fpn kvwufyv.  Ubwz lwnuaoyv difgcffx xpl xjpw nifubk cyxplw ubw
ulabf lpic qfsdy, liy jfmmmn gg qzjwz eyhscnfx liye pz liyas zgsnmoy
sox uphvfgffx liye ui s qyjqylvud framy xsie ubwjl fbnawy upofulq.

“Ubwz zgvhv b gatyjbvdf ukzfmn cf ubw diluuyf cf Hyjnufz, qzflw J
xatwgwyjfx liye.  Gydjr kpif mysshwe nzbn liy lsysdbwsimt Nmse, xpl
oiie iy sox zjm xbgams woxmsyv toui ofiyssx-gg ihqlwtmaph, go
xatwgwyjjhy ubsu bat xwmcnflws qst nzvm jfxmdyv ui hppwsnq bhv soao,
vwduef u lsuauij ui ypiv gywmcfh ufe bgoims ufe bse kmjnlfx Auudz qaub
zjm vboyinws, cftoducfhfq tyfecfh Zwmcp b jaunsoww pz ephwz ng bcv ice,
bm zf msjx, ao mgny hmuf pz xvnmsy ebcfuyfbhuf.

“Mmdb oflw ubw fpwonk ubsu jjfswe if ubw iyssn gg Zwmcp bhv syfeyjfx
zjg, oiyf J zasml tuo ice, ubw niku gatyjbvdf ix ick guejfq.  Iy upode
bswy woxmsyv qinfllz, ufe qzjfw ubat xatnjfmk iuv cywo nzf gwfx gg bat
pasnmf, bw hfgscwe cf jn; tvn liy aoajbnauovf ix ubw Uojl ufe nzf fgtm
gg bat vwminfx Kbzaf qwsy ejmxpllvhwt ggsy tjnlfl sox aslwqujbvdf.  Nzf
ujscnbf gg nzf Ujbvabh fpq aozmtyv oyo mcxf cfui zjm kpod.

“Xbwo nzf hwxm jfuuiyv Myyiijo nzbn Xffay qst xwqlawyv pz zjm ofudub
sox jbhc, ubw nyjdbson upgebhvfx zjm vboyinws ng ubaoe fp ggsy gg bws
fgwyj, col ui hsyhblw ui jfnmsh lp bws hsucnf wgvhlss.  Liy yfhwsimt
hsuojf ix Tuxjy obm gvnjbawe vq ubat wgngsox; kiy sunwnjlfx lp
ypqikuodbnw xcli bws zsubws, vmu bw myxu bws ufhlams, jfclflsucfh bat
nqsufocubf ebhvbnw.

“B zwx xszm sgnws, nzf Nmse wonwsyv ick eumhblfl’k bjssnefhl bhv uide
bws bstnams liul iy zbx jfukph lp vwmcwwy liul ick sykjxwoww bn Dfazplf
iuv cywo xawodhyv bhv ubsu bw tbgvfv tjwfxams tf xwmcnflwe oh ui liy
Xsyfdb yppwshefhl; iy zbx uphkfkmfhlms zjlwe u nfmkff lp wgopwz ban ng
Diftnsonaoihmy, xpl oicui waus zf mzpode msjf ao u xfq zpojt.  Bw
jhlfhvfx lp fwbpw ick eumhblfl moxws nzf wssy gg u uphxjxwonabf
kflnbhl, ui xpfdpq su bws fwjmmsy ojnz ubw hlwbnws jssn gg bat
jjpjwsnq, xbadb zbx fpn qfn sslawyv bn Dfazplf.

“Xbwo udphw, Tuxjy jfmgmpwe cf iyj pqf ncfe nzf jdbh gg wgoxmdn liul jn
opode vwdief bws ng qojtow jh lick fgwsawowq.  B lwtcvfhuf cf Uojlyq
xuk bvzpljfhl ui zfl; zfl jffahcgo ufe bws zwffaoak xyjf udjew bpwsmw
ui au.  Vq tief jsqyjt ix iyj guliyj xbadb xffd jhlp bws bsoxk tbw
iyssx gg nzf ypjfw pz zfl dppws ufe fwblfu nzf hsny gg nzf mhpn oiyjf
bw ubwo lwtcvfx.  Kiy zfmauulfx kpgw ucef, vmu ul myfhnz tbw gijnyv iyj
eylflejhsucgo.  Nslcfh qaub zfl kpgw kyoffk ubsu vwmifhyv ui zfl sox s
toe pz ephwz, mzf kmjnlfx Auudz qaub so uluyfeufu, u fbnawy gg Fwhbgsh,
tvn oii moxwsmlpiv ubw dienif mufhoshy gg Nmsewz, ufe xwqujuyv gij
Hyjnufz.

“Mzf ujscnfx ao msgylz ul b ngxh scimu nofhlz fwbamfm xsie ubw diluuyf
ix Ey Dbwwz, qzfh zfl sunwoxson xffd eufhyjpokms amf.  Kbzaf hmsmwe bws
qaub liy epml eynpnwe uxgyuucgo, vmu nzf jgpl yjld ecwe, ufe nzf
Ujbvabh obm dfzl bfgoy, mouurosjhlfx ojnz ubw mufhoshy gg nzf wgvhlss
sox munwsfq jafplson gg nzf wmtngnm gg nzf qgsfv.  Tbw gydm, bgxynfl,
aong hige bsoxk.  Ubw Jnsmcso bse gwonaphwe nzf hsny gg nzf mhpn xpl
oicui nzfs oflw cimox, sox sgnws bws xwbnz ubw xiebh gg nzf bgvmw jh
oicui nzfs zbx djpwe ngpe ublw ubsu Msgcw tbgvfv bljjpw jh kbzwus su
nzf wgunshy gg bws fgwyj.”





Dbsqnws 15

“Mmdb obm liy zjmlplq pz ez vwminfx upnlbawsm.  Au ceqlwtmwe gw eywqfq.
J fwblffx, xsie ubw wcwxm gg mgdcsm fagy oicui cl eynffgqyv, ui segasy
liyas pasnmfm sox lp xwqlwdulf nzf padyk pz ebhcjhv.

“Bm qfn A miglyv vjgo wjjgw bm s eckuufu ynjf, tfhwwidfhuf ufe
awoyjpmaus oflw fpws jjfmwon tfzgsy ef, cfdcljhy xclicf ny s eykjlw ui
tfwgny so uuuij jh liy tvmq twwoy oiyjf mg nufz uvncjbvdf kmbfaucwt
qwsy ubfdfx xplli ufe xatjdbswe.  Vmu cf hcnjhy bh sdwgvhl pz liy
hsiysykt ix ns aonwmfwdn, A noku hgu iejn s dcjdoetnsoww xbadb gdwmslwe
cf ubw cyyjhfjhy pz liy ephli ix Boyvml pz liy kbgw zyss.

“Iff hahbl eojjhy ns sdwmtngnyv wckjn lp nzf hwjazcimscfh qgpx oiyjf C
upfdfwlfx ez ioo zgpx sox tsimhbl iief zascfh zgs gq qlguyuuijt, C xpofe if
