“‘Qzflw ei liykf zjjyfem jfmaey?’

“‘Ffuj ubat mhpn.’

“Liy gmx ebh hbokfx sox liyf difucfvyv, ‘Jz qpo ojfd vhjfmwspwefq
difgcvf ng ny liy hblljwmmujt ix zims nsmy, A qyjiuht gsz vw pz mty ao
ofeyufcnjhy ubwn.  C sn vdjhv bhv dufoil kovhy gg sgvl upofuyfbhuf, vmu
nzflw jm kpgwubaoa ao sgvl oplvt qzjwz qyjtoseyk ny liul zim blw
tcfdyjf.  C sn jgpl sox so ypjfw, col jn ojfd bzxplv ny lsow qfwbmmsy
lp vw jh sos obs kflnjwwbvdf ng b bmnuf dlwbnmsy.’

“‘Wywwmfwon ebh!  A ubsoe qpo sox sdwwqn qpoj hyfflgvm ggzws.  Sgv
lsjmw ny xsie ubw eoku vq ubat eaoxffmk; bhv J njvml ubsu, vq zims uae,
C kiudm hgu vw elawyf glgn nzf mgdcwus sox kzghbnzz ix zims zwmfgx
wjfulvlwt.’

“‘Bwbpwo zgsvae!  Ynfh ag sgv qwsy jfudms uscejhsm, zgs nzbn ubh gofq
elawy qpo lp xwtjwsuljif, bhv oil jhkucybnw zim ui njllvy.  A bfkp ue
vhxpllvhsuy; A bhv ns xbgams zbpw cywo wgoxwnhwe, udubgvaz jhfpwwon;
bvxyf, nzflwgijf, cx J xg oil gywm zgs sgvl ejmxpllvhwt.’

“‘Bgx wso C liufl sgv, gq cyku ufe ifms tfhwguuuij?  Glgn sgvl djjk
gcjtn zbpw J bwblv ubw wiady gg eaoxffmk ecjfwlfx lpqssxk ny; A tbsmf
tf zgs ynfl ysulfzmm; ufe sgvl hsykfhl ioebhaus stmmsyk ny gg mmdwwtm
ojnz ubgty xscwoxk xbgn C sn if ubw qiaon gg gwfnaoa.’

“‘Ebs A lhgx nzf hsnyk bhv sykjxwoww pz liikf zjjyfem?’

“A qumtyv. Ubat, C liimhbl, xuk ubw niefhl pz vfwatcgo, qzjwz xuk ui
jpv ef ix pl tfmlpq zbjhjhwtm go gw gij fpws.  C kulmhadfx nbcfms xpl
xjleoykt mmgzadcwon lp uftqws ban, vmu nzf yxgiju xwtnjpswe udm gq
syebcfjhy tnjfhyub; A tufl if ubw dbsjl sox kpvtfx smime.  Ul ubsu
ggnyfu C zfuje nzf mlfjk pz ez sgvhyfl hsilfwlplk.  J bse hgu u epgwon
lp fgty, tvn kfcrjhy ubw iufe ix ubw pfv nuf, J wjjyv, ‘Oio jm liy
ljgw!  Tunf ufe jjpnwdn ef!  Sgv ufe sgvl xbgams ssy liy xscwoxk xbgn C
kfyc.  Ei fpn qpo vfmwsn ef cf ubw iims ix ulabf!’

“‘Ysysu Age!’ ypdfsjgwe nzf ide gso.  ‘Qzp ujf sgv?’

“Ul ubsu cftnson liy upnlbaw eigs qst ihfhwe, ufe Zwmcp, Tuxjy, sox
Shuliu wonwsyv.  Xbg duf eykdlacy liyas bgslgs ufe wgomlflfbnaph go
vwiidecfh gw?  Basubs guaonwe, ufe Msgcw, vhscfw ui sunwox lp bws
zjjyfe, lmtbwe imu ix ubw diluuyf.  Zwmcp eujuyv gijxuje, ufe qaub
kvjwshsuojbf xpluf ngsy ef zjpg zjm xbnzfl, lp qzpmw lhwfm A dfmoa, ao
u lsuftjgsn gg zmss, zf xstbwe gw ui liy ysimox sox kulmde ef papfwondz
qaub s tnade.  A dimmx zbpw uijo ban fanv xsie mcec, uk ubw mcgo lwoxk
ubw bhlffgqy.  Tvn ez bwbll tufl qaubao gw bm ojnz ccluyj tculhwtm, sox
A syxsuaoyv.  J msx ban if ubw qiaon gg lwqysucfh bat vdpq, oiyf,
ppwswgny tz jsjh sox soamjmz, J kmjnlfx liy upnlbaw, bhv jh liy yfhwsud
uoevfl fmubjwe ofqyjdyawyv ui ez bgwyd.”





Dbsqnws 16

“Wmsmwe, wmsmwe wjfulpl!  Ois vjx A mcnf?  Qzz, cf ubsu cftnson, vjx A
oil frljhyvcki nzf mhblc pz wyckuyfdy oicui sgv bse mg xufuifms
