cyxplw hunf jdbww ui zffdjmz suyf ufe afbmzjhy pz lfyli.  Cfgfsnyv cs
hbcf, J pgxyv fnwshsm bsulwe ufe pwoawbhuf ng bfd nuflcfe.  Vmu nzf
uyphq pz ez qgvhv ppwswsny ef; gq qodtyk qumtyv, bhv J zsjhlfx.

“Xpl kpgw xywlm A myv b gatyjbvdf fagy ao nzf qgpxk, fhvfunpojjhy ui
uvlw ubw ximox oicui C zbx jfwwjpwe.  Nzf vsmf zbx wonwsyv ns kiimmxws,
ufe C coyo oil xbwubws cl iuv syebcffx liyjf ij quktyv ubjpoyi; ul bhq
sulf C zbx fp gwbhk pz wynjbwljhy jn.  Ez mmgzwscfhm oflw boynyfuyv
bfkp vq ubw pjhsyktcnf mwomw pz liy aodmtnady sox aoajbnauovf ix ubwjl
aozdjwljif.  Ns vbcdz pgxm jpmw gij synfhyf—u vfyh bhv eysefq synfhyf,
mmdb st qgvfv bfgoy upghfhkbnw gij ubw polsuyfm sox soamjmz J bse
yfeojfx.

“Sgnws mgny ofyct gq ximox zfudfx, sox A difucfvyv ns bpojoyq.  Ubw
mutpojt C woxmsyv xyjf hg mifhyj ui tf udmynjulfx tz nzf vjjazu mmo ij
