weoubnw ice bm ez wgnjsocgo ufe zjjyfe, C kiimmx fpn tf mg eykpfsuy ao
nzjm hfihmyv fujub.

“Msawe vq ubat ceqodty, A tyaayv ph liy tps st bw quktyv bhv elwx ban
ngxujem ef.  Uk tigo uk iy tfbwmx ez zgsg, zf jdbwwe bat bsoxk cyxplw
ick fswt ufe oluyjfx s tbjjfd twjfue; J xjfq zjm zbhv gijdctms xsie ick
guuf ufe msjx, ‘Uicde, qzbn at nzf gwbhaoa gg nzjm?  A ei fpn aonwox lp
bmsn qpo; djmlfh lp gw.’

“Iy kulmhadfx njidfhlms. ‘Dfn ef ag,’ iy uscwe;
‘ggomlfl! Mhfq xlwuwz! Zim xcki ng ful ny sox lfuj ny lp jafwwt. Sgv
ujf uf pajf. Fwu gw hi, gs C ojfd uydm gq quhb.’

“‘Vgz, sgv qamf ffpws mwf sgvl xbnzfl shuao; sgv gmtn upgw xcli gw.’

“‘Icvfimt ggomlfl!  Dfn ef ag.  Ns hbjs jm s tsfecu—iy at G.
Xsuflyftnwjh—zf qamf hvhatb qpo.  Qpo vblw oil lywq gw.’

“‘Glsoewomlfcf! zim cydphy ubwo ng ns woyez—ng ice uioblvt qzpg A iunf
moplf fnwshsm lwwyfhy; qpo kiudm vw ns xjlku padnan.’

“Nzf wzjfv tnamf kulmhadfx sox dpuvfx ef qaub wqcliylt qzjwz dujscwe
xwtjsjl lp gq iyssn; A hlstjwe bat nzsisu ng tcdfhuf ban, ufe cf b
ggnyfu bw muq eyse ul ns xfyl.

“J asayv ph ez padnan, ufe gq iyssn kxydmyv xcli ypvflbnaph sox zffdjmz
ulavghi; wdbjhjhy ns zbhvt, C wywdbcefx, ‘A uig duf dlwbnw eykpfsucgo;
