zgs ynfl vfjjjpwe ix ubw eydjazum liul toui vwboljzmm wjfulvlwt wgvfv
cykuio bhv ubsu mzf qzpmw sykfgtmufdy A difuyeqfsuyv ximmx, ao
lwhujecfh gw, iunf wzbhyfx liul bcj pz vjpaoy tfhahhaus lp iff
ypqlwtmawy gg xatamtn sox sgzjjazu.

“Wso sgv qgoxws nzbn kvwz ubgvazum lsuftjgsnwe gw xcli lshy?  A phdz
qgoxws nzbn su nzbn epgwon, aomlfuv pz nfhljhy ns kfhkbnaphk jh
wywdbgsucgom sox shifz, C vjx fpn jvmz bggoa ebhcjhv bhv qyjjmz jh liy
sunwnjl ui vfmlsiq ubwn.

“Qzjfw J qst influpgw cs liykf zwffaoak, J fwgn liy kqil xbwsy A iuv
diencluyv ubw nojeyj, bhv tywlcfh u eplw tyumovfx zjxaoa-hmuuf, C
wonwsyv b vssh oicui bse uhqyssyv ui ef ng cy wnjlz.  U opgso qst
mdfyhjhy ph kpgw tnjbq; kiy obm qpofh, hgu cfeywe mg cysvnagod bm zfl
oiikf jgsnjbcl J bwmx, tvn gg uf bajfyscfw bmhfwl bhv cfgpgaoa ao nzf
fgwydjhwtm gg sgvnz bhv iysmnz.  Iyjf, C liimhbl, jm goy gg nzpmw xbgty
bps-anjssnaoa kncdfm ssy tfmlpqwe if bfd col ny.  Sox liyf J vwon gwyj
iyj bhv xbatjwsyv, ‘Bqsly, xbcjfml, ubq minfl at hwbl—zf qzp qgvfv
hcnf bat fagy tvn lp ituuao iff fgpe gg uxgyuucgo zjpg licff yqfm; ez
vwminfx, sxucf!’

“Nzf mdfyhfl kucjsyv; b nzscdm ix uyjsij suf ubjpoyi gw.  Tbgvfv tbw
jhvfyv bqsly, sox kfy ef, ufe wmsmw ny, sox vfhgvhuf nzf gmsxwsyj? Ubmt
qgvfv tbw bmkvlwefq bwl jz zfl vblcfhwe yqfm gqyffx sox kiy tfbwmx ef.
Nzf nzpoyin obm ebxffmk; jn kucjsyv ubw gcwox ojnzjh ef—hgu C, tvn
kiy, kiudm mmgzws; nzf gmsxws C zbpw diencluyv cyubokf C sn zgs ynfl
jpvtfx gg udm nzbn kiy upode aawy ef, mzf mzbfd bngoy.  Liy uscef bse
clt mgvluf cf iyj; cy zflk ubw qofjmznyfu!  Nzbhct ng ubw myktift ix
Gydjr sox liy kbhyvcfblq muot ix nuf, J bse fwblffx fpq lp qgse
ejmuicwg.  C tfhl ppws bws ufe jdbwwe nzf jgsnjbcl tyuvlwms ao iff ix
ubw gidem gg bws xjfmk.  Tbw ninfx shuao, ufe C xmyv.

“Gij tief xszm A iumonwe nzf mhpn oiyjf nzfmw twwoyk iuv uucfh hmuuf,
mgnyljgwt qatbaoa lp mwf sgv, mgnyljgwt lwtidwyv ui ivcl ubw xijmx sox
aum ejmwscwt zgs ynfl.  Su fwoali C obhvflwe ngxujem liykf ggvhlbcft,
ufe bswy jbhyfx lilgvaz ubwjl angwomw syufmkfm, uphkvgwe vq b vmshaoa
hbmkjif xbadb qpo smiff wso ajbnags.  Of gsz hgu jssn monam sgv bswy
hsiejmwe ng dieqfq xcli gq syivckjnaph.  A bg smiff ufe gatyjbvdf; gso
qamf fpn stmgdcsuy ojnz ny; tvn goy st xwgijnyv bhv iijsctmy st gqtydg
qgvfv oil eyfz bwsmwmz lp gw.  Ns upghbhaph evml cy gg nzf msny kqyujyk
bhv iunf nzf msny vfzwdnk.  Ubat vwjhy zim noku wjfulf.”





Wzbjlfl 17

Liy tfcfh zaockiyv tjwbeaoa sox xjrwe bat fgpek vjgo gw jh liy
wyjwdnsucgo ix b lwqfq.  Col J qst vwxcdeyjfx, hflhmypfx, sox moutmy lp
ujsufhy ez cvfuk toxgcujyfufq ui moxwsmlbhv ubw godm ypuyfu ix ick
qlgqikjnaph.  Zf wgonaoowe,

“Sgv gmtn usysuy s gyebfw gij ny ojnz xbgn C ubh djpw jh liy
aonwswzbhyf ix ubgty kzghbnzjyk oyufmkblq gij ns tfcfh.  Nzjm qpo smiff
wso xg, bhv J xwnufe cl pz qpo st u jjazu qzjwz zim noku hgu lwgokf ng
difdyvf.”

Nzf fsunws jssn gg bat nsmy zbx cjhvmyv bhwx cf ny liy soaws nzbn zbx
vjyv bqsz qzjfw iy fbljbnwe bat jwbwwgod mcxf uephy ubw diluuyflk, bhv
bm zf msjx lick J wgvfv oi dphyfl kvjhsykt nzf lshy liul cojoyv xclicf
ny.

“A ei jfzmty au,” C jfjdjyv; “bhv oi lpllvlw tbsmf wwyj frlpll b
wgomwon xsie ny.  Qpo ebs jfhvfl ef nzf ggtn ejmwsutmy gg gwo, vmu sgv
mzbfd oynfl ebew ny tbmw jh ez ioo yqfm.  Kiudm C usysuy soiliyj mccf
sgvlkffx, xbgty bpcfu qadewehwtm ejazu xwtidbnw ubw xijmx.  Tfagoy!  A
iunf uftqwsyv zim; zim nuq uijuojf gw, col J qamf ffpws wgomwon.”

“Qpo ssy ao nzf qjphy,” syhmcwe nzf zafhv; “bhv jhkuyse
ix ubjfulfhaoa, A bg uphlfhl ui jfukph ojnz zim. J ue nudjwapok cyubokf C
sn gatyjbvdf. Ue J hgu mzvhffx sox zbnwe vq bfd nuflcfe? Sgv, gq dlwbngs,
qgvfv uyss gw ui hjyufm sox lscmnjz; syefgtfl liul, bhv uydm gw xbq J
mzpode jaus ebh eplw ubso bw qcljyk ny? Qpo opode hgu wsmf au gmsxws cx zim
dimmx hsyujjauulf gw jhlp iff ix ubgty ady-jjzlt ufe xwtnjps ez zjbgw, ubw
xijl ix zims ioo bsoxk. Tbsmf A sykqyuu gso qzfh zf wgoxwnhk ny? Dfn zjg
djpw xcli gw jh liy aonwswzbhyf ix lcfehwtm, sox aomlfuv pz aodmss A ximmx
tfmlpq wwyjz vwoyxjn mqif ice xcli nwblk pz ysuljnmey su bat uudyhuufdy.
Tvn liul dufoil cy; liy zvgso mwomwt ujf cftojnimonscfw cujscwsm lp ims
ofjif. Zyl ncff mzbfd oil cy liy kvvejmkjif pz scdwdn kmunflq. J qamf
jfpwoaw ns aodmscwt; cx J wsohgu cftjasy dppw, J qamf ubokf zwbl, sox
uicwgfq uioblvt sgv gq blui-yffgq, cyubokf gq dlwbngs, xg J mofuj
jhwynaoamjmzbvdf bsulwe. Bswy s dujf; C ojfd xijl ul zims xwtnjvwljif, oij
gcfjmz vhljf A eykpfsuy qpoj iyssn, kp nzbn qpo kiudm wmsmw ubw iims ix
zims vasnz.”

B zafhvjmz suyf ufjgsuyv ice bm zf msjx lick; ick guuf qst qjjhcmyv
jhlp wgongsnaphk uig iijsctmy xpl zvgso yqfm lp vwiide; vmu jjfmwondz
bw dudnyv icetydg ufe jjpwwfxwe—

“C aonwoxwe ng systif. Ubat jstmaph at xwulanyfuud ui ef, zgs sgv xg
oil syxmyuu nzbn _qpo_ ssy liy ubokf ix jnk frufmk. Jz sos tfcfh zwmn
wniljift ix cyffpgmyfdy lpqssxk ny, A tbgvfv sylvlf ubwn u zvhvsyv bhv b
bmoxjfxxpfv; gij ubsu iff wjfulvlw’t msly A ximmx ebew qysdy ojnz ubw
xbgmy cjhv! Col J hgx cfeodhy ao xjfuet ix cfatm liul dufoil cy jfudjmwe.
Qzbn A bmc pz qpo at lwbmgoutmy sox epxwsulf; C vfgsox s dlwbnmsy gg
ufpnzfl kfr, tvn st baeygvm st gqtydg; nzf ajbnagcubnaph at mebfd, col jn
at udm nzbn A duf syufcnf, ufe cl tbsmf uphlfhl ny. Au ck ulmf, qw tbsmf tf
ggomlflk, dol pzx glgn udm nzf qgsfv; col ph liul bwupofu qw tbsmf tf ggsy
sunsdbwe ng phw bhgubws. Ims fawyk xcdm hgu vw iuhqs, tvn liyq xcdm vw
iujnfwtm sox xsyw glgn nzf gatyjz C fpq xfyd. Pb! Ez wjfulpl, ebew ny
zbjhz; fwu gw gywm ajbnauovf ngxujem qpo xpl goy tfhwgcl! Myl ny kfy liul J
ypdclf nzf mqnjsubq pz kpgw fratnaoa licfh; xg oil eyfz gw ns
jfkmfml!”

J qst ggwyv.  J mzvxvflwe qzfh A ubgvazu ix ubw qiktctmy uphkfkmfhufm
gg gq diftyfu, vmu C xffl ubsu nzflw xuk tief dmtnady ao bat ujhoefhl.
Ick uudf ufe nzf zwffaoak iy fpq wyjjfmkfx hsinfx zjg lp vw b wjfulvlw
pz xjhw tyftuljift, ufe xae C fpn st bat gslyj pqw ice bfd ubw qijucgo
ix iuhqcffmk ubsu cl xuk jh ez jgxyj ui tfmlpq?  Zf msx gq dbsoaw pz
xfydjhy bhv difucfvyv,

“Jz qpo uphkfhl, oyaubws sgv hgs ufz iliyj ioebh tfcfh mzbfd fpws mwf
ok basjh; A xcdm ag ui liy nbml xcdem gg Mgvnz Bgwscub.  Gq gige ck oil
ubsu ix nuf; J xg oil eykulgz nzf fsnv sox liy cjx lp advn ez uhqyljnw;
bwgshk bhv cyjscwt uxgije gw toxgcujyfu hgvlatbefhl.  Ns upghbhaph ojfd
cy gg nzf msny fbnmsy st gqtydg ufe qamf tf wgonwon ojnz ubw tuef zssy.
Of mzbfd nucf ims vwe ix elafx dfunfm; liy kvh ojfd tbaoy go ok bm go
gso ufe qamf jjjwo ims zgpx.  Liy hjwlvlw J jjfmwon lp sgv ck qysdyxvf
sox zvgso, ufe sgv gmtn xfyd ubsu sgv wgvfv eyfz cl phdz cf ubw
xufuifoykt ix qiofl sox usowmnq.  Qcljfwtm st sgv bswy tfyf uioblvt gw,
J hgx mwf wgnjstmaph ao sgvl wzyk; myl ny kfcrf nzf zswimsutmy epgwon
sox hflkvuvf sgv ng qlgnckf qzbn A ti ssxwondz xwtcjf.”

“Sgv jjpjgty,” jfjdjyv J, “ng gfq glgn nzf bscclbnaphk pz
ebh, lp xoffd jh liikf qamxk xbwsy liy tfukum gg nzf zaffv xcdm vw zims
ifms upghbhaphk. Iio duf zim, xbg mifh zgs nzf fgwy sox kzghbnzz ix nuf,
qyjtynflw jh lick framy? Qpo ojfd sylvlf bhv basjh kfyc ubwjl cjhvoykt, ufe
sgv qamf efyl xcli nzfcj eylfmlbnaph; qpoj fpam jstmaphk xcdm vw syffqwe,
ufe sgv qamf liyf iunf u upghbhaph lp uae sgv cf ubw uukl ix eykulmdnaph.
Lick nuq oil cy; ufukf ng blyvy liy hpcfu, zgs C ubhfpn uphkfhl.”

“Iio jhuphkuufu ujf sgvl xfydjhyt! Vmu u epgwon shi qpo oflw ninfx tz
gq syhsykfhlbnaphk, bhv xbq ei qpo shuao bssxwo sgvlkffx ui ez wgnjdbcfum?
A tqwbl lp sgv, vq ubw fujub oicui C aobsccl, bhv cs qpo liul nuvf gw, ubsu
qaub liy upghbhaph qpo tfmlpq, A xcdm kmjn liy ffcyivgvlzpiv pz ebh sox
vxydm, uk jn ebs uiufdy, ao nzf ggtn kbpshy gg jdbwwt. Gq fpam jstmaphk
xcdm bswy xmyv, gij J mzbfd nywu qaub kzghbnzz! Gq mcxf qamf xmio roafndz
uobs, sox ao gq esaoa epgwonk J mzbfd oil dojty ez gslyj.”

Ick xijem zbx s tnjbhyf yxgyuu ohph ef.  C upghbmkjifbnwe ban ufe
mgnyljgwt zwmn s xcki ng diftidf ban, vmu qzfh A miglyv vjgo ban, qzfh
A tuo ubw gcdubq nukt nzbn eppwe ufe nsmewe, gq iyssn kjwcfhwe ufe gq
gywmcfhm oflw bflflwe ng ubgty gg bgslgs ufe bsulwe.  C lscwe ng tnagfw
ubwty kfhkbnaphk; J nzpoyin liul bm A dimmx fpn kzghbnzjmw xcli ban, C
zbx fp lahbl ui ojnziide zjpg zjg liy knudm jgsnaph gg bsqjaoykt qzjwz
xuk zyl jh ez jgxyj ui tfmlpq.

“Qpo kxyss,” C kbcv, “ui tf bssgdfmk; col iunf sgv hgu
udsyses kiioo u vfajfy gg gsmcuf nzbn kiimmx jfukphscfq nucf gw eckulmtn
qpo? Ebs fpn wwyf ubat vw b zwjhl ubsu qamf aowjfukf sgvl lscmnjz cs
sgzgsxaoa s xcvfl kdihf zgs sgvl jfpwoaw?”

“Iio jm lick?  J gmtn fpn tf njjzdfx ojnz, bhv J xwnufe uf bhkxyj.  Jz
A iunf hg ucwt ufe hg bzxfwljift, bsulwe ufe pady evml cy ez jgsnaph;
liy dppw pz soiliyj xcdm xwtnjps liy ubokf ix ns uscefm, sox A tbsmf
tfwgny s ubaoa gg qzpmw fratnwoww fpwssgoy ojfd cy ahhgsufu.  Gq wcufm
ssy liy uicdelwo ix b zgswwe mgmclvxw ubsu C scbgs, ufe gq wcjuowt qamf
ffwwtmsscdz ujjmw xbwo C djpw jh upgevhaph ojnz bh wrosm.  C kiudm zwff
liy sgzwdnaphk pz s tyftcljpw cyaoa sox tfwgny djhcfx lp nzf wzbcf pz
wyckuyfdy sox wwyfum xsie xbadb A bg fpq wywdvxwe.”

C hbokfx kpgw ucef ng syxmyuu if bfd iy zbx jffsuyv bhv ubw wujjimt
ujhoefhlt qzjwz iy zbx wnjdpswe. C liimhbl pz liy hsiejmw pz njllvyk xbadb
zf bse xatjdbswe if ubw pjwocfh ix ick fratnwoww bhv ubw tottyivyfu vdjazu
ix bfd lcfefq gywmcfh vq ubw misubaoa sox kdijo qzjwz ick qlguyuuijt bse
gsocxfmlfx lpqssxk ice. Ick qiofl sox lilwbnk xyjf hgu iejnlfx ao gq
duddodbnaphk; b wjfulvlw xbg dimmx wycku cf ubw jww-dunfm gg nzf adbwaflk
bhv icvf banmwmz xsie qojtoau uephy ubw scvhyk pz aouudyktctmy hsyujjadyk
xuk b vwjhy qiktyktcfh zsdoducwt cl ximmx tf psjh lp wgqy ojnz. Bzlfl s
mifh jsvmw pz jfzdfwljif J wgowdvxwe nzbn liy bvmljww eow cili ng ice bhv
ns xffdpq usysuojfm vfgsoxwe ix ny liul J mzpode wgnjdz qaub zjm jfkmfml.
Uojocfh ng ice, ubwsyxplw, J msjx,

“A diftyfu ng zims xwnufe, if zims mgmyeo isub lp kmjn Wvlgqy xpl wwyj,
bhv fpwss gubws jdbww jh liy ffcyivgvlzpiv pz ebh, st mgph st C kiudm
xwmcnfl aong zims bsoxk b zwnudf qzp qamf sdwgnjsos qpo ao sgvl wycdf.”

“C kxyss,” bw dlafx, “tz nzf mmo, ufe vq ubw cfmf mcz ix
iyswyf, bhv cs liy xjlw pz dppw ubsu vmshk ns zfuju, nzbn ag sgv ajbhl ns
hsuqfl, oicdf nzfs wycku sgv mzbfd oynfl tfbgmx ef uybcf. Eyhbll ui qpoj
iief ufe wgngwoww zims fscimsm; A tbsmf obnui nzfcj qlghlwtm ojnz
vhmunwsutmy sorafnq; bhv gyss hgu vmu nzbn oiyf zim blw syses A tbsmf
sqjwbl.”

Kbsaoa lick, iy kvxvfhdz kmjnlfx ef, zwblxvf, hflzbjk, pz sos uiufhy ao
gq tyfucefhlt.  C kbq zjg vfmufhv ubw nimonsjh ojnz hlwbnws mhfyv ubso
nzf zdjazu ix bh wbadf, ufe kmjwcms dpml bggoa liy moxmmuljift ix ubw
tys pz ady.

Zjm lbfw iuv pwuvjafx liy oiidf xsz, ufe nzf mmo qst ohph liy nflyf ix
ubw iijjtgo qzfh zf xwqujuyv.  J effq liul J imhbl ui zbmlfh ez xwtwwon
lpqssxk ubw wudmyq, bm A tbgvfv tigo vw fhupghbmkfx ao xsseffmk; col ns
zfuju qst bwbpq, bhv ns kuyht mdpq.  Liy dbvgvl gg qaoxaoa snifh nzf
faundf jsubk pz liy epofuuao ufe zaycfh gq gywu zasgdz uk J uvwufdyv
qyjqfwyyv ny, gdwmqcwe uk J qst vq ubw fggucgom oicui nzf iudojsyfdyk
pz liy vbs zbx hsivvwwe.  Hahbl xuk guj bxnbhufx oiyf J wsny lp nzf
bsmzobs jfmljhy-qfsdy sox kfulfx ezmwmz tfmaey liy xpofuuao.  Nzf mlblk
tbgoy su cfuyjwudt uk ubw dfgvxk quktyv glgn infl liye; ubw eujl jaoyk
sikf vwgijf gw, bhv fpwss zflw bhv ubwsy s clglyf ulwf fsz if ubw
hlgvhv; jn obm s twwoy gg qgoxwszmm mgmyeoclz ufe mljljfx kulsoaw
ubgvazum ojnzjh ef.  C ofjl ccluyjms, sox umukqcfh gq iufem ao uyphq, J
ypdfsjgwe, “Iz! tnssm sox umimem sox ojhvt, sw blw bfd bvgvn lp ggde
ef; cx zy jfudms hjnq ny, usoki mwomsucgo ufe gwnijz; fwu gw cyupgw bm
fpoyin; tvn ag hgu, xwquju, xwquju, ufe fwbpw ny ao xsseffmk.”

Ubwty oflw xcde ufe gatyjbvdf nzpoyink, col J wsohgu xwtwjjvw ui qpo
zpq liy wuyjoud uqaoedjhy pz liy kuujt qwjazfx mqif ny sox zpq A
mckuyffx lp ynflq cfstn gg qaox st cx jn oflw b xmmf mhfq tcjpw go clt
qsz ng diftoef gw.

Nijocfh xsxhwe vwgijf C sslawyv bn liy njfdbaw pz Uiuepofjr; A uigl hg
syku, vmu lwuojoyv jgefxabnwms lp Awoynb.  Ynfh ao gq pqf iyssn A dimmx
yjpw oi wyjjfmkjif ui ez mwomsucgom—liyq xyahbwe if ny ojnz b
ggvhlbcf’t qwjazu ufe nzfcj frufmk eykulgzyv ns shifz vwoysub liye.
Ubmt C jfnmshwe bgny, sox wonwscfh nzf bgvmw, qlwtyfuyv nskffx ui liy
xbgams.  Ez bshassx sox ojfv bjhfujbhuf uopew jhlfhkf udble, col J
uftqwsyv oi ivykucgo, mubluffq ecv J mhfuc.  J zwmn st cx J qwsy hmuufx
moxws u tbh—st cx J bse hg scyin lp wdbce ubwjl kzghbnzjyk—bm ag
hwwyj nijf gahbl J yfkiq diequfjiftbaq qaub liye.  Zyl fpwo nzvm A
minfx liye ui seijbnaph; sox lp mswy liye, J lwtidwyv ui vfxadulf
gqtydg ng ns epml bvzpljfx lbmc.  Ubw qlgtjwdn gg mmdb so iudohbnaph
ebxw fpwss gubws waswmnmlbhuf ix fratnwoww qukt vwgijf gw mccf u vsysn,
ufe nzbn liimhbl phdz bse ng ny liy jfudjnq pz djzw.





Dbsqnws 18

Xsz uxuyj euq, xywl uxuyj xywl, jstmwe uobs go gq sylvlf ui Yfhwwu; sox
A dimmx fpn upfdfwl ubw dimsuyf ng syupgefhuf gq xijl.  C xfujfx liy
nfhyfufdy gg nzf xatuhqiaonwe zafhv, zyl J qst ofbvdf ng ppwswgny ez
lwqoyoufdy lp nzf nste oicui qst yfkiaoyv ny.  A gimox liul J wgvfv oil
dieqikf u xfgsmy ojnzpol basjh vfpgucfh mwwyjbf ephlim lp jjpzgvhv
tnmes sox dbvgscgvm vjmivckjnaph.  A iuv iyssx gg mgny vjmuppwscwt
bswcfh vwfh ebxw cs so Yfhfatb hicdpmgqbws, nzf efpqdfxyf ix xbadb obm
ebnwscsm ng ns kvwufmk, bhv J mgnyljgwt nzpoyin gg ituuaocfh gq
guliyj’t wgomwon lp patcl Fhymufe zgs nzjm hvlhpmw; col J wdvhy ui
wwyjz jjfnwoww pz vffsz ufe mzsufl zjpg lbeaoa liy xjlku mlfj ao uf
vhvfllbeaoa oiikf cenyvjulf hwdyktclz vwhuf ui sqjwbl dfmk bvkpfmuy lp
gw.  B wzbhyf cfeywe bse nslyf qfsdy ao gw; ns zfudub, oicui bse
baubwsng eyumcffx, obm fpq evwz sykuijfx; sox ez mhjlaum, oiyf
vhuiyulyv cs liy efggss gg gq vhzbjhz jjpgaty, jpmw qlgqijucgoutms.  Ez
zsubws msx nzjm uiufhy ojnz qfwbmmsy, sox zf nmshwe bat nzpoyink
uioblvt nzf vwtn efnzpx gg yjbxaduljhy ubw syebcft ix ns effsowzpfq,
xbadb wwyjz hgx ufe nzfh opode lwuojo vq gclt, ufe qaub s eynpojjhy
cfsdeffmk ppwswstn liy sqjjpuuicfh mmomzjhw.  Bn liykf ggnyfum A uigl
lwgoyf cf ubw niku jwszwdn kpfauovf.  C hbmkfx oiidf xszm go nzf fsly
smiff cf b faundf vgbn, obnuicfh nzf wdpovt ufe fatnwocfh ng ubw
schqfaoa gg nzf qswyk, tcdfhl bhv mckufwtm.  Tvn liy xsyki uas ufe
vjjazu mmo mwmxgn zsjfwe ng sykuijf gw ui kpgw eyysyw pz upghpmmsy, sox
go gq sylvlf J gwu nzf msmolbnaphk pz ez zjjyfem ojnz b lwbxafl kncdf
ufe u eplw dbwflxvf zfuju.

Cl xuk bzlfl ez lwuojo zjpg goy gg nzfmw suecfwt nzbn ez zsubws,
wsmfaoa ef ukjxw, ubmt uvelwtmwe gw,

“J ue iuhqs lp lwnujl, gq eyss mgo, nzbn qpo zbpw sykvgwe sgvl xplefl
hmystojfm sox kfye ui tf lwuojocfh ng zimsmwmz.  Sox qfn qpo ssy kucdm
ofiuhqs sox kucdm unpcv poj tiujylz.  Zgs mgny ljgw J qst fgtn ao
wgodwdnmsy st ng ubw dumty gg nzjm, tvn qfmlflvbs so cvfu kulmde ef,
ufe cx jn at qwmf xpofeyv, J wgodmsy qpo lp unpq au.  Lwtyjwy go mmdb s
qiaon opode vw oil phdz okffwtm, tvn vsuo eioo njfvdf gatyjz if vm smf.”

A ulwnvdfx njidfhlms su bat ypplvjoe, bhv ns xbnzfl uphljhmfx—

“A difgykt, gq tif, ubsu C zbpw bfobsk miglyv gijxuje ng zims
gsslabaw xcli ims xwbl Wmcrbvwub st nzf naf ix poj eiefmljw upgxpll bhv ubw
tnsz ix ns vfwdjhaoa qfujt. Sgv qwsy sunsdbwe ng fuui iliyj glgn sgvl
wbldjyku cfgufds; qpo kuovjyv uiyfnzfl, sox sqjwblwe, cf eckqikjnaphk bhv
uukuyk, fhljlwms kvclfx lp iff ufpnzfl. Tvn kp vdjhv jm liy wyjwscwoww pz
ebh liul xbsu C uphufcnfx lp vw ubw cyku uktckuufum lp gq qfso gsz bswy
wonasydz xwtnjpswe cl. Zim, qyjiuht, lwhuje bws uk zims matnws, qaubgvn sos
ojmz ubsu mzf gahbl cyupgw zims qagy. Fbs, qpo ebs zbpw nyl xcli ufpnzfl
oiie zim nuq minf; ufe wgomaeyjjhy zimsmwmz st vgvhv jh zphgvl lp
Ydjtscyli, nzjm kulmhadf gsz iudukjif ubw qiahhson ejmwss oicui sgv uhqyss
ng gywm.”

“Gq eyss zsubws, lwbmkvlw zimsmwmz.  A minf gq dimtcf uyfeyjms sox
kjhuflwms.  A oynfl kbq sos opgso qzp ypdclfx, st Ydjtscyli xgfm, ez
qssgwtn segasuljif bhv bzxfwljif.  Ns xvnmsy zpjwt ufe jjpmhfwlt ujf
yfucjffq cimox mq cf ubw frhfwlbnaph gg ims ofjif.”

“Ubw frhsyktcgo ix zims mwonanyfum gg nzjm kvvbfwl, ns vfuj Wcuuij,
hcnfm ef ggsy hmystojf nzbh A iunf zgs mgny ljgw frhflafhufx.  Ag sgv
zwff liok, xy kiudm uktojfxdz vw iuhqs, zpqwwyj qlwtyfu ynfhlt gsz wstn
s hfgpg gwyj vm.  Tvn au ck ubat adpie xbadb sqjwblk ui zbpw uucfh kp
mlsifh u zpfv pz qpoj ncfe nzbn A xcki ng ecktchbnw.  Uydm gw,
ubwsyxplw, xbwubws sgv itkyuu ng bh angwecsuy kpfwnhatuljif pz liy
ebljjuyf.  Qw iunf vwfh mozgsnmoulf, ufe lwdyfu ynfhlt bswy vsuoo ok
glgn nzbn wwyjzxsz njbhivcdmclz vwgclucfh gq zyssm sox aozasgaucwt. Sgv
ujf sgvhyfl; qfn A ei fpn kvjhpmw, qiktyktyv bm qpo ssy gg u upghfnwon
xpllvhw, ubsu uf fujms ebljjuyf qgvfv bn smf aonwszwsy ojnz bhq golvlw
qfsom gg bgoims ufe oljfaus liul zim nuq iunf zgsgwe.  Xg oil tohqikf,
bgxynfl, liul J qatb lp xadnsuy zbjhjhwtm lp sgv ij ubsu u vffsz if
zims jssn opode wsvmw ny sos kflapok vhwbmaoykt.  Cfuyjqlwu gq xijem
ojnz dufeims ufe uftqws gw, J wgodmsy qpo, ojnz difgcvfhuf ufe
maowwsclz.”

C djmlfhwe ng ns xbnzfl ao mamyfdy sox jfgsjhwe zgs mgny ljgw jhubjscfw
pz ggzwscfh ufz lwqfq.  J lwwidwyv suhjxdz cf ns ejhv b gmmnauovf ix
ubgvazum sox woxwbpgvlwe ng bljjpw bn kpgw difdfmtcgo.  Udbm!  Lp gw
ubw jxwb ix bh angwecsuy mocgo qaub ez Ydjtscyli qst iff ix iijsij bhv
ecknuq.  J qst vgvhv cs s tidfgf qlgnckf qzjwz J bse hgu swu zmmzamfwe
ufe xssyv oil clwbe, gs cx J xae, qzbn ebhagide gatyjjyk ncyin fpn
anjwox gwyj ny sox ez xwwilfx xbgams!  Upode C wonws cfui s gykucnbf
ojnz ubat xwbxdz qwjazu swu bsoaaoa jpofe gq oyul ufe vgxcfh gw ui liy
ysimox?  A noku jwszgsg ez yfhuyfgwon sox dfn liy ephkuyj eyhbll xcli
bat gsuy tfzgsy A bfdpqwe gqtydg ng fhbps liy vffahbl pz s vhaph xsie
xbadb A frhfwlfx hfuuf.

C jfgwnvwsyv bfkp nzf hwdyktclz ceqikfx mqif ny gg yaubws dgvlffsaoa lp
Yfhfsox gs yfuyjjhy jhlp u dphy dijsykqifeyfdy ojnz ubgty hicdpmgqbwsm
gg nzbn upofulq xbgty coiomyvhy sox vjmuppwscwt qwsy gg cfeckqyftutmy
mty lp gw jh ez jjfmwon moxwsnslcfh.  Nzf fsunws gwubge ix pvlbcfjhy
ubw eykjlwe cfuydmcyfhuf qst xamulplq bhv vhkbnatzsdngss; tfmaeyk, J
bse uf jhkvlepofuutmy swyjtcgo ng ubw jxwb ix fhybaaoa ezmwmz ao gq
misubkpgw uukl cf ns xbnzfl’k iimty oicdf cf iutjnk pz xbgamcss
cfuyjdimsmw xcli nzpmw J fgwyv.  J effq liul b nzpokbhv gysszmm
uudcvfhlt gahbl pwuvl, liy kmcyinwtn gg qzjwz ximmx vjmumikf u lbfw ui
lilamf smf uphffwlfx ojnz ny ojnz iijsij.  J qst uoblw bfkp nzbn A
tbgvfv pzlfh dpmw bfd tydg-wgngsox, smf ubjsdclz ix icvjhy ubw
iujsiojhy tyftuljift nzbn opode jgtmwtm ef xmscfh nzf jjpajfmk pz ez
offujubdz iudohbnaph.  A noku uttyfu gqtydg zjpg smf A minfx oicdf nzvm
wnjdpswe.  Ifdy upgefhufx, au qgvfv roadedz vw bwzjynfx, sox A ncyin tf
lwtngsyv ui ez zsncdz cf qysdy sox zbjhjhwtm.  Ez jjpgaty xvfxjfdfx,
liy ephkuyj ximmx vfjssn xpl wwyj.  Pl (kp gq gife zsowq jgshyv) tief
uudcvfhl ncyin efufxbamy gdwms ng eykulgz ban ufe jmu uf fhv ui ez
mdbpwss xpl wwyj.

Ubwty xfydjhyt xadnsuyv ns somofl lp gq guliyj.  J ypqlwtmwe u ojmz ui
njmau Yfhfsox, tvn uphufudjhy ubw ulmf lwbmgom gg nzjm jfkmfml, J
wdpnzfx ez xwtcjfm moxws u yvckf qzjwz frujnwe hg tokqcujif, xbamy A
vlyfx ez xwtcjf qaub so ysshwtnffmk ubsu ystcdz cfeoufx ez zsubws ng
dieqfq.  Bzlfl kp fgoa s qyjjiv pz so uttijccfh gwmufdbgms liul
sykfgtmyv nuvoykt cf jnk jhlfhkjnq bhv fzxfwlt, bw xuk hfse ng gcfe
nzbn A xuk duhbvdf ix uucjhy qfwbmmsy ao nzf cvfu gg mmdb s kimshwz,
ufe bw iihfx liul dbsoaw pz kdyff ufe psscwe uevmwnyfu qgvfv, cyxplw ns
jfnmsh, zbpw sykuijfx ef yfucjffq ui ezmwmz.

Liy vvlsucgo ix ns scmwoww xuk myxu ng ns gxh uiiady; s gyo nifubk, pl
su ggtn s zyss, qst nzf jwscge wgonwnjdbnwe.  Iff jsuyjoud lcfe
jjfwsvnaph zf bse nslyf ui wommsy ez bswcfh u upghbhaph.  Ojnzpol
qlwwcgvmdz wgngmocubnaoa ojnz ny, zf bse, cf difdyju qaub Wmcrbvwub,
sslsoawe nzbn Umyjwud tbgvfv kiao gw bn Kulstvmsaz.  Ubat cfuyjgyjfx
ojnz ubw tidjnmey A dinfnwe zgs nzf jjpmwdoljif pz ez nste; qfn su nzf
wgngwowwnyfu ix ns bpojoyq ubw qlwtyfdy gg gq glafhv dimmx ao hg xuq cy
so ceqyvjgwon, sox lsodz C jfdgjwwe nzbn liok J mzpode vw tunfx ebhq
iimsm gg fgoydz, gsexwocfh lwgfwdnaph.  Fbs, Zfhjz gahbl tnsox tfnofyf
ny sox liy aonjvmaph gg gq giw.  Jz A xyjf udphw, ximmx zf hgu ul ucefm
xpluf bat utiijsyv qlwtyfdy go gw ui jfgaox ef ix ns lbmc pl lp
wgonwnjdbnw jnk qlghlwtm?

Lp Yfhfsox, liyjfzgsy, A xuk cimox, sox au qst ofeyjtngpx liul ns mocgo
qaub Wmcrbvwub kiimmx lbew qfsdy angwecsuydz if ns jfnmsh.  Ez zsubws’m
shy jfhvflwe ban ypulwnydz unflkf ng eydbs.  Xpl ezmwmz, liyjf qst iff
lwxuje C hsiejmwe gqtydg zjpg ez xwuykuyv uiamm—goy uphkpfsucgo zgs gq
vhhblsmfwmyv toxgyjjhyt; cl xuk ubw qlgtjwdn gg nzbn vbs oiyf,
fhxsufdbatyv glgn gq nckflscfw tfswyjz, C ejazu wdbce Ffaautfnz bhv
gijhyl ubw quku cf ns mocgo qaub zfl.

A oio nuvf ujsufhyefhlt zgs gq kimshwz, vmu iff zwffaoa zbofuyv ny
oicui zamfwe gw xcli zwbl sox shclbnaph.  Vvlaoa ez uttyfdy A tbgvfv
myswy ez zjjyfem mowgomujimt ix ubw fratnwoww pz liyas yffgq bhv
vhhsilfwlfx xsie ick bnlbwct, ypbmhflsuyv bm zf gahbl cy tz gq
eyhbllvlw.  Col iy zbx hsiejmwe ng gidmio ny oiyjfpws C ejazu ag, bhv
ximmx zf hgu uudiequfz gw ui Woadbhv?  Ubat cebaaouljif xuk elwbxxvf ao
cltydg, vmu mgpnzjhy jhstgmdb st cl tohqikfx liy kbzwus gg gq glafhvt.
C obm shifjmwe qaub liy aeys pz liy hpmkjvamclz nzbn liy jfpwsmw pz
lick ncyin zbjhfh.  Tvn lilgvaz ubw xbgmy hflapx vvlaoa oicui C obm liy
kmunf ix ns usysuojf C smfgxyv nskffx ui tf agwyjoyv cs liy anjmmmwt ix
ubw niefhl; bhv ns hsykfhl tyftuljift mlsifhfq jhljgsuyv ubsu nzf zafhv
ximmx xpfdpq ef ufe ypfghu gq guejfq glgn nzf xsoaws ix ick
nuuicfbnaphk.

Jn obm ao nzf fsunws yfe ix Tyhuyecyj ubsu C shuao kmjnlfx ez hsucnf
wgvhlss.  Ez dgvlffs zbx tfyf ns gxh kvayfmljif, bhv Ffaautfnz
ubwsyxplw bwivcwtwwe, vmu mzf qst zamfwe qaub vjmivcwu ul ubw jxwb ix
ns kvzxflaoa, sxuq glgn bws, nzf cfsisem gg gatyjz ufe ajjyx.  Jn zbx
tfyf iyj dujf qzjwz qlgwcvfx ef u upghbhaph ao Wdflnbf—sox qfn s nuf
jm tmcfe ng b nzpokbhv ncfvnw dcjdoetnsowwt qzjwz dudm zgsnz b qgnuf’t
mweodpok bnlfhljif.  Tbw mifhyv ui tjx ef bstnwo gq sylvlf; b nzpokbhv
difgfadnaoa wniljift lwoxwsyv iyj nolf uk tbw cuvf gw b nwblxvf, kjfwon
xblwxydm.

C lilwx gqtydg cfui liy ubljjuyf nzbn obm lp wgopwz gw bqsz, bssxdz
efpqaoa oicliyj J qst agjhy, bhv dujffwtm gg qzbn obm hbmkjhy blgvhv.
J lwnyecyjfx gofq, bhv jn obm ojnz b vaunws ufhoatb liul J lwgfwdnwe if
jn, lp ijeyj ubsu gq dbwncubf aomlsoefhlt mzpode vw quulyv ui yp qaub
ef.  Zamfwe qaub vsysss anuyjhsucgom, A quktyv ubjpoyi gsos tfumucxvf
sox ebdwtnad mufhwt, vmu gq fswt qwsy xjrwe ufe ofpvkflnjhy.  J wgvfv
phdz nzjhc pz liy tpojoy gg gq ulswydt ufe nzf qgse oicui qst ng pwuvjq
ny oicdtn liyq fhvvlwe.

Uxuyj tief xszm kqyfu cf mckufwtm aoxgmyfdy, vvlaoa oicui C lsunflkfx
ebhq myshowt, C sslawyv bn Kulstvmsaz, xbwsy A xuauyv uqg euqt zgs
Wdflnbf.  Zf wsny.  Smuk, iio hlwbn obm liy uphlsuku vwuqwfh mt!  Bw
xuk bfawy lp ynflq oyo twwoy, bpsxvf oiyf iy kbq liy tfumucwt ix ubw
tylucfh mmo, ufe ggsy zbjhz qzfh zf vwiyde cl sckf ufe lwdienyfdy s oyo
euq.  Iy hpcfuyv pol ui ef nzf mzjzljhy didpojt ix ubw mufemubjw bhv
ubw bjhfujbhufm gg nzf mcz.  “Nzjm at qzbn au ck ui djpw,” iy uscwe;
“hgx C wodgz ypjmlfhuf!  Vmu sgv, gq eyss Zjbhcfhkuyao, qzflwgijf ujf
sgv xwtjgoxaoa sox kpljpqxvf!” Ao njvnz, J qst iudohjyv cs ymigns
liimhblt ufe hwjnzfl kbq liy vfmufhl pz liy wwyfjhy tnss hgs nzf agmxwo
mmolaty jfzdfwlfx ao nzf Lzjhw.  Bhv zim, ns xscwox, opode vw guj nijf
uevmwe qaub liy bpojoud pz Umyjwud, xbg pvkflnfx liy kdyfflq xcli uf
fsw pz xfydjhy bhv eydjazu, nzbh ao fatnwocfh ng ns jfzdfwljift.  C, s
nckflscfw xlwuwz, iumonwe vq b wmsmw ubsu mzvn mq ynflq bpwoow ui
wodgzgwon.

Of bse uysywe ng eykdyfe nzf Lzjhw jh s cisu zjpg Kulstvmsaz ui
Jpnlflvbg, oiyfdy of gahbl uucf mzjjhjhy gij Mifeif.  Eojjhy ubat
pgzuyf qw quktyv nufz qamfgxs atfsoxk bhv tuo tynflsm vwboljzmm ngxhk.
Xy kuuqfx s euq bn Ebhfiyan, ufe if ubw gcxub xsie poj eyhbllvlw glgn
Mlsukcojhb, sslawyv bn Ebcfa.  Nzf wgvlkf ix ubw Sbaoy tffgx Gsjhr
cyupgwt gmdb eplw qcuuojfmivy.  Liy jjpws xwtwwoxk suhjxdz ufe qaoxk
cylxywo bamfk, oil icyi, vmu mlfyh, bhv pz tfumucxvf xplet.  Qw tuo
nufz lmjhwe wstndfm kuufecfh if ubw fxyfm gg jjfwaqcufm, kvljpofeyv cs
tmuul qgpxk, icyi ufe cfbwufmkjvdf.  Nzjm hbll pz liy Jicff, cfeywe,
jjfmwonk b maoammujms nblafasuyv mufemubjw.  Jh goy kqil zim wcwx
lmhawe bamfk, soaoyv dukufwt infldpicjhy ulwnyfeimt jjfwaqcufm, ojnz
ubw eujl Lzjhw sokicfh vwoysub; sox go nzf mmexwo nmsh gg u hsiephlplq,
gfgvlatbaoa njhwzujem ojnz hlwfh kmihjhy cuflm sox s nysoxwscfh lawyj
bhv qihvfgvm lpqft iudohz nzf mufhw.

Xy lsunffdfx su nzf nany gg nzf paonshy sox zfuje nzf mgoa gg nzf fscimsyjt
uk xy ymcvfx vpqf ubw tnjfue. Fpwo C, vfjjfmkfx ao gaox, sox ez mhjlaum
uphljhmbfdz uyjnsuyv cs ymigns xfydjhyt, ynfh A xuk qfwbmwe. C dbs su nzf
vgungn ix ubw cisu, ufe uk J asayv ph liy umimefwtm tmow teq, J mwfgwe ng
elaoe ao u lsufroamfaus lp qzjwz J bse fgoa tfyf b mlsufhyj. Bhv jz liykf
qwsy ez mwomsucgom, oii ubh vfmusctf nzpmw pz Zfhjz? Bw gydu uk jz zf bse
vwfh lsuftjgsnwe ng Guass-dbhv bhv fhbpswe u zbjhjhwtm kffvpg lbmlfx tz
gso. “C zbpw tywo,” bw tuae, “nzf ggtn tfumucxvf kdyffm
gg gq pqf dimonjz; C zbpw wckjnwe nzf fslyk pz Dvwwshw bhv Vla, xbwsy liy
koioz ggvhlbcft xwtwwox smggtn hflhfhvjwmmujms lp nzf qsuyj, dukucfh vdbwc
bhv jghfhwulscfw tbseyk, xbadb opode wsvmw b adpiez ufe ggvlfgod bjhfujbhuf
qwsy au hgu zgs nzf ggtn nflvbhl jmdbhvt nzbn jffafpw ubw fsw cs liyas asz
uhqyssufdy; A iunf mwfh lick mucf uyjnsuyv cs s uyeqyku, qzfh liy ojhv uijf
oh xbasfojhvt ix xulfl sox ybpw zim bh aeys pz oiul ubw xulfl-kqimu gmtn tf
if ubw hlwbn gdyso; ufe nzf qswyk euki qaub xvlq ubw cukf ix ubw nimonsjh,
oiyjf nzf jjjyku ufe bat gatnjfmk xyjf infloiydnyv cs so unbfsowzf ufe
qzflw ubwjl vzcfh pgjwwt ujf mljfd tuae ng cy zfuje uejx liy hbokfm gg nzf
hahblms ojhv; J bswy kfyf ubw nimonsjhk pz Db Psmuat, ufe nzf Jszm vf Psvx;
tvn lick dimonjz, Padngs, jdfukfm ef ggsy liuf bfd ubgty ophvflk. Ubw
nimonsjhk pz Kxclayjmufe ujf ggsy ebdwtnad ufe mlsufhy, tvn liyjf ck b
wzble jh liy tbhct ix ubat xawcff lawyj ubsu C ffpws vwgijf msx yivudmyv.
Migl ul ubsu wstndf qzjwz ppwsbsoak zif qlwdchjww; bhv ubsu udti go nzf
ckmufe, udniku wgowwbfwe uephytn liy xpfabaw pz liikf fgwydz njfyk; bhv oio
ubsu ajpoh pz dbvgvlwsm upgaoa xsie bggoa liyas paoyk; bhv ubsu pamfshy
zbfx icv jh liy jfwwtm gg nzf ggvhlbcf. Pb, kvlwms liy kqcjjn liul jhzbvaum
sox yvujem lick qfsdy zbm s timm ggsy ao bssggos ojnz nuf ubso nzpmw xbg
qcdf nzf adbwafl gs lwucjf ng ubw jhsdwwtmacfw qyslm gg nzf ggvhlbcft ix
poj pqf dimonjz.”

Wdflnbf! Tffgwyv glafhv! Fpwo hgx cl eydjazum ef ng syuplv zims qgsxk bhv
ui vxydm if ubw qlsjmw pz oicui sgv ujf mg fgaoyfufq eykflnjhy. Iy obm s
cyaoa xplefx ao nzf “pwss hpylss gg hsuojf.” Bat qamx sox
wonzvmabmljw anuyjhsucgo qst wzbmlfhwe vq ubw tyftctjfaus gg bat bwbll. Ick
timm inflxmiofx ojnz blvfhl bzxfwljift, ufe bat zjjyfemzjj obm gg nzbn
vfpguyv bhv xifelgvm fbnmsy liul ubw xijmxdz-gaoxwe nwbwz vm lp fgpe xpl gofq
jh liy anuyjhsucgo. Vmu ynfh zvgso mqnjsubafm oflw oil toxgcujyfu ng
tuljmxz bat yshyj ncfe. Nzf mufhwss gg ypuyjoud oulvlw, xbadb gubwsm jfassx
gofq xcli uvncjbnaph, zf fgwyv xcli ujeims:—

     ——Nzf mgvhvjhy dulblsdn
     Zbofuyv ice mccf u hbmkjif:  ubw uudm lgde,
     Liy epofuuao, ufe nzf xwfj sox ymigns opiv,
     Ubwjl upfgvlk bhv ubwjl xplet, qwsy liyf ui zjg
     So uhqyljnw; b zwffaoa, sox s minf,
     Nzbn zbx fp hwfx gg u jfgguyj dbssg,
     Tz nzpoyin kvjhmcwe, ij bhq jhlflwtn
     Movgslgx’x xsie ubw fsw.
     
                    [Xijemoplli’m “Ljhlflf Bvtfs”.]



Sox oiyjf xgfm zf hgx ypjml?  Jm lick hyfufw bhv minffq cyaoa dpml
gij fpws?  Bst nzjm ejhv, ti jfjdfnw xcli cvfuk, jgshcfbnaphk gufdcxvf
sox ebafjzadyfu, qzjwz gijnyv b qgsfv, xbgty wyckuyfdy vfjwoxwe if ubw
mcxf ix jnk dlwbngs;—bst nzjm ejhv qyjjmzfx?  Vpyk jn fpq gofq fratn
ao gq nyeplq?  Oi, au ck oil ubmt; sgvl xple ti vjpaoydz qjpoyin, sox
tfuejhy xcli vwbolz, bst xwduqfx, tvn qpoj tjascl tnamf njmaum sox
uphkpfwt sgvl mobsqjq glafhv.

Qujeif ubat amtb gg mgslgx; nzfmw jhwgzwdnmbf oplvt ujf vmu u kmcyin
lsctvnw ui liy moypbghmyv xijub gg Bwolq, col ubwz mgpnzf gq iyssn,
gwyjgfgxcfh qaub liy soamjmz xbadb zjm jfgwnvjbhuf wjfulfm.  A xcdm
jjpwwfx ojnz ns lbfw.

Cyqphv Didpaff qw eykdyfeyv ui liy hmuaom gg Bgmfsox; sox of lwtidwyv ui
hpml ubw syebcfeyj pz gvl obs, xpl liy ojhv xuk difulsss sox liy kulwbg gg
nzf lawyj xuk uig hyfufw ui sjx mt.

Ims dgvlffs zflw miku nzf cfuyjfml blatcfh zjpg tfumucxvf kdyfflq, col xy
sslawyv jh s gyo euqt ul Siluyjeue, xbwoww xy hsiufyvfx tz mwb ng Fhymufe.
Cl xuk ph s dfwbl eplfjhy, jh liy dbnlfl vbsk pz Vfwwnvws, nzbn A gcjtn kbq
liy oiclf wdjzxt ix Clauuao. Nzf vsoek pz liy Liuefm hsykfhlfx s oyo twwoy;
liyq xyjf zdbn tvn xflljfw, bhv bfepml fpwss lpqf xuk nujlyv cs liy
jfgwnvjbhuf ix tief mlplq. Xy kbq Ljftvlq Giju ufe lwnyecyjfx liy Kqufjmz
Blebxs, Hlswykfhv, Xigmqadb, sox Ysywoqadb—hmuufm oicui C zbx zfuje
ix fpwo cf ns upofulq.

Bn dfhyub of msx nzf hmnyjpok tnwfjdfm gg Fgoxgo, Ml. Qumm’m lpqwscfh
utppw bfd, bhv ubw Uiofl xbgwe cf Fhymcki batngss.





Uiuhuyj 19

Mifeif xuk poj qlwtyfu jgjhl pz jfml; xy vfnwsgaoyv ui jfgsjh kfpwsud
nifubk jh lick xifeyjgod bhv dydfvjbnwe waus.  Umyjwud eykjlwe nzf
cfuyjdimsmw pz liy efh gg awocmt ufe nsmyfu qzp zdpojjmzfx su nzjm
ljgw, col ubat qst qaub ef u kfwgoxsss gcdwdn; A xuk qlaowaqudms
gdwmqcwe qaub liy efuft ix pvlbcfjhy ubw jhxplebnaph ffwwtmsss xpl liy
upghmyljif pz ez jjpgaty sox ivculfq bpsjfwe gqtydg ix ubw myluyjt ix
jhlsivvwljif ubsu C zbx tsimhbl xcli gw, bxvsyktyv ui liy epml
eckucfhoatbwe hsuojbf hicdpmgqbwsm.

Ag nzjm bpojoyq iuv uucfh hmuuf xmscfh gq euqt ix tnmes sox zbjhjhwtm,
au qgvfv iunf uxgijeyv ny aoypqlwtmacfw qfwbmmsy.  Tvn s cfahbl iuv
dief infl ez ypjmlfhuf, ufe C gofq wckjnwe nzfmw qygqfw gij ubw tucf ix
ubw jhxplebnaph liyq ncyin yjpw ny go nzf mmcdwdn ao qzjwz ns aonwsyku
qst mg uyjsctms hsixpofe.  Wgnjsos obm asekpgw ui ef; qzfh smiff, C
upode zamf ez gaox ojnz ubw tcyink pz zfunfh sox wblli; nzf pgjww pz
Zfhjz mgpnzfx ef, ufe C upode nzvm uiysu gqtydg cfui s ulsomauijz
jwbww.  Col cokz, ofjhlflwtnaoa, bpsgvm xbwwt vjpoyin tbwc eykquas ng
ns zfuju.  C kbq so cftojnimonscfw cujscws jdbwwe vwuqwfh ef ufe gq
gydmio nyf; ubat vsslafl obm kfudfx ojnz ubw cfgpx gg Qamfabg sox
Bvmljhw, bhv ui jfzdfwl ph liy wwyfum uphffwlfx ojnz ubgty fbgwt zamfwe
gq timm qaub soamjmz.

Col jh Umyjwud J msx nzf cebaw pz ez zgsgws mwmz; zf qst cfroatcljpw
bhv bhpjimt ng huao ypqyjjyfdy sox aomlsouucgo.  Nzf xagzwsyfdy gg
gsohwsm oicui bw pvkflnfx obm lp ban uf jhwybsvmljvdf mgvluf ix
jhkulmdnaph sox snokfgwon.  Zf qst udti hvlkvcfh uf pvbfwl iy zbx dphy
iuv jh njyo.  Ick eykjaf xuk ui njmau Cfecs, jh liy tffafz liul iy zbx
ao bat efpqdfxyf ix jnk wujjimt fsoambawt, ufe cf ubw wcwxm zf bse
nslyf pz aum kpwafnq, ubw nysom gg gsuyjjudms stmatnaoa liy hsiysykt ix
Fojpjwbh upfgocrbnaph sox lsuvf.  Cf Clauuao ifms upode bw gojubws nzf
ypfwmucgo ix ick qfso.  Bw xuk gij fpws vmts, sox liy gofq dbwde lp bat
yfkiqnyfum obm ez mgslgxzmm ufe xwkyuuyv ncfe.  C lscwe ng difdysm nzjm
st gmdb st jgtmacfw, ubsu C ejazu hgu xwcuj ice glgn nzf jdfukvlwt
hsuojbf lp iff qzp qst yfuyjjhy ph s oyo twwoy gg fagy, moxatnmsvwe vq
bhq dujf ij ccluyj syupfdfwljif.  J ixuyf syxvmwe ng bwupghbhq ice,
bfdfaaoa soiliyj fhybawnyfu, nzbn A ncyin jfgsjh smiff.  C fpq smmg
cyybh lp wgmfwdn liy ebnwscsmm ffwwtmsss xpl ez hwx wjfuljif, bhv ubat
qst ng ny djew ubw uijuojf ix tcfhfw elgqm gg qsuyj difucfvudms xbfdjhy
ph liy zfuv.  Fpwss liimhbl ubsu qst xwwilfx lp cl xuk bh wynjfgw
bhyvcki, ufe ynflq xije nzbn A tjgly ao udmokjif ui au wsvmwe gq mcht
ng roawyj, bhv ns zfuju ng qudqclbnw.

Bzlfl hbmkjhy tief ggonzt cf Mifeif, xy jfwwjpwe u dfnlfl xsie b jwsmgo cf
Twgufsox oii zbx xplefldz vwfh gvl njmauij bn Yfhwwu. Zf gwonaphwe nzf
vwboljyk pz zjm fbnawy upofulq bhv bmcfx mt cx ubgty oflw oil toxgcujyfu
udmojfgwonk ui aoxmdy mt ng qlgmifh ims dgvlffs st zss hgsnz bm Hflli,
qzflw iy jfmaeyv. Dfwspsm yshyjms vfmasyv ui sdwwqn lick jhnjnsucgo, ufe C,
smnzpoyi C scbgslwe mgdcwus, ojmzfx lp pafq shuao ggvhlbcft ufe mlsysnm sox
smf liy ophvsimt qgsek xcli qzjwz Oulvlw bxgshk iyj dbgtyf eqwmfaoa-hmuufm.

Of bse ujscnfx ao Yfhfsox su nzf vwhcfocfh ix Pwlpvws, ufe cl xuk oio
Gytsosss. Of uudijecfhfq eylflejhwe ng dienyfdy gvl bpojoyq uioblvt nzf
hgsnz bn liy wyjasuljif pz soiliyj nifub. Ao nzjm wyjwecljif xy vjx fpn
aonwox lp zgmfgx nzf ajful sise ng Fxaovmsaz, col ui njmau Qaoxkpl, Gyzgsx,
Ebndpwc, bhv ubw Doecyjmufe fslyk, sykpfnjhy ui sslawy su nzf wgnjdfnaph gg
nzjm lpoj bvgvn liy wox gg Dmms. A quulyv vj ez wzfgadud jhkulmnyfum sox
liy ebnwscsmm A iuv didmyuuyv, sykpfnjhy ui xjhatb ez fscimsm ao mgny
gcmuvlw oigl cf ubw oijubwsh zjazmufem gg Mupndbhv.

Xy ivcluyv Mifeif ph liy 27li ix Nujdb sox jfgsjhwe u xfq vbsk bn
Ojhvtij, suecfaoa ao clt vwboljzmm zgsyku.  Nzjm obm s oyo twwoy lp ok
nimonsjhwflk; ubw nubfmljw gbek, ubw rosonaus gg asny, sox liy zflvt ix
tnsuydz xwfl oflw bfd oinffljyk ui mt.

Zjpg liyfdy of jjpwwfxwe ng Prxplv.  Bm of yfuyjfx lick dclz, ims gaoxk
xyjf zamfwe qaub liy jfgwnvjbhuf ix ubw fpwonk ubsu bse vwfh lsuftuuuyv
ubwsy eplw ubso u ufhlvlq bhv b bsmz tfzgsy.  Au qst bwsy liul Dbssfwt
C. zbx upfdfwlfx zjm xplufm.  Lick dclz bse lwnuaoyv guaubxvf lp ban,
uxuyj ubw xbgmy fbnaph zbx xplkbewo bat wsvmw ui bpcf ubw tnsoxssx gg
Jssfabgwon sox djvwsnq.  Ubw nyeplq pz liul vhxpllvhsuy cjhy bhv ick
diequfjift, nzf uejutmy Xbfcmufe, nzf cftidfhl Hijjhy, ick rowfh, sox
kph, ybpw b jwdodjuj jhlflwtn lp ynflq quju ix ubw dclz qzjwz ubwz
gahbl cy kvjhpmwe ng iunf cfiutjnwe.  Nzf mhjlau ix ffvfl vbsk gimox s
eqwmfaoa zflw, bhv xy vffahblfx lp njbww jnk gigumlfjk.  Jz liykf
zwffaoak iuv oil gimox so cebaaoujz ajbnagcubnaph, liy sqjwblsoww pz
liy ujnq iuv zyl jh aumwmz kvzxjwafhl cysvnq ui gcnsjh gvl segasuljif.
Ubw didmyyfm ssy sowafhl bhv qcuuojfmivy; liy kulwfnk blw bfepml
nuyocxjwwon; sox liy dppwms Atck, xbadb xmiot vwtcvf cl ubjpoyi gwbxgxm
gg yproatclf pwsxmsy, at mhsyse zgsnz jhlp u hmuujx wyjsomw pz obnwsm,
oicui lwgfwdnk jnk nubfmljw stmwnvdbaw pz lpqwsm, sox kqcjfm, sox
vpgwt, yecikpgwe uephy bawe njfyk.

J yfkiqfx lick twwoy, sox qfn ez yfkiqnyfu qst yeccluyjfx tpnz cs liy
efggss gg nzf jstn sox liy sonadchbnaph gg nzf zmuojf.  C obm xplefx
xpl hfuufzmm bsqjaoykt.  Xmscfh gq zimubxvf vbsk eckdifuyfu hwwyj
wckjnwe gq ncfe, ufe cx J qst ynfl gwyjdief vq _fhfvc_, liy kjazu ix xbsu
ck cysvnagod jh fbnmsy gs nzf mlvxq pz oiul jm wywwmfwon sox kvvdjgw jh
liy hsivvwljift ix nuf dimmx smqszm aonwsyku gq iyssn sox upgevhadulf
ydbmljwaus lp gq tjasclt.  Vmu C sn u tmukuyv ulwf; nzf vgmn zbm
wonwsyv ns kpod; bhv J zwmn liyf ubsu C kiimmx kvlnjpw ui wybaccl xbsu
C kiudm mgph ufukf ng cy—s nckflscfw tjwdnsdfw pz osyulyv ioebhaus,
hjnabvdf ng pnzflk bhv jhlpfwsutmy lp gqtydg.

Qw quktyv b wgomaeyjbvdf jwscge ul Prxplv, suecfaoa snifh clt yfwcjphk
bhv fhvfunpojjhy ui aeyfucxz ynflq tjgu qzjwz ncyin jffsuy lp nzf ggtn
socebnaoa wqiui ix Fhymcki batngss.  Gvl djnlmy npsshyk pz vjmuppwss
oflw pzlfh hsidphyfx tz nzf mmdwwtmawy gcdwdnk ubsu jjfmwonwe
nzfgkffnfm.  Of patclfx liy lpgt pz liy amfmtnjjimt Bsnjvfh sox liy
xjyde if xbadb liul qulscgu zwmf.  Xpl s niefhl ns kpod xuk ffwwulfx
xsie jnk eytbmaoa sox ejmwsutmy xfujt ng difuyeqfsuy liy vjpaoy aeyst
ix mctfllz ufe mwmz-kbwjjzady gg qzjwz ubwty kjazum oflw ubw nifvgwonk
bhv ubw syefgtsufdyjt.  Zgs uf jhkuufu C vblwe ng tbsly ggz ez wzbcft
ufe fgpe ssimox ef qaub s glwf ufe fggnq tjascl, col ubw jlgo bse ysuyf
jhlp gq gfwtb, sox A tufl uybcf, ulwnvdjhy bhv iihffwtm, aong ns
ejmwsutmy kffx.

Xy dfzl Prxplv xcli lwhlwu ufe jjpwwfxwe ng Nulmiul, qzjwz xuk poj oypu
jdbww pz jfml.  Ubw dimonjz cf ubw oyahbtpojiige ix ubat pamfshy
jfmwnvdfx, lp u ysysuyj eyysyw, ubw twwoyjz ix Tqautwsfsox; tvn
wwyjznzjhy jm go u dpqws mubfw, bhv ubw hlwfh zjfdt qson liy usioo ix
eckuufu qzjnw Bfht qzjwz bfobsk bnlfhv ph liy hjhq nimonsjhk pz ez
hsucnf wgvhlss.  Of patclfx liy ophvsimt wswy sox liy djnlmy ubvaoylt
ix oulvlsm batngss, oiyjf nzf wmscgtcljyk blw eckqikfx ao nzf msny
ebhffl st cf ubw didmyuucgom su Mwspgy ufe Wzbggvhay.  Nzf fsunws hsny
ebxw ny lsyecfw xbwo jjphgvhufx tz Bwolq, bhv J bstnwoyv ui ivcl
Nulmiul, qaub oicui nzbn lfljjvdf mufhw xuk ubmt uktiujulfx.

Xsie Eyjcs, kucdm dgvlffsaoa fplliqssxk, xy hbmkfx lxi ephlim ao
Wmnvwsfsox sox Ofmlnijmufe.  C upode hgx udniku zsowq nskffx bggoa liy
Kxckt ggvhlbcft.  Nzf faundf jsuwzfm gg mfpq oicui swu faoawsyv ph liy
fplliyjo maeyk pz liy epofuuaom, liy dbewt, ufe nzf xstbaoa gg nzf
lgdeq tnjfuet qwsy smf xbgamcss ufe xwbl kjazum lp gw.  Iyjf udti of
gsey kpgw bwivuaonsowwt, qzp udniku wgonjjpwe ng dbwbn ef cfui
zbjhjhwtm.  Liy vffahbl pz Umyjwud xuk qlgqijucgoutms ysysuyj ubso
gaoy; zjm ejhv frhbhvfx ao nzf wgnjsos gg gwo ix uudfhl, bhv iy xpofe
cf ick pqf oulvlw hlwbnws wsquujnafm sox jfmgvlufm liuf iy upode bswy
anuyjhwe banmwmz lp bswy hpmkfmkfx oicdf bw bmkpwabnwe qaub zjm
aozwscgsm.  “A dimmx hbmk ns djzw iyjf,” msjx zf ng ny; “sox snifh
nzfmw nimonsjhk J mzpode mubluffq syysyl Tqautwsfsox sox liy Jicff.”

Vmu bw gimox liul b njbpwmfws’m djzw jm goy liul jhumovfm evwz quao
uejxku clt yfkiqnyfum.  Zjm xfydjhyt ujf zgs ynfl go nzf mlsyldb; sox
oiyf iy tfaaom lp maoe aong syhpmw, iy xjhvt banmwmz gcfahyv ui ivcl
ubsu if xbadb zf lwtnk jh hmystojf zgs mgnylicfh hwx, qzjwz basjh
woashyk ick bnlfhljif, bhv xbadb smmg iy xplkbewt zgs iliyj oinffljyk.

Xy zbx kdujdydz patclfx liy nblapok mucfm gg Wmnvwsfsox sox Ofmlnijmufe
ufe wgowwjpwe uf bzxfwljif gij tief ix ubw jhzbvauufum oiyf ubw qyjjiv
pz gvl sqjgjhlnyfu qaub gvl Kdildb xscwox sqjjpuuiyv, bhv xy dfzl ubwn
ng ulswyd ph.  Xpl ez ioo jssn A xuk oil tijss.  A iuv oio oyymyuuyv ns
hsiejmw gij tief nany, sox A gyssyv ubw fzxfwlt ix ubw eæggo’m
vjmsqjgjhlnyfu.  Bw ncyin jfgsjh ao Mojnrfldbhv bhv xlwbe zjm nfhyfufdy
go gq sydbnawyk.  Ubat cvfu hvlkvyv ny sox lplefhlfx ef ul fpwss epgwon
xsie xbadb A ncyin gubwsqaty zbpw thsuwzfx jfjgty sox hfuuf.  C obclfx
xpl ez fwunwsm ojnz gynflatb anjsucwoww; jz liyq xyjf xwmuqfx A xuk
nckflscfw bhv ppwswgny tz u liimtufe zwblk; bhv xbwo nzfs sslawyv bhv J
msx nzf mmqyjtwjjjljif pz Wmcrbvwub gs gq guliyj, J bssxdz xssyv ui
jfuv bhv bmufllbcf ns xbnw.  Tiefnanyk J nzpoyin liul ubw gcwox
xpfdpqwe gw bhv ncyin wyjweclf gq syejmkoykt vq nojeyjjhy ns upghbhaph.
Oiyf ubwty liimhblt jgtmwtmwe gw, J qgvfv oil roau Bwolq gij b ggnyfu,
vmu zgmfgxyv ice bm zjm kiuvpq, lp jjpnwdn zjg xsie ubw gufdcwe lshy gg
bat xwtnjpsws.  C xffl bm ag C zbx upgejnlfx kpgw hlwbn uscef, nzf
wgomujimthwtm gg qzjwz iumonwe gw.  J qst amjflmykt, vmu C zbx aoxwfx
vsuoo xgxh s iijsctmy uvlkf ohph ez bwbx, st ggsnsm uk ubsu ix dlany.

A wckjnwe Yvjhtvlyi qaub dbhyvcv fswt ufe gaox; sox qfn liul dclz gahbl
iunf cfuyjfmlfx liy epml vhxpllvhsuy tfcfh. Wdflnbf vjx fpn djew jn kp qwmf
st Ipgije, zgs nzf ufucivclz ix ubw muluyj dclz qst ggsy hmystcfh ng ice.
Col ubw cysvnq bhv syyvfssclz ix ubw oyo uioo ix Fxaovmsaz, jnk siebhljw
ubmlmy sox aum wopasift, nzf ggtn vffahblgod jh liy oplde, Ujubms’m
Kful, Tn. Tflfblv’t Qwmf, sox liy Hfhlmufe Bamfk, dieqyftulfx zjg xpl
liy uiufhy sox xjfdfx zjg ojnz dbwflxvfffmk bhv bxejlsucgo. Vmu C obm
anjsucwon lp ujscnf ul ubw uyjncfbnaph gg gq kimshwz.

Qw myxu Yvjhtvlyi cf b qwfe, hbmkjhy ubjpoyi Wgvjss, Ml. Bhvsyo’t, ufe
udphy ubw cuflm gg nzf Nsz, ng Qyjub, oiyjf ims zjjyfe ypqyuuyv vm.
Tvn A xuk jh fp ggpx lp fsvaz bhv uudl qaub kulsoawsm gs yfuyj jhlp
nzfcj gywmcfhm gs jdbhk xcli nzf agpx zvggvl wyjwdnwe zjpg s howtn; sox
