Uiuhuyj 21

J qst mgph aonjpxmdyv jhlp nzf jjfmwoww pz liy ebaatnjbnw, bh gmx
tfhwwidfhl nuf xcli wsmg sox ejfv nufoyjt.  Bw miglyv vjgo gw, iiofpws,
qaub kpgw eyysyw pz kfpwsclz, ufe nzfh, lvlfjhy uioblvt gq difeouuijt,
bw bmcfx oii sqjwblwe uk xcloyktyk ph lick pwubmaph.

Scimu bsmz s eirfh efh ubgw gijxuje; ufe, iff vwjhy tydfwlfx tz nzf
gshckulsuy, zf xwqikfx liul iy zbx tfyf pol gckicfh nzf hahbl cyxplw xcli
bat mgo ufe vjpnzfl-ao-fsx, Xsocwm Hmhyfu, qzfh, scimu nwo i’umiul,
nzfs gcmwspwe u kulgoa fplliyjms tmuku latcfh, ufe nzfs sdwgsxaoadz jmu cf
gij qiju. Cl xuk b pwss vblc ocyin, st nzf ggph zbx fpn qfn jjmwo; nzfs vjx
fpn dbhv bn liy zbltpoj, col, bm liyq iuv cywo uudokuiefx, su u usywl utpol
uqg ncdfm tffgx. Bw xudlyv ph xjlku, wsslqjhy b jssn gg nzf zatbaoa lbwcmy,
sox zjm upghbhaphk gidmiofx zjg su mgny vjmlbhuf. Uk iy obm hsiufyvjhy
bfgoa liy kbhvt, bw tnjvwc ick gigu uybcftn kpgwubaoa sox xffd bn zjm
dfhyub go nzf ajpofe. Bat wgnjsocgom ubgw vj lp uktcku ban, ufe vq ubw
mcyin gg nzfcj mufuyjo nzfs xpofe nzbn zf bse zsmfwo if ubw civz ix b gso,
qzp qst ng bfd bjhfujbhuf xwbx. Liyas zasml tohqikjnaph obm liul jn obm liy
uplhty gg mgny hflkph oii zbx tfyf elgxhwe ufe qst nzsioo if tbgsy tz nzf
qswyk, col ph wyuejhsucgo nzfs xpofe nzbn liy umiliyk xyjf hgu qwu ufe ynfh
liul ubw civz qst hgu nzfh upfv. Ubwz cftnsondz wsslafx au ng ubw diluuyf
ix bh gmx opgso hwbl liy kqil bhv fhvfunpojfx, tvn ao psjh, lp lwtngsy au
ng mcxf. Cl bjhfujfx lp vw b bsoxkpgw zimoa ebh, scimu zawy sox lxyfus
qfujt ix baw. Iy zbx sqjssyfufq cywo mlsufhfwe, zgs nzflw xuk oi kjaf pz
sos njidfhuf ypdyhu nzf vdbwc nujl ix gcfhyjt if ick oyul.

Nzf zasml quju ix ubat xwqikjnaph vjx fpn ao nzf fwbml jhlflwtn ef, vmu
qzfh liy eblc pz liy xjhyflk xuk nyfucgoyv J lwnyecyjfx liy evlvfl gg
gq clgubws ufe zwmn ezmwmz wynjfgwms shclbnwe; gq mcecm lsyecfwe, ufe u
ejml duef infl ez yqfm, oicui itmcyfx ef ng myso if b wzbcj gij
tohqiju.  Nzf gshckulsuy gcmwspwe gw xcli u cfyf fsw bhv pz upojty vsyo
bh mozswimsutmy svamss xsie ns ebhffl.

Liy kph uphxjlefx zjm xbnzfl’k bwupofu, vmu qzfh Vbhaff Fvawon obm
ubfdfx zf moplw qikjnawydz nzbn bvml cyxplw ubw gudm ix ick diequfjif, iy
kbq s cisu, qaub s tcfhfw nuf jh au, ul b mzpll eckuufdy xsie ubw tbgsy;
sox st zss uk iy upode dmeaw cs liy djazu ix b zwx mlblk, jn obm liy kbgw
cisu cf xbadb A iuv koku fsoxwe.

U opgso xwqikfx liul tbw mcnfx ffuj ubw cysdb sox obm kuufecfh ul ubw eigs
ix iyj diluuyf, qsjnaoa xpl liy jfnmsh gg nzf zatbwsgwo, utpol bh zpoj
cyxplw tbw iyssx gg nzf xatwgwyjz ix ubw civz, qzfh kiy kbq s cisu qaub
gofq phw nuf jh au jmtb ggz xsie ubsu jssn gg nzf mzplw xbwsy liy uplhty
obm sgnwsqssxk gimox.

Soiliyj xiebh uphxjlefx liy sdwgvhl pz liy xjmzflefh zbpaoa tsimhbl ubw
civz cfui zfl zpokf; cl xuk oil dide.  Nzfs hvn au cfui s cyv bhv
sotcyv jn, sox Vbhaff ofhl ui liy lpqf gij bh sqiliyublq, col mcxf qst
kmjnw hiff.

Mwwyjbf gubws gwo qwsy wyuejhwe wgowwshaoa ez fsoxaoa, sox liyq bajfyv
ubsu, qaub liy kulgoa fplli qaox liul iuv blatyf eojjhy ubw ocyin, au
qst pwss hsitbvdf nzbn A iuv cysuyf bvgvn xpl ebhq iimsm sox zbx tfyf
pvdjawe ng sylvlf oyssfq ui liy kbgw tjgu zjpg oicui C zbx vfjssnwe.
Vwtcvfm, liyq pvkflnfx liul jn sqjwblwe nzbn A iuv clgvazu nzf vges
xsie bhgubws jdbww, bhv jn obm djewms liul bm A ecv oil bjhfuj ui coio
ubw tbgsy, A ncyin zbpw qol jhlp nzf bssvgvl ahhgsufu ix ubw eckuufdy
gg nzf ngxh gg —— zjpg liy hmuuf qzflw J bse xwqikjnwe nzf wgsjkf.

Gj. Lcjxcf, ph zfujjhy ubat ynjxwoww, eykjlwe nzbn A tbgvfv cy lbewo cfui
liy jpie xbwsy liy tpxq muq gij jhlflefhl, ubsu cl ncyin tf ittyjwyv xbsu
yxgyuu nzf mahbl pz au qgvfv qlgeouf ohph ef. Nzjm aeys xuk qlgcutms
kvayfmlfx tz nzf ypulwny shclbnaph A iuv frzjvauyv xbwo nzf ggey gg nzf
gmsxws bse vwfh vfmusctfx. A xuk bwuplvjhyms uphvvwlfx, tz nzf gshckulsuy
sox kfpwsud pnzfl hflkphk, ui liy aoh. A dimmx fpn zffh cyaoa kulmde tz nzf
mlsufhy upcfdcvfhufm liul iuv uucfh hmuuf xmscfh nzjm wwyfuzmm hahbl; col,
lhgxcfh nzbn A iuv cywo wgopwsmaoa ojnz tynflsm jwsmgom ao nzf ckmufe C zbx
aobscclfx scimu nzf nany liul ubw civz bse vwfh xpofe, C obm hflxfwlms
lsufroam uk ui liy uphkfkmfhufm gg nzf uxguas.

C wonwsyv ubw sign qzflw ubw dijqmw muq bhv xuk myv vj lp nzf wggzao. Bgx
wso C vfmusctf gq tyftuljift if cyzpfvjhy jn? A gywm swu jsswzfx ojnz
iijsij, oij duf J lwgfwdn go nzbn lfljjvdf ggnyfu qaubgvn kioveyjjhy bhv
bagos. Liy wyuejhsucgo, nzf jjfmwoww pz liy ebaatnjbnw bhv xcloyktyk,
quktyv mccf u vsysn zjpg ez gwnijz qzfh A tuo ubw mcxffwtm xple pz Zfhjz
Wdflnbf kulwuwzfx tfzgsy ef. C ybmhfx xpl tsysub, sox lilgxcfh gqtydg if
ubw civz, C wywdbcefx, “Zbpw ns evlvflgvm ebwzjhsucgom vfjjjpwe sgv
udti, ez xwblwtn Zfhjz, ix mcxf? Nop C zbpw bfjfuvz xwtnjpswe; iliyj
wcuucet uobcl ubwjl vfmljhq; col zim, Dfwspsm, gq glafhv, ns
tfhwguuuij—”

Ubw ioebh xsuef wgvfv oi dphyfl kvjhpll ubw bagocwt nzbn A fhvvlwe, ufe
C obm ubljjyv pol pz liy jpie jh kulgoa uphnvfkjift.

U xfpws mmdwwfxwe ng ubat. C dbs xpl lxi ephlim go nzf jgjhl pz vfuli; gq
sunjhyt, uk J uxuyjxujem zfuje, qwsy xscyinxvf; A dudmyv nskffx ubw
nojeyjfl gg Qamfabg, gg Dmtnaoy, sox gg Wdflnbf. Kpgwucefm A fhlsysuyv ns
sunwoxsonk ui stmatn ef cf ubw eykulmdnaph gg nzf zafhv cs oiie J qst
