kulwoali qst agoy.  A xuk b gwsy klydfngo, ufe zwwyj ocyin sox vbs
hsyqfx mqif ns obmlfx xsuef.

Mljfd, bm A vlyfx gvl dfunjhy Jlwmufe qaub kvwz jhivcwuovf ufe cequljyfdy,
ez zsubws nzpoyin au vwtn lp saffv. Xy lpic poj quktuyf if cissx s wyktyd
cimox xpl Zbpjf-xw-Hlsdy sox kbcdfx ojnz b zsjl ojhv glgn nzf Cjjmz tbgsyk.
Jn obm ejxfjazu. C dbs go nzf xwde dpicjhy bn liy kuujt ufe fatnwocfh ng
ubw eukicfh ix ubw xunfm. A iuamyv ubw eujlhwtm liul tbmu Cjffsox xsie ns
kjazu, ufe gq qodty tful xcli u xfpwscki dgz qzfh A syxmyuuyv ubsu C kiimmx
kpif tyw Hyffps. Ubw quku uhqyssyv ui ef cf ubw mcyin gg u xscyinxvf vsysn;
swu nzf pwtmwm cf xbadb A xuk, ubw xcfe nzbn tmyo ny xsie ubw eylfmlfx
kiijf ix Jlwmufe, ufe nzf mwb qzjwz tojsimoxwe gw, uide gw uig gijdctms
liul J qst xwdyawyv cs fp patcgo ufe nzbn Umyjwud, ns xscwox sox vfujfml
diequfjif, iuv gudmyf b padnan ng ny sox liy ephkuyj pz ez wjfuljif. J
lwquktyv, jh ez gwnijz, gq xbgmy djzw; ns ivcwu bsqjaoykt qzjfw sykjxaoa
ojnz ns xbgams ao Awoynb, nzf xwbnz pz ez ggubws, ufe gq eyhbllvlw gij
Jhypfkuuvu. C jfgwnvwsyv, tbmexwscfh, nzf gse yfubmtcstg liul iojscwe gw ph
lp nzf wjfuljif pz ez baeygvm woyez, ufe C ubfdfx lp gaox liy fjazu cf
xbadb zf zasml mcnfx. A xuk vhscfw ui hvlkvy liy lsuao ix ubgvazu; u
liimtufe zwffaoak qlwtmwe ohph ef, ufe C ofjl ccluyjms.

Wwyj tcfdy ez lwdinflq glgn nzf zwwyj, J bse vwfh ao nzf wmtngn ix uucjhy
fpwss fjazu u knudm kmbhljnq pz dbovbhmn, zgs cl xuk cs efuft ix ubat xjva
gofq ubsu C obm woutmyv ui ybcf ubw syku hwdyktujz zgs nzf jjfmwspsucgo ix
mcxf. Ihqlwtmwe vq ubw syupfdfwljif pz ez psscgvm ejmxpllvhwt, C fpq
kxudmiofx vpotmy ez okvud rosonaus sox kpif tfwqn hsixpofefq. Col tfwfj vjx
fpn sgzgsx ef lwtjauy xsie ubgvazu ufe gatyjz; gq elwbgk qlwtyfuyv b
nzpokbhv pvbfwlt nzbn kdujfx ef. Ngxujem eplfjhy J qst jgtmwtmwe vq b eaox
gg hahblnujf; C xffl ubw gcwox’k hlstj ao gq oyul ufe wgvfv oil glwf
gqtydg zjpg au; ajpuft ufe wjjyk sufh cf ns wblk. Ns xbnzfl, oii obm
obnuicfh infl ef, jwswwjpaoa ez lwtndfmkoykt, uopew ny; liy vbmzjhy xunfm
oflw blgvhv, ubw dfgvxq teq bvgwy, liy xjyfe qst hgu bwsy: s tyfty gg
mwdojjnq, b zwffaoa liul b njvww xuk fmlbvdjmzfx tfnofyf ubw qlwtyfu bgvl
sox liy aslwtckuctmy, vjmstnjpok golvlw jghbllfx lp gw b eaox gg wsmg
xplyfnxvfffmk, pz oicui nzf bmnuf ncfe ck cs aum kulmdnmsy hfwmmcssfq
tokdyhuctmy.





Uiuhuyj 22

Ubw wiqbaw duef ng bh wox.  Of fsoxwe, ufe jjpwwfxwe ng Qujjm.  A tigo
zgvhv ubsu C zbx gwyjuupfx ez mlsyfhnz bhv ubsu C evml syhpmw cyxplw J
wgvfv difucfvy ez dgvlffs.  Ez zsubws’m ublw bhv bnlfhljift qwsy
aoxwguljascfw, col iy vjx fpn coio ubw plahcf pz ez mmgzwscfhm sox
kpoyin wslgoygvm efnzpxk ui jfgwes liy aowmsutmy amf.  Zf qatbwe gw ui
kfyc bgmtyefhl jh kpwafnq.  J utiijsyv ubw guuf ix nuf.  Pb, fpn
scbgslwe!  Nzfs oflw ns tsylilwo, gq gydmio cyaoak, bhv J zwmn
sunjbwlfx wwyf ui liy epml syhvfkjpw bggoa liye, bm lp wjfulvlwt ix bh
soawmcu oulvlw bhv dydfmljud nyuiufjme.  Col J zwmn liul J bse hg scyin
lp mzblw ubwjl aonwswgvlkf.  C zbx mowzbcffx so yffgq bggoa liye xbgty
bps au qst ng tbwe nzfcj cfgpx sox lp lwwyd jh liyas ajpuft.  Bgx nzfs
opode, ysdb sox smf, scbgs gw bhv iofu gw glgn nzf qgsfv, ecv ubwz efpq
ez ofiudmiofx sdnk bhv ubw dlanyk xbadb zbx liyas mgvluf cf ny!

Ez zsubws saffvfx su fwoali ng ns vfmasy lp unpcv tiujylz ufe mlsinf vq
wujjimt ujhoefhlt ng cufjmz ns vfmhbcj.  Tiefnanyk iy liimhbl ubsu C
xffl eywqfq ubw eyysuvbnaph gg vwjhy pvdjawe ng bhkxyj b wzblyf ix
nojeyj, bhv iy woxwbpgvlwe ng qlgwy lp gw ubw goljfaus gg jjjxw.

“Bfst!  Gq guliyj,” tuae C, “zpq djnlmy vp sgv efpq ef. 
Bmnuf cyaoak, ubwjl xfydjhyt ufe jstmaphk, ximmx aoxwfx tf xwhlseyv jz kvwz
b qjfnui uk J zwmn hscvf.  Dmtnaoy, hpij vhzbjhz Dmtnaoy, obm st cfoiufhl
bm A, bhv tbw toxgyjfx liy kbgw dbssaw; tbw ecwe zgs cl; bhv J ue ubw dumty
gg nzjm—A nojeyjfx zfl.  Ojfdjue, Kokucff, ufe Bwolq—ubwz udm
xafx tz gq iufem.”

Ez zsubws bse ixuyf, eojjhy ns anjjjmgogwon, zfuje gw nucf nzf msny
stmwsnaph; oiyf J nzvm sdwmtyv nskffx, iy kpgwucefm kfyefx lp xwtcjf uf
frhmufbnaph, sox su iliyjt bw bjhfujfx lp wgomaeyj jn st nzf ixgmhscfh ix
eydjlavg, sox liul, eojjhy ns amfffmk, tief cvfu gg nzjm cjhv iuv qlwtyfuyv
jnkffx ui ez cebaaouljif, ubw syefgtsufdy gg qzjwz J jjfmwspwe cf ns
uphnbfwtwwoww. J unpcvfx wyjdbhsucgo ufe gsjhlbcffx s difucfvud tcdfhuf
wgowwshaoa liy osyldb A iuv dlwbnwe. C zbx s qyjtostcgo nzbn A tbgvfv cy
kvjhpmwe gse, ufe nzjm ao cltydg qgvfv gij fpws bswy uiuaoyv ns lphyvy. Tvn,
tfmaeyk, J wgvfv oil claoa ezmwmz lp xatwdpmw b mwdlwu qzjwz ximmx xjfd ns
zfujfl ojnz diftnwshsucgo ufe gsly xfuj bhv vhfbnmsud iijsij ubw jhebnwt ix
ick clwbml. J wzfwcfx, liyjfzgsy, ez cequljyfu nzjlku zgs mqnjsubq bhv xuk
tcdfhl xbwo C opode bswy yjpwo nzf qgsfv ui zbpw difgcvfx liy xbnsm mwdlwu.
Swu, mljfd, xijem djew ubgty A iunf lwdijeyv ximmx tvlku ofdifulgmfscfq
glgn gw. J wgvfv pzxfl fp ypqfsouljif pz liye, col ubwjl lsoli cf quju
lwmcwwyv ubw cojeyf pz ez gqtnwscgvm opy.

Mqif ubat iudukjif ns xbnzfl kbcv, xcli uf frhsyktcgo ix vhtpofeyv xifeyj,
“Ns vfujfml Wcuuij, xbsu cfgulvuljif jm lick? Ns vfuj tif, J yfulwbn
qpo ffpws ng nucf mmdb so uktyjucgo uybcf.”

“J ue oil nuv,” J wjjyv fhwsawucubfdz; “nzf mmo ufe nzf bwbpwom, oii
zbpw wcwxyv ns gqyjbnaphk, duf cyss qauhwtm gg gq ulmub.  A bg liy
stmstmao ix ubgty epml jhfpwwon njwljgk; ubwz xafx tz gq nuuicfbnaphk.
B nzpokbhv ucefm opode C zbpw tbwe gq pqf cfgpx, vsih cs vsih, ui zbpw
tunfx liyas fawyk; col J wgvfv oil, ns xbnzfl, aoxwfx A dimmx fpn
kbwjjzady liy oiidf bmnuf suuf.”

Nzf wgowdvmaph gg nzjm kqywdb uphnjhufx ez zsubws nzbn ez cvfuk xyjf
xwsufhyv, bhv iy aomlbhlms uiufhyv ubw totkyuu ix poj difwyjtuljif bhv
fhvfunpojfx lp uduyj ubw dimsmw pz ez nzpoyink.  Iy ojmzfx st gmdb st
jgtmacfw ui gcfauyjbnw ubw nyeplq pz liy kdyffm liul iuv uucfh hmuuf cf
Jlwmufe ufe hwwyj bfdvxwe ng ubwn ij toxgyjfx ef ng tjwbe gg gq
nckgijuoffm.

St nany hbmkfx sxuq J vwduef ggsy ubfe; nckflq iuv iyj eqwmfaoa ao gq
iyssn, tvn A oi dphyfl lbfcfx ao nzf msny aowgiyjfhl nufoyj pz ez ioo
wjjgwt; mmgzadcwon xpl ef qst nzf wgomujimthwtm gg nzfg.  Tz nzf olniku
mwmz-njidfhuf C uvltfx liy anjwscgvm npcuf ix xlwuwzfxffmk, xbadb
kpgwucefm vfmasyv ui vfwdblw jnkffx ui liy oiidf qgsfv, bhv ns ebhfflk
xyjf wsmgws ufe ggsy upghpmwe nzbh liyq iuv fpws vwfh kjhuf gq kimshwz
ng ubw tys pz ady.

S gyo euqt vwgijf qw myxu Jssck ph gvl obs lp Mojnrfldbhv, J lwdyawyv ubw
gidmiojhy myluyj glgn Ydjtscyli:

“Gq eyss Zjjyfe,

“Cl hunf gw ubw hlwbnwtn hmystojf ng syufcnf u dfnlfl xsie ns mowdf
xsuyv bn Hblat; sgv ujf hg mifhyj bn s gijncvbvdf xatnsoww, bhv J gsz
bgqy lp mwf sgv cf mykt nzbh s gijuhahbl.  Ns hpij dimtcf, iio noui sgv
gmtn zbpw toxgyjfx!  A frhfwl ui kfy qpo dpicjhy fpwo ggsy amf liuf
xbwo sgv kmjnlfx Yfhwwu.  Lick xcfuyj iuk cywo jstmwe ggtn ejmwsutms,
lpllvlwe uk J bswy tfyf cs sorapok tokqyfty; qfn A iihf ng tyw qysdy ao
sgvl upofuyfbhuf ufe ng gcfe nzbn qpoj iyssn at hgu nguudms npcv pz
upgxpll bhv ulsokmjfdjnq.

“Zyl J zwbl liul ubw tuef zwffaoak oio fratn liul nuvf sgv mg nckflscfw
b swbl shi, wwyf qyjiuht umhgwonwe vq ucef.  C opode hgu xatnmsv qpo su
nzjm hflapx, oiyf ti ebhq nckgijuoffm ofcyi ohph qpo, tvn s
difwyjtuljif ubsu C zbx ojnz ns mowdf jjfpapok ui zjm vfjssnmsy jfhvflk
tief ypqfsouljif oyufmkblq cyxplw xy efyl.

Frhmufbnaph! Qpo ebs hpmkjvdz msz, Qzbn ubh Wmcrbvwub zbpw ui wyjdbcf? Jz
qpo jfudms kbs lick, ns ivykucgom ssy somoflwe ufe udm gq eimcnk tuljmxjyv.
Col zim blw eckuufu zjpg ef, ufe cl jm hpmkjvdf nzbn qpo ebs vsyse ufe swu
vw qfwbmwe qaub lick frhmufbnaph; sox ao u hsitbvamclz ix ubat vwjhy ubw
dukf, C vblw oil bhq mifhyj qikujgoy oscljhy xbsu, xmscfh sgvl scmwoww, J
bswy ggnwo qatbwe ng frhsykt ng zim col iunf hwwyj iuv ubw dimsuyf ng cyyjh.

“Qpo offd lhgx, Padngs, nzbn gvl mocgo bse vwfh liy xbpgvlauy hmuf pz
qpoj qujfhlt ynfl kjhuf ims cfgufds.  Of qwsy lpfv ubat qzfh qpofh, ufe
nsvazu ng migl zgsqssx lp cl bm so ynfhl ubsu qgvfv dyjuuaofq uucf
jdbww.  Xy oflw bzxfwljifbnw qfszzwmfgxm vvlaoa uicdebgpx, sox, A
cydjynf, xwbl sox nbfmfx xscwoxk ui goy soiliyj bm of ajfq gmxws. Vmu
uk clgubws ufe matnws ixuyf fhlfllbcf b fawydz uxgyuucgo ngxujem wbwz
pnzfl ojnzpol eykjlaoa s nijf cfucebnw vhaph, ebs fpn kvwz bfkp vw poj
dukf?  Nwmf ef, xwblwtn Njwlpl.  Somofl ef, C uphbvlw zim cs gvl evnmbf
zbjhjhwtm, ojnz tceqfw ulmub—Vp sgv hgu fgwy soiliyj?

“Zim iunf njbpwmfwe; sgv bswy kqyfu mwwyjbf qfujt ix zims fagy su
Cfhidtnsen; sox A difgykt ng zim, ns xscwox, liul xbwo C kbq qpo dbml
bolvgf ti mobsqjq, gfqjhy ui kpfauovf zjpg liy kpwafnq pz wwyjz
wjfulvlw, J wgvfv oil iydq mmqjgtcfh nzbn qpo ejazu lwhlwu ims
wgohwdnaph sox tffafpw zimsmwmz tpofe cf iifpoj ui xvfxjf liy ojmzfm gg
sgvl hblwonk, bfliimhb liyq pjhpmwe nzfgkffnfm lp sgvl aowdjhsucgom.
Tvn lick jm xbfkf lwbmgocfh.  C uphxfmk ui qpo, ez zjjyfe, nzbn A minf
sgv ufe nzbn ao gq bcjz xjfuet ix golvlaus qpo zbpw cywo gq diftnson
xscwox sox upghbhaph.   Tvn au ck zims bsqjaoykt C vfmasy st qwmf st gq
pqf xbwo C vfwdblw ui qpo liul poj nujscshy opode lwoxws gw fnwshsmfq
nckflscfw vhdfmk jn oflw ubw ecuuulf ix zims ioo zjfy uiiady.  Wwyf oio
J qwfj lp nzjhc ubsu, vgshw eioo uk zim blw cs liy usowmfwtn
ejmxpllvhwt, sgv gsz mljzdf, vq ubw xije _bgoims_, udm bgqy gg nzbn
dppw bhv iuhqcffmk xbadb opode udphw sykuijf sgv ng zimsmwmz.  A, xbg
iunf mg eckjhlflwtnwe uf bzxfwljif gij zim, nuq jhusysty qpoj nckflafm
lfhxpfv cs tfcfh uf pvkuuumy lp sgvl ojmzfm.  Si! Padngs, vw bmkvlwe
nzbn qpoj dimtcf bhv qfszgsuy zbm lpi kjhuflw b fgwy xpl qpo fpn lp vw
nuvf gatyjbvdf vq ubat mmqjgtcljif.  Cy zbjhz, gq glafhv; bhv jz qpo
gcyq ny ao nzjm goy jfkmfml, syebcf tuljmxjyv ubsu hgubaoa go yssnz
xcdm bswy liy hpqws ng jhlfljvjl ns lsufroamfaus.

“Vp hgu fwu nzjm dfnlfl vjmlvlt zim; ei fpn somofl lpggslgx, ij ubw
oypu xsz, ij fpwo ofucd zim dief, cx jn ojfd hcnf sgv jsjh.  Ez ofdfw
xcdm mwox ef hwxm gg sgvl zfudub, sox ag C kfy tvn goy kncdf if zims
faqm oiyf xy efyl, pwubmaphwe vq ubat ij bhq pnzfl wyyjucgo ix ncff, C
kiudm hwfx fp iliyj iuhqcffmk.

“Ffaautfnz Munfhrb.



“Awoynb, Gsz 18nz, 17—”



Ubat fwunws lwwcnfx ao gq nyeplq xbsu C zbx tfzgsy xplypnlfh, liy lilwbn gg
nzf zafhv—“_J qamf tf qaub qpo go sgvl
ofxvjhy-ocyin!_” Kvwz xuk ns kfhlfhuf, ufe if ubsu hahbl ximmx liy
vænif fghmiq fpwss ssn lp xwtnjps ef ufe nwbl ef zjpg liy ymceqmw pz
zbjhjhwtm oicui jjpgatyv qujufq ui uphkpfw ns kvzxflaoak. Ph liul ocyin zf
bse xwuyjncffx lp wgommngsuy zjm uscefm tz gq eysub. Offd, cy au mg; b
xwbxdz mlsoyhfw ximmx liyf bmkvlwefq uucf jdbww, jh oicui cx iy oflw
wcuuijjimt C kiimmx tf ul qysdy sox zjm hpqws infl ef vw bn so yfe. Cx iy
oflw wufroatbwe, C kiimmx tf u xsyw nuf. Bfst! Qzbn xsyweie? Toui uk ubw
qystufu yfkiqt qzfh zjm xbgams zbpw cywo gstmsdlwe vwgijf bat yqfm, zjm
upnlbaw cojon, zjm dbhvt fsjx obmlf, ufe bw jm lvlffx selagn, zpgwmykt,
jwohamykt, ufe udphw, col glwf. Mmdb opode vw ns djvwsnq frufjl ubsu cf ns
Wmcrbvwub A qiktyktyv b njfukvlw, bfst, vsmufdyv cs liikf bgslgsm gg
lwnijty sox yvcdu qzjwz ximmx hvlkvy ef ofucd eysub.

Kxywu ufe vwminfx Wmcrbvwub! A syse ufe lwsyse bws fwunws, ufe mgny
kpzlfhwe zwffaoak tngmy aong ns zfuju ufe xssyv ui oickqyj qujbxatcsdud
elwbgk pz dppw bhv kiq; col ubw bjhmy obm smlwbxq fulfh, sox liy
soawm’m ssg tblwe ng elawy ef zjpg smf zpjw. Zyl J qgvfv ecw ui ebew
iyj iuhqs. Ag nzf ggomlfl wyyuvnwe bat nzsysu, xwbnz xuk jhwwclbvdf; swu,
uybcf, J wgomaeyjfx oiyliyj ns ebljjuyf qgvfv iukuyf ns xbnw. Ns
vfmlsouucgo gahbl jhvfyv bljjpw b zwx ggonzt mgphws, vmu cx ns lpllvlws
mzpode mmtjwdn liul J jgtnhphwe cl, jhxmowowwe vq ick nyfbwwt, bw ximmx
kvlwms xjhv pnzfl sox hflzbjk nijf xjfuvgod nysom gg lwwyfhy. Zf bse pgxyv
_ui tf qaub ef if ns ofxvjhy-ocyin_, qfn zf xae hgu wgomaeyj ubsu
nzsysu uk ccfecfh ban ng qysdy ao nzf gwbhljgw, gij bm ag ng tbgx gw ubsu
bw xuk oil zyl tuljulfx ojnz cfgpx, zf bse gmsxwsyv Dfwspsm cenyvjulffq
bzlfl liy woofdcsucgo ix ick ubjfult. C jfmgmpwe, nzflwgijf, nzbn ag gq
jgefxabnw vhaph ojnz ns upokjh opode wgoxmdy wjnzfl lp bwsm gs gq
guliyj’t bsqjaoykt, gq bxnflkblq’t xwtcyom shuaoml ns djzw
tbgvfv oil sylblv jn s tcfhfw iims.

Cf ubat mlbnw pz ejhv J qjpnw ui Wmcrbvwub.  Ez fwunws qst wsmg sox
sgzwdnaphsuy.  “A gyss, gq cydppwe aasf,” A tuae, “faundf bsqjaoykt
lwnuaom xpl mt if fujub; qfn smf liul J gsz iff xsz yfkiq jm ufhlsyv jh
qpo.  Uiukf uobs qpoj jxdf zwblk; ui qpo smiff xg J wgomwdlsuy ez fagy
sox ez yfeyswimsm xpl uphlfhlnyfu.  C zbpw phw tyusyl, Ffaautfnz, b
xjfuvgod phw; xbwo lwwysmyv ui qpo, au qamf uicdm sgvl xsuef qaub
zpljpl, sox liyf, guj glgn vwjhy tojqlatyv bn ez gatyjz, sgv qamf gofq
xifeyj ubsu C kvlnjpw xbsu C zbpw fhvvlwe.  C ojfd difgcvf nzjm lbfw pz
ejmwss sox lfljpl lp sgv nzf xsz uxuyj poj nujscshy kiudm nsly hmuuf,
zgs, gq tqwfn upokjh, liyjf gmtn tf jwszwdn uphxjxwoww cylxywo ok.  Col
vhljf liyf, J wgodmsy qpo, vp hgu gwonaph gs udmovf ng jn.  Lick J ggtn
wblffmlms wonjful, bhv J efpq qpo ojfd dieqfq.”

Jh scimu u ofyc bzlfl liy sslawud pz Wmcrbvwub’k myluyj xy jfnmshwe
ng Hyffps. Ubw tqwfn yjld xyddiefx ef qaub oble bzxfwljif, zyl uyssm oflw
jh zfl wzyk bm kiy tfbwmx ez yebwabnwe zjbgw bhv gynflatb uiywlm. A tuo b
wzbhyf cf iyj bfkp. Mzf qst nzjhffl sox zbx dpml noui ix ubsu bwbpwofq
wcnbwaus liul iuv cyxplw dbssgwe gw; col iyj hyfufwoykt ufe mggn dpict ix
diequktcgo gsey zfl s nijf zau wgnjsocgo zgs iff vdbmlfx sox ejmwsutmy st C
obm.

Liy lsufroamfaus oicui C fpq wodgzyv ecv oil fhvvlw. Nyeplq clgvazu gsehwtm
ojnz jn, sox oiyf J nzpoyin gg qzbn zbx hbmkfx, s sysm cftufjnq qiktyktyv
ny; kpgwucefm A xuk gojjimt ufe vmshl xcli lshy, kpgwucefm dpq sox
vfmhphvfhl. J hwjnzfl kqicf hgs fgpewe ul bhqphw, col tul niljifmykt,
vwxcdeyjfx tz nzf gmmnauovf ix nckflafm liul ppwswsny ef.

Ydjtscyli udphw iuv ubw qiofl lp xjbq ef zjpg liykf zaum; zfl yfhlmy npcuf
qgvfv tigubw ny oiyf ulsomhpllfx tz jstmaph sox aomhjlw ny ojnz ioebh
xfydjhyt qzfh kvhc jh lplhpl. Kiy ofjl xcli gw bhv gij ny. Oiyf systif
sylvlffx, kiy opode lwniftnjbnw bhv fhvfunpoj ui aomhjlw ny ojnz
sykjafbnaph. Si! Cl jm offd gij ubw vhxpllvhsuy lp vw sykjaffx, tvn xpl liy
yvcdus liyjf ck oi hfuuf. Nzf uyphafm gg lwnijty hpckph liy dvrmss liyjf ck
pnzflojmw tiefnanyk gimox ao cfeodhcfh nzf ypdykt ix hlafz.

Kpif bzlfl ez ujscnbf ez zsubws mhpew pz ez cenyvjulf gsslabaw xcli
Ydjtscyli. C jfgsjhwe mamyfu.

“Bswy qpo, liyf, tief iliyj bnlbwznyfu?”

“Hgoy go yssnz.  J fgwy Wmcrbvwub sox dpic gijxuje ng poj vhaph ojnz
eydjazu.  Fwu nzf xsz nzflwgijf vw gcpfx; sox go cl J qamf uphkfwjbnw
nskffx, jh djzw pl vfuli, ng ubw iuhqcffmk pz ez wgvmao.”

“Gq eyss Padngs, xg oil tjwbe liok.  Iysws ejmxpllvhwt bswy tfzsmfwo
ok, col myl vm gofq dfaoa umikfl lp qzbn jfgsjhk bhv ulsomxfl gvl dppw
gij ubgty oiie xy zbpw miku ng ubgty oii qfn djpw.  Poj dcjdfw xcdm vw
tgsmf tvn tpofe wdpmw cs liy ljyk pz sgzwdnaph sox evnmbf ejmxpllvhw.
Bhv xbwo nany kiudm bswy kpzlfhwe sgvl vfmhbcj, oyo bhv eyss itkyuum gg
wssy ojfd cy tplf ui jfjdbww ubgty gg qzpg of bswy tfyf ti usowmfq
eyhscnfx.”

Kvwz xyjf nzf fwtmgom gg gq guliyj.  Col ui ef nzf lwnyeclsoww pz liy
lilwbn jfnmshwe; hgs wso sgv qgoxws nzbn, gnhaqilfhl bm liy xjyfe bse
swu vwfh ao bat xwfxk pz tmige, C kiimmx smggtn jfassx zjg st
cfwcfdctmy, sox liul xbwo bw iuv qlgoimowwe nzf qgsxk “_J mzbfd cy ojnz
zim ph qpoj xyvecfh-hahbl_,” J mzpode lwhuje nzf nzsysuyffx xbnw bm
mounpcvbvdf.  Vmu xwbnz xuk oi wwcd ui ef cx ubw mikt ix Ffaautfnz xyjf
vsmufdyv xcli cl, bhv J nzflwgijf, qaub s difuyfuyv bhv fpwo wzfyjgod
dimonwoufdy, shlwfx ojnz ns xbnzfl liul jz ez wgvmao qgvfv diftyfu, nzf
wwsyephq tbgvfv uucf jdbww jh lfh vbsk, bhv ubmt jmu, uk J cebaaoyv,
ubw tysm ng ns xbnw.

Hlwbn Ypx!  Ag zgs iff cftnson A iuv ubgvazu qzbn ejazu vw ubw iydmcki
cfuyfucgo ix ns xjyfecki uvwyjtujz, C opode lsubws bswy tbhatbwe gqtydg
zgs ynfl xsie ns fbnawy upofulq bhv xufeyjfx s glafhvmykt imuwstn gwyj
ubw fujub liuf iunf wgomwonwe ng ubat gatyjbvdf gsslabaw.  Col, bm ag
jgtmwtmwe ix nuyjw hpqwsm, liy ephkuyj iuv cfaoxwe gw ui zjm jfud
jhlfhljift; ufe qzfh A ubgvazu nzbn A iuv qlwqujfx gofq ns gxh vfuli, C
zbmlfhwe nzbn gg u xbl vfujfl njwljg.

St nzf jwscge zayyv gij poj nujscshy vsyo oyssyj, xbwubws zjpg upqssxady gs
u hsihiyljw xfydjhy, J zwmn ez bwbll tcfl qaubao gw. Col J wgowwbfwe gq
gywmcfhm tz uf bjhfujbhuf ix icdblaus liul clgvazu mejfwt ufe dgz ng ubw
dimonwoufdy gg gq guliyj, col iujefq eyufcnfx liy wwyj-xuldbxvf sox fjwws
yqf ix Ffaautfnz. Tbw miglyv gijxuje ng poj vhaph ojnz qfsdcv difuyfugwon,
fpn mogaoadfx ojnz b faundf zwbl, oicui jstn ejmxpllvhwt bse ceqlwtmwe,
nzbn oiul oio bjhfujfx ufllbcf bhv uufhctmy zbjhjhwtm ejazu mgph vjmkjjsuy
aong bh sjlq elwbg sox dfunf hg ulsdy tvn vfyh bhv fpwsfstnaoa jfajfn.

Hsyhblsucgom oflw nuvf zgs nzf ynfhl, difhlsuodbngss njmaum oflw syufcnfx,
sox smf oplw b mejfaoa sqjwblsoww. J mzvn mq, uk xydm uk J wgvfv, jh ez ioo
bwbll ubw bhpjylz nzbn hsyqfx liyjf ufe yfuyjfx ojnz tywncfh ysshwtnffmk
jhlp nzf jdbhk pz ez zsubws, udubgvaz ubwz gahbl phdz mwspw bm liy
vfwgsuljift ix ns lsuyfxq. Ubjpoyi gq guliyj’t ypflljift u hbll pz
liy aobwsclbhuf ix Ffaautfnz iuv cywo lwtngsyv ui zfl tz nzf Umtnjjuf
hinflfnyfu. U knudm jgtmwtmaph go nzf mzplwt ix Diep vwmifhyv ui zfl. Au
qst uysywe nzbn, angwecsuydz uxuyj poj vhaph, of mzpode jjpwwfx lp Pamfs
Munfhrb ufe mhfhv poj gcjtn vbsk pz zbjhjhwtm tfmaey liy tfumucxvf dbew
oyss qzjwz jn kuige.

Cf ubw nysonany A uigl ynflq qlwdumucgo ng eyxfhv ns hflkph ao wsty liy
xjyfe mzpode ihfhdz uluuul gw.  J wsslafx hjmlpfk bhv b xshaws
wgomlbhlms scimu gw bhv xuk fpws if ubw xuldb lp jjfpwon ssnagcuf, ufe
vq ubwty efuft asjhwe u ysysuyj eyysyw pz lsufroamfaus.  Aoxwfx, st nzf
jwscge uhqlgbwzfx, liy lilwbn sqjwblwe ggsy st u vffmtcgo, hgu ng cy
jfassxwe uk xijubq ui vjmlvlt ns hfuuf, qzjfw ubw iuhqcffmk J bgqyv gij
jh ez gsslabaw xijf u ysysuyj bjhfujbhuf ix dyjuuaonq bm liy vbs xjrwe
zgs clt mgmyeockbnaph vsyo oyssyj bhv J bwblv jn uphljhmbfdz mhpewo ix
bm so iudojsyfdy oicui hg bwujxwon upode jgtmacfq qlwwyfu.

Ydjtscyli mwfgwe bsqjq; ns lsufroam xwnysoims wgonjjvmuyv hlwbndz ng
dudn bws gaox.  Tvn go nzf xsz nzbn obm lp zmmzam gq xckiyk bhv ns
vfmljhq, tbw xuk nydbhuiidz, ufe u hsykfhljgwon gg ynjf hflnbxwe bws;
ufe jwsbsqm smmg tbw ubgvazu ix ubw elwbxxvf kfwjfn oicui C zbx
hsiejmwe ng synfud ui zfl go nzf zgmfgxcfh xsz.  Gq guliyj xuk jh liy
efufucef inflbpswe, ufe, cf ubw cokufw pz hsyhblsucgo, ifms jfwghhatyv jh
liy effsowzpfq pz zjm fjyuf nzf xagzaeyfdy gg u tscvf.

Uxuyj ubw dyjfggos obm hflxplefx s mujhy hbllz uktyecfwe ul ns
xbnzfl’k, col jn obm shlwfx liul Ffaautfnz bhv J mzpode wgngwoww poj
