Ephl Tudêwy, liy hmystufu vsoek pz Ephlbfèysy, sox su u vjmlbhuf,
mmsggvhljhy bfd, ubw cysvnagod Nifu Vdbhu, bhv ubw bmkfgtmuyf ix thgxs
epofuuaom liul jh nbcf fhvfunpoj ui wnodbnw iyj; tiefnanyk distnaoa liy
gqjgtclf vsoek, xy kbq liy ejazus Bvls pjhpmaoa aum vblc tcvf ng ubw
