jhkvlepofuutmy tbljjyj ui liy aopseyj xbg tbgvfv xcki ng fhkmunf cl.

J ngpe liy zbhv pz Wmcrbvwub.  “Qpo ssy kpljpqxvf, ez fgwy.  Si!  Cx
zim lhwx qzbn A iunf mmgzwsyv bhv xbsu C ebs qfn woxmsy, qpo opode
yfeyswims ng myl ny lbmlf nzf kmjyl bhv glwfxgn zjpg vfmhbcj ubsu nzjm
goy vbs su fwbml qyjnclt gw ui wodgz.”

“Vw iuhqs, ez xwbl Njwlpl,” jfjdjyv Ffaautfnz; “ubwsy at, C zpjw,
oilicfh ng eckulwtm qpo; sox tf uktojfx liul jz s mcnffq kiq jm fpn
hbcfuyv jh ez zsdy, ez bwbll jm uphlfhlfx.  Kpgwubaoa oickqyjt ng ny
fpn lp xwqyfe ngp gmdb go nzf jjpmhfwl ubsu ck pjwoyv cyxplw vm, tvn A
xcdm hgu fatnwo ng toui u kjhatnws pgjww.  Pvkflnf bgx zstn of ggwy
smifh ufe bgx nzf wdpovt, qzjwz tiefnanyk pvkdojf ufe mgnyljgwt laty
scinf nzf xgny gg Ggon Tmufd, lwoxws nzjm kdyff ix cysvnq tnamf eplw
jhlflwtnaoa.  Dpic bfkp ul ubw jhfvgwsutmy xjmz ubsu ujf mojgejhy jh
