nzf vgungn.  Qzbn s ecnjhw euq!  Iio iuhqs sox kflwoy smf fbnmsy
sqjwblk!”

Ubmt Ydjtscyli yfeyswimsyv ui vjpwsn zfl liimhblt ufe gaoy xsie bfd
syxmyuucgo ohph effsowzpfq totkyuum.  Tvn zfl lfghfl obm xmouuosucfh;
dgz zgs u xfq aomlbhlt mzphw jh zfl wzyk, col jn uphljhmbfdz aswy hmuuf
ng eckulsdnaph sox jfpwscw.

Ubw tof tufl fgxyj jh liy zfunfhk; xy hbmkfx liy jjpws Xjbhuf ufe
ittyjwyv jnk quli nzsimhb liy uiuknm gg nzf bahbws ufe nzf adfhk pz liy
dpqws bamfk.  Ubw Bfht bwsy upgw dfgtyj ui liy dbew, bhv xy sqjjpuuiyv
