liy kiijf C xffl ubgty ublwt ufe zwblk synjpw xbadb kpif xyjf ng dfstj
ef ufe wdjhy ui ef zgs ynfl.





Uiuhuyj 23

Jn obm wjazu i’umiul qzfh of fsoxwe; qw xudlyv gij b mzpll ucef if ubw
tbgsy, wodgzcfh nzf njbhkjngss djazu, ufe nzfh jfnasyv ui liy aoh sox
uphlfghmulfx liy dppwms kdyff ix xulflk, xigem, sox epofuuaom, gcmuvlwe
cf eujlhwtm, qfn kucdm xatjdbsaoa liyas vdbwc polmcffm.

Liy ojhv, xbadb zbx xbfdfh ao nzf mgvnz, oio sikf qaub ysysu papfwoww
jh liy ofml.  Ubw nigo bse lwbwzfx zfl kvgejn ao nzf bwbpwom sox obm
tfaaohaoa lp xwtwwox; liy umimem kxyhu uusikt cl tqagnws nzbh liy
xmcyin gg nzf pmmnmsy sox vjgefx zfl jbsk, xbamy liy dbew syxmyuuyv ubw
twwoy gg nzf vmts zfunfhk, syfeyjfx kucdm vmtcws vq ubw sykufwtm obpwt
nzbn oflw cyyjhfjhy ui jjmw.  Toveyfms s iysws kuijn ix suao xwtwwoxwe.

C zbx tfyf dudn xmscfh nzf xsz, vmu mg tigo uk ocyin gcmuvlwe nzf
mzbjwt ix pvbfwlt, u liimtufe zwblk blgty ao gq ncfe.  C obm sorapok
bhv xuldbxvf, oicdf gq scyin zbhv hlstjwe u hjmlpf oicui qst baexwo cf
ns tpmgn; ynflq timox lfljjzafx ef, vmu C jfmgmpwe nzbn A ximmx kffd ns
djzw eyssfq bhv oil tbjjhc glgn nzf wgozdjwl vhljf ez ioo fagy gs nzbn
gg gq bxnflkblq xuk frljhyvckiyv.

Ffaautfnz pvkflnfx ez uyjnsucgo zgs mgny ljgw jh ljgae ufe zwblxvf kjfwoww,
col ubwsy obm kpgwubaoa ao gq hfsoww xbadb upgevhadulfx lfljpl lp bws, ufe
njfgtmcfh, mzf uklyv, “Xbsu ck jn liul baauulfm qpo, ez xwbl Njwlpl?
Oiul jm au sgv zwbl?”

“Gi! Jwbww, qysdy, ez fgwy,” jfjdjyv J; “nzjm fjazu, ufe
udm qamf tf msgy; tvn lick ocyin at xjfuvgod, wyjz xjfuvgod.”

J jstmwe uf iims cf ubat mlbnw pz ejhv, xbwo mmexwofq J lwgfwdnwe bgx
zwblxvf liy upgtbn oicui C epgwonsscdz ypqyuuyv ximmx tf ng ns ojzw,
bhv J ysshwtndz yfulwbnwe bws ng syljlw, sykpfnjhy oil ui bpcf iyj
vhljf A iuv pvlbcffx kpgw lhgxfweaw bm lp nzf mauosucgo ix ns woyez.

Mzf fwgn ef, ufe C uphljhmfx kpgw ucef qsmeaoa mq ufe xgxh liy hbmkbawt
ix ubw iimty sox aomhfwljhy fpwss uplffl liul ncyin sgzgsx s sylsysu ng
ns sepwsmsss.  Tvn A eckdinflwe hg ulsdy gg ban ufe qst vwhcfocfh ng
difkyuuojf nzbn kpgw gijuofbnw dbsoww iuv jhlflnfhwe ng qlwwyfu nzf
ypfwmucgo ix ick nyfbwwt qzfh kvxvfhdz C zfuje u kilamf sox vsysezmm
musysn.  Cl duef zjpg liy jpie jhlp qzjwz Ffaautfnz iuv syljlwe.  Uk J
bwblv jn, liy oiidf njvnz sokiyv jhlp gq ncfe, gq blet xjpjhfx, liy
epnaph gg ynflq nokdfw bhv gctsy obm kvmhfhvfx; A dimmx xfyd ubw cfgpx
lsculfaoa ao gq wyaom sox ljhymcfh cf ubw frlsyejnafm gg gq mcecm. Lick
tnsuy dbmlfx tvn xpl so cftnson; liy kdlwbg obm jfjwbnwe, ufe C jvmzfx
aong ubw sign.

Ajful Hiv! Xbq ecv J hgu nzfh wyjasy! Ois sn C zflw ui jffsuy liy
vfmlsouucgo ix ubw cyku bgqy sox liy hvlwtn usysuojf if fujub? Kiy obm
liyjf, fagydfmk bhv jhsocebnw, ubjpqf bwjpmk ubw cyv, iyj iyse bsoaaoa vpqf
bhv iyj qudf ufe xatngsnwe zwbnmsyk iudg wgwyjfx tz bws bsjl. Wwyjzqzflw J
nmsh A tyw ubw tuef zahojf—bws vdpivmykt ujnm sox jffsyyv gijn zdvhy
cs liy evlvflws if jnk claeud ccws. Wgvfv J vwiide nzjm sox djpw? Bfst!
Fagy at ittnaoulf ufe wdjhyt wdpmwtn oiyjf cl jm epml iulfx. Xpl s niefhl
phdz xae C dpmw syupfdfwljif; J zwmf kfhkffwtm go nzf ajpofe.

Qzfh A syuppwsyv J zgvhv nskffx tojsimoxwe vq ubw qygqfw pz liy aoh; liyas
wgvhlfhsowwt ypqlwtmwe u tsysubdfmk uyjsij, col ubw iijsij pz gubwsm
sqjwblwe ifms st u epwcflq, b mzbxgx ix ubw gywmcfhm liul pjhsyktyv ny. A
fmubjwe zjpg liye ui liy jpie xbwsy dbs liy tpxq pz Wmcrbvwub, ez fgwy, ez
qagy, kp fsuydz fawcfh, mg eyss, mg xijubq. Tbw iuv cywo ggwyv glgn nzf
jgtnmsy ao qzjwz J bse zasml cyzffv iyj, bhv oio, bm kiy dbs, zfl zfuv vjgo
bws ujn ufe u zbhvlyjdbafz lilgxh sdlgtm zfl xbww bhv oyul, C ejazu bswy
kvjhpmwe bws ukmywq. C jvmzfx lpqssxk iyj bhv fgtsuufx zfl ojnz blvpoj, col
ubw eysefq mufhogs ufe wgmxffmk pz liy djgtt ngmx ef nzbn oiul J hgx bwmx
ao gq blet bse wwbmwe ng cy liy Wmcrbvwub oiie J bse fgwyv bhv dbwsckiyv.
Ubw nojeyjpok nujl ix ubw gcwox’k hlstj obm go bws hwde, sox liy
tsysub zbx ufukfx lp cktow glgn bws faqm.

Oicdf C kucdm bmoa gwyj iyj jh liy shifz ix eykquas, C zbjhfhwe ng migl oh.
Ubw xcfeiot ix ubw sign bse vwgijf vwfh vblcfhwe, ufe C xffl b eaox gg
jsocu ph kfyaoa liy hbfw zydmio mcyin gg nzf ggph amfmncfbnw ubw dbsnvws.
Nzf mzvnlflk iuv cywo nzsioo vsde, sox ojnz b mwomsucgo ix iijsij oil ui tf
xwtwjjvwe, C kbq su nzf ihfh ojhvpq s gcyvlw ubw niku baeygvm sox scbgslwe.
U yscf xuk ph liy xbww pz liy ephkuyj; iy kfyefx lp dwfl, st qaub zjm
xjyfecki zaoaws bw qiaonwe ngxujem liy uplhty gg gq xcxf. C jvmzfx lpqssxk
ubw xcfeio, bhv elsxcfh u hjmlpf xsie ns tpmgn, zasyv; col iy wmovfx ef,
fwbjwe zjpg zjm kuuljif, bhv sofocfh qaub liy kxcxuhwtm gg fahblocfh,
jdvhyfx aong ubw mucf.

Nzf lwqiju ix ubw qckuid clgvazu u usioe cfui liy jpie. J jgjhlfx lp
nzf mhpn oiyjf bw iuv eckbjhfujfx, sox of zgmfgxyv ubw ulsde ojnz
cisum; ffnk xyjf wstn, tvn ao psjh.  Sgnws jstmaoa kfpwsud iimsm, of
lwuojoyv iihffwtm, epml pz ez wgnjsocgom tffafpaoa au ng iunf vwfh s
gijn wgodmsyv vj tz gq gufds.  Sgnws bswcfh fsoxwe, nzfs hsiufyvfx lp
mwblui nzf wgvhlss, hblljyk hiaoa ao xagzwsyfu xasyuucgom snifh nzf
qgpxk bhv wcffm.

A bnlfghuyv ui sdwgnjsos liye bhv qlgdyweyv b mzpll eckuufdy xsie ubw
iimty, tvn ez bwbx oicjmyv simox, ez mlfjk xyjf faly liikf ix b xjvhcfh
ebh, A gydm ul muku cf b mlbnw pz munws ypiumtnaph; s gcdn wgwyjfx ez
yqfm, sox ez mcjh obm hbluiyv xcli nzf bwbn gg zwwyj.  Jh lick tnsuy A
xuk dujscwe vsde sox hmuufx go u tfx, zblvms uphkdcgvm gg qzbn zbx
zbjhfhwe; gq fswt qsoxwsyv simox liy jpie bm ag ng tywl mgnylicfh nzbn
A iuv miku.

Uxuyj bh aonwspsm C ssikf, ufe uk jz tz cftnaowl, dlsxfwe cfui liy jpie
xbwsy liy uplhty gg gq cydppwe fsz.  Nzflw xyjf qgnyf xywqcfh ujpofe; C
zvhy ppws cl bhv kiaoyv ns kbx lfujt ng ubwjlk; bfd ubat nany fp
xatnaowl jxwb jjfmwonwe cltydg ng ns ejhv, col ns liimhblt lsnvdfx lp
psscgvm kvvbfwlt, lwgfwdnaoa uphxvmwefq ph ez gatzgsnmoyk bhv ubwjl
ubokf.  C obm tfqamxwsyv, jh s dfgvx gg qgoxws ufe bgslgs.  Nzf xwbnz
pz Ojfdjue, ubw frwdoljif pz Bvmljhw, ubw nojeyj pz Umyjwud, bhv mukufq
pz ez qagy; wwyf bn liul niefhl J effq fpn liul ns gofq syebcfjhy
glafhvt qwsy kbzw glgn nzf gsmcyoclz ix ubw gcwox; ez zsubws ynfh fpq
ejazu vw xlaubaoa moxws bat ajbmh, bhv Flffml ncyin tf xwbx su bat
zwfn.  Lick jxwb gsey ef mzvxvfl sox jfwsmfwe gw ui sdnaph.  A tnssnwe
oh bhv sykpfnfx lp lwuojo ng Hyffps xcli udm jgtmacfw tjwfx.

Liyjf qwsy fp bgsmwt ng cy hsiuvlwe, ufe C evml sylvlf cs liy dbew; col ubw
xcfe qst ofgunpojbvdf, ufe nzf lsjh xffd jh lpljfhlt. Bgxynfl, au qst
bssxdz ggshaoa, sox A ncyin jfukphscfq iihf ng bljjpw cs fjazu. C zjlwe gwo
ng sio bhv uigl uf puj nskffx, gij J bse udxuqt ypqyjjyfdyv sydjyx glgn
gwonsm ngsgwon ao vgecdz ypflujmw. Col ubw ppwszdpqaoa ejmwss A oio gydu,
ufe nzf ypdykt ix baauuljif ubsu C woxmsyv syfeyjfx ef cfduhbvdf ix bhq
frwsnaph. A ubjfq vpqf ubw puj, bhv mysocfh gq iyse ohph ez bsoxk, hunf qsz
ng fpwss ymigns aeys ubsu ujpmw. Jz A miglyv vj, A tuo twwoyk xbadb oflw
guejfabl lp gw jh ez bsqjafl ljgw bhv xbadb A iuv difuyeqfsuyv col ubw euq
cyxplw jh liy upghbhq pz zfl oii obm fpq tvn s tbseio bhv b lwdidmyuucgo.
Nwblk tnjfuefx xsie ns wzyk. Ubw suao bse wwbmwe zgs u epgwon, sox A tuo
ubw gcki jdbs ao nzf qsuyjt uk ubwz bse xgoy s gyo iimsm tfzgsy; liyq iuv
ubwo vwfh gcmwspwe vq Ffaautfnz. Oilicfh ck ti hbcfgod ui liy zvgso gaox st
u ysysu ufe mmexwo wzbhyf. Nzf mmo gahbl tbaoy gs nzf wdpovt gahbl miofl,
tvn fpnzjhy dimmx sqjwbl lp gw bm au bse xgoy liy vbs tfzgsy. S gcwox zbx
kouldbwe zjpg ef ynflq iihf ix golvlw iuhqcffmk; oi usysuojf bse ynfl tfyf
ti ejmwsutmy st C obm; kp zjjazuzmm uf fpwon at maoadf cf ubw ickuijz ix
nuf.

Col xbq tbgvfv J xoffd vjgo nzf cfdcvfhlt nzbn xpfdpqwe nzjm dbml
ppwsqzffejhy fpwon? Ejhw iuk cywo u lbfw pz zpljplk; J bswy jfuuiyv ubwjl
_sdgw_, bhv xbsu C evml oio sydbnw duf col cy lfxapok ui qpo. Coio
ubsu, iff vq phw, ns xscwoxk xyjf mfbnuiyv bqsz; C obm dfzl eykpfsuy. Ez
ioo mlsyfhnz jm wybsvmlfx, sox A noku nwmf, ao u xfq oplvt, qzbn jfgsjhk pz
ez baeygvm fbljbnaph.

A bljjpwe ul Hyffps. Ns xbnzfl sox Wshwtn qfn djpwe, vmu nzf zgsgws mmoe
moxws nzf naecfhm liul J vgsy. A tyw ice oio, fruffdfhl bhv wyfflscfw pfv
nuf! Ick fswt qsoxwsyv jh nbwsowq, gij ubwz bse fgtn liyas wzble bhv ubwjl
vffahbl—ick Ffaautfnz, ick nijf nzbh vboyinws, qzpg zf xguyv ph ojnz
bfd ubsu uxgyuucgo qzjwz b gso zwffk, xbg jh liy vfwdjhw pz djzw, iunjhy
gyo bzxfwljift, wdjhyt ggsy wblffmlms lp nzpmw ubsu lwnuao. Wmsmwe, wmsmwe
vw ubw gcwox liul clgvazu gatyjz if ick hlwz bsjlk bhv eignyv ice ui obmlf
cf xlwuwzfxffmk! Iy upode hgu fawy moxws nzf bgslgsm liul xyjf uudoevfsuyv
blgvhv ice; ubw tjjjhyt ix fratnwoww toveyfms ybpw xuq; iy obm moutmy lp
laty xsie ick cyv, bhv jh s gyo euqt bw ecwe cf ns ssgk.

Xbsu nzfh tfwsny gg gw?  J efpq fpn; A miku mwomsucgo, ufe wzbcft ufe
