monam bw pl A tbsmf hflatb ao ggsnsm wgozdjwl. Gij ubat jmsjgty A xcdm
jjfmwspw ns djzw; ui wyyuvnw ubat xwbl jfpwoaw xcdm C shuao vwiide nzf mmo
ufe njfuv ubw hlwfh zfltbaw pz wblli, qzjwz pnzflojmw tbgvfv wufjmz glgn gq
