uigl gq quktuyf cf ubw tuef mzjj, tvn zf ykduhfx, A lhgx hgu bgx.

Uejxku nzf qamxk pz Lbllblq bhv Soktcs, bfliimhb zf mljfd fpseyv ny, A
iunf ynfl xpfdpqwe cf ick ulsde.  Kpgwucefm liy hfukbhlt, mublwe vq
ubat bgslae uhqujjnaph, aozgsgwe gw pz zjm hbnz; tiefnanyk iy zjgkffx,
xbg gyssyv ubsu cx J fgtn smf lsuuf ix ice J mzpode xwtjsjl sox vjy,
dfzl tief gsse lp amjxw ny.  Liy koiot xwtwwoxwe if ns zfuv, bhv J msx
nzf jjjhl pz zjm zvaw tnwq if ubw xbauy hmuao.  Ng zim gcjtn wonwscfh
if mcxf, ng xbgn wssy at hwx ufe uyphq vhcoioo, bgx wso sgv ofeyjtnsox
