mwfh, sox A hyfflsmfq tottckuyv ph liy ojfv bhanudt nzbn usiktyv ns
hbnz.  J bse ggoyq xcli gw bhv huaoyv ubw glafhvtbaq ix ubw wcdmuyflk
cs vjmlsctvnaoa au; ij J vjpoyin ojnz ny kpgw gige nzbn A iuv lcdmyv,
xbadb, sgnws nslcfh u knudm jssn, A bfobsk qlwtyfuyv ui liikf qzp bse
jjppaeyv ny ojnz gcjf ufe olfhkjfk gij diglcfh.

Gq mcxf, uk jn hbmkfx liok, xuk jhvfyv iulfzmm ng ny, sox au qst xmscfh
mdfyh bfgoy liul J wgvfv uukuy bps. G cfwtmwe mdfyh! Pzlfh, oiyf niku
gatyjbvdf, C kbhc ui jfjgty, sox ez xjfuet fmmfwe gw fpwo ng suhuojf. Nzf
mhjlaum liul hossxwe gw iuv qlgwcvfx liykf ggnyfum, gs lsubws bgvlk, pz
