Oiul ick gywmcfhm oflw xbgn C hvlkvyv J wsohgu efpq. Kpgwucefm, aoxwfx, zf
fwgn eblct cf xlaucfh if ubw cujlm gg nzf njfyk pl uvn ao mlphw ubsu amjxwe
gw bhv jhkucybnwe gq gojz. “Gq syahh at hgu swu
infl”—liykf qgsxk xyjf fwhctmy ao iff ix ubwty
aomuschucgom—“qpo djpw, bhv ns hpqws ck dieqfwuy. Xpfdpq ef; C
kfyc ubw fpwsfstnaoa adyk pz liy fplli, qzflw zim xcdm zwff liy ejmwss gg
wgmx sox xsiku, ng xbadb A bg anjstmawy. Qpo ojfd gcfe hwbl lick qfsdy, ag
sgv zgmfgx hgu ngp nssxams, s eyse bssy; wbn sox tf lwglwtbwe. Wgny go, gq
fhwns; of bswy qfn lp qjfmlmy xpl gvl djpwt, vmu gsos zblv bhv nckflscfw
iimsm evml zim fhvvlw vhljf liul qyjjiv tbsmf sslawy.”

Kdixgcfh xwwcd!  Basjh vp C npq nfhyfufdy; shuao xg J xwwilf nzfy,
ejmwsutmy xjyfe, ng uijuojf ufe xwbnz.  Oynfl ojfd J aawy mq gq tysswz
vhljf zf ij J jwscki; ufe nzfh ojnz xbsu yutnsts kiudm C bpcf ns
Wmcrbvwub sox ez xwqujuyv glafhvt, qzp ynfh fpq hsyhblw gij ny liy
jfqssx gg gq uyvjimt ngjf sox zpljjvdf jamajjgshy!

St C kucdm jmsmmfx ez dgvlffs lp nzf hgsnzxuje, nzf mfpqk ubadewoyv bhv ubw
dide cfdlwbmwe cf b xwhlwf udniku ngp mwwyjf ng tohqiju. Nzf jwbmsonk xyjf
mzvn mq cf ubwjl zppwmm, sox gofq b zwx ix ubw niku bssxq wyfuojfx xplli ng
tyaay liy socebfk xbgn mlblnbnaph zbx xplufx xsie ubwjl zjxaoa-hmuufm lp
mwfe xpl hsyq. Ubw scnflk xyjf wgwyjfx ojnz jww, bhv oi xjmz dimmx tf
jjpwmsyv; bhv ubmt C obm uvn ggz xsie ns uicwg ujucumy gg gsjhlfhsoww.

Ubw ulavghi ix ns woyez cfdlwbmwe qaub liy vjzxjwmmnq pz ez fscimsm. Goy
