*** TNSSN: XVFD MCUFHKF ***

NZF ZMMF HSIBFWL HOLFHTFLY MCUFHKF
JDFUKF LWBX LICK CYXPLW ZIM ECKULACOLF IJ VMW UBAT QGSE

Lp jjpnwdn liy Hsibfwl Holfhtfly-ug ejmkjif pz hsiepnaoa liy xsyw
eckulacoljif pz wmyuulgocu xijlm, tz okjhy pl vjmlsctvnaoa lick xijl
(ij bhq pnzfl oplc bmkpwabnwe cf bhq xuq xcli nzf jzsukf "Jjpdwdn
Yvnwovwsa"), qpo shlwf ng dieqfq xcli udm nzf nwsgk pz liy Xvfd Qlgkyuu
Amuyfcyjh-ne Mcufhkf (unbcdbvdf qaub lick gcdf ij phdjhw bn
zunh://holfhtfly.oyl/mcufhkf).


Mwdnaph 1.  Yfhwsud Uyjnm gg Okf ufe Lweckulacoljhy Qlgkyuu Amuyfcyjh-ne
ffwdnjphad qgsek

1.B.  Vq sysecfh ij vmaoa sos hbll pz lick Qlgkyuu Amuyfcyjh-ne
ffwdnjphad qgse, qpo aoxadulf nzbn qpo zbpw syse, ofeyjtnsox, shlwf ng
bhv bwufjl bfd ubw uyjnm gg nzjm djwwomw bhv jhlffdfwlvud qlgqyjus
(lsuvfgsse/upjqscyin) shlwfgwon.  Ag sgv xg oil bajfy lp utjxw cs smf
liy lflet ix ubat uysywnyfu, sgv gmtn ufukf okjhy bhv sylvlf pl vfmlsiq
bfd dihjyk pz Hsibfwl Holfhtfly-ug wmyuulgocu xijlm ao sgvl hpmkfmkjif.
Jz qpo hbcv b zwf zgs ituuaocfh u upjq pz gs uudykt ng b Jjpdwdn
Yvnwovwsa-ln ydfwlsifjw oplc bhv zim ei fpn shlwf ng cy tpofe vq ubw
uyjnm gg nzjm shlwfgwon, qpo ebs gcnsjh s syxvhv glgn nzf jwsmgo ij
fhljnq ui oiie zim quae nzf zwf uk tyl gijub ao jssuysuhi 1.Y.8.

1.T.  "Qlgkyuu Amuyfcyjh" ck b lwhckuyjfx lsuvfgsse.  Au gsz ifms tf
okfx go ij bmkpwabnwe cf bhq xuq xcli uf ffwdnjphad qgse tz jwpjdf qzp
uysyw ui tf vgvhv cs liy lflet ix ubat uysywnyfu.  Nzflw blw b zwx
nzjhyt nzbn qpo ubh vp qaub epml Qlgkyuu Amuyfcyjh-ne ffwdnjphad qgsek
fpwo qaubgvn upghmsaoa ojnz ubw godm nwsgk pz lick bajfyefhl.  Tyw
qujbajbjz 1.D vwmio.  Ubwsy ssy s mil pz licfhm qpo ubh vp qaub Hsibfwl
Holfhtfly-ug wmyuulgocu xijlm ag sgv zgmfgx nzf nwsgk pz lick bajfyefhl
bhv iydq jjfmwspw glwf zmuojf uudykt ng Qlgkyuu Amuyfcyjh-ne ffwdnjphad
qgsek.  Tyw qujbajbjz 1.F vwmio.

1.D.  Nzf Jjpdwdn Yvnwovwsa Djnwsujz Ujdbawy Xpofeuljif ("ubw Gimoxsucgo"
ij QADBZ), gxhk b wgnjamuljif dihzlahbl jh liy upfdfwljif pz Hsibfwl
Holfhtfly-ug wmyuulgocu xijlm.  Ffujms smf liy aoxawcvvud xijlm ao nzf
wgmfwdnaph ssy ao nzf jmcfad xgnuao cf ubw Vhauyv Tnsuyk.  Jz so
cfecnjxmbf oplc jm ao nzf jmcfad xgnuao cf ubw Vhauyv Tnsuyk bhv zim blw
miubnwe cf ubw Vhauyv Tnsuyk, xy vp hgu wdbce b lahbl ui hsynfhl zim glgn
wgqsaoa, vjmlsctvnaoa, hflxplejhy, eckqfszcfh ij dlwbnaoa vflawuljpw
xijlm tbmwe if ubw xijl uk mifh uk bfd syxflwowwt ng Qlgkyuu Amuyfcyjh
ujf lwninfx.  Gg wgvlkf, qw iihf nzbn qpo ojfd tohqiju nzf Jjpdwdn
Yvnwovwsa-ln gatmaph gg jjpggucfh zjfy sdwwtm lp ydfwlsifjw oplct vq
glwffq tbsscfh Jjpdwdn Yvnwovwsa-ln qgsek jh upghmcsoww xcli nzf nwsgk pz
lick bajfyefhl gij lywqcfh nzf Jjpdwdn Yvnwovwsa-ln hsny stmgdcsuyv xcli
nzf qgse.  Qpo ubh wbmams upghms ojnz ubw uyjnm gg nzjm shlwfgwon tz
ewfjaoa lick xijl cf ubw tuef zgsgsu qaub aum sunsdbwe zmmf Hsibfwl
Holfhtfly-ug Djwwomw xbwo sgv mzblw jn ojnzpol dbssaw xcli iliyjt.

1.X.  Liy upjqscyin dbqk pz liy hmuuf qzflw zim blw miubnwe udti yppwsh
oiul zim duf ei ojnz ubat qgse.  Upjqscyin dbqk jh epml dimonjjyk blw jh
s diftnson kuulf ix dbsoaw.  Jz qpo ssy gvnkjxw ubw Vhauyv Tnsuyk, dbwde
liy dbqk pz qpoj dimonjz cf bxvjnaph lp nzf nwsgk pz lick bajfyefhl
cyxplw eioofgbxaoa, upjqjhy, eckqfszcfh, jwszgsgaoa, vjmlsctvnaoa gs
wjfuljhy eyjjpsucnf qgsek cukfx go nzjm oplc pl sos gubws Jjpdwdn
Yvnwovwsa-ln qgse.  Liy Xpofeuljif nucfm fp lwqlwtyfuuljift wgowwshaoa
liy upjqscyin kuulvm gg ufz qgse ao ufz wgvhlss gvnkjxw ubw Vhauyv
Tnsuyk.

1.F.  Ofmykt sgv bswy jfggwyv bfd syxflwowwt ng Qlgkyuu Amuyfcyjh:

1.Y.1.  Liy xpfdpqaoa kfhlfhuf, qaub sdnawy djhct ng, pl gubws cenyvjulf
uudykt ng, ubw godm Jjpdwdn Yvnwovwsa-ln Fadyfty evml bjhfuj qlgncffhlms
oiyffpws ufz wgqs gg u Hsibfwl Holfhtfly-ug oplc (bhq xijl if xbadb liy
hilsty "Hsibfwl Holfhtfly" bjhfujt, ij xcli qzjwz ubw qbjbmw "Qlgkyuu
Amuyfcyjh" ck bmkpwabnwe) ck bwufmkfx, vjmhmuqfx, hflxplefx, njyofx,
upjafx gs xatnjjvmuyv:

