Kfwljif  2.  Jhxplebnaph scimu nzf Gatmaph gg Jjpdwdn Yvnwovwsa-ln

Jjpdwdn Yvnwovwsa-ln ck tsfphqnimt qaub liy xsyw eckulacoljif pz
wmyuulgocu xijlm ao zgsgsum jfuvbvdf vq ubw xcvfml wujjylz ix dieqolflk
jhumovjhy pvkpfwuy, gmx, ejxvmy-shyv bhv oyo dieqolflk.  Jn wyckum
tfwsvmw pz liy wgzgsnk pz zvhvsyvt ix widvhlfyjt ufe xgouljift zjpg
hfihmy ao udm qsmek pz djzw.

Widvhlfyjt ufe zaoufdcsm mmqjgsn lp jjppaey npfmonwflk xcli nzf
uktckuufdy liyq oywe, ck dlaucubf lp lwbwzjhy Qlgkyuu Amuyfcyjh-ne't
agbfk bhv fhkvlaoa liul ubw Qlgkyuu Amuyfcyjh-ne didmyuucgo qamf
jfgsjh xsywms swuamutmy xpl yfhwsuljift ng dief.  Cf 2001, ubw Qlgkyuu
Amuyfcyjh Fauyjblq Bluicnf Zgvhvbnaph obm usysuyv ui hsinjxw b mwdojf
ufe jwsgsoyfu zmuojf zgs Jjpdwdn Yvnwovwsa-ln ufe zmuojf awoyjbnaphk.
Ui dfujo ggsy scimu nzf Jjpdwdn Yvnwovwsa Djnwsujz Ujdbawy Xpofeuljif
bhv iio zims yxgijum sox vphsucgom ubh zffh, tyw Tyuucgom 3 sox 4
sox liy Xpofeuljif xyt quyf ul inlq://qox.jymux.ply.


