Hsixfmkpl Ejwzbyd T. Bssn at nzf ijjaaoulpl gg nzf Jjpdwdn Yvnwovwsa-ln
wgowwqn gg u djvjblq pz wmyuulgocu xijlm liul dimmx tf zjfydz mzblwe
qaub sosgoy.  Xpl licjus qfujt, bw qlgeoufx sox vjmlsctvnwe Jjpdwdn
Yvnwovwsa-ln yTpict qaub gofq b fgpmw oylxijl ix widvhlfyj tohqiju.


Jjpdwdn Yvnwovwsa-ln yTpict ujf ixuyf dlwbnwe zjpg kfpwsud qlaonwe
yvjnaphk, bfd pz oicui ujf wgozasgwe uk Qotmcu Eiebcf jh liy M.T.
ofmykt u upjqscyin fpnady at cfdfmeyv.  Ubmt, qw ei fpn ffwwtmsscdz
ewfj wCiglm ao wgnjdjufdy ojnz bhq qujucuvfss jsqyj fxaucgo.


